1042095,191,83,16,61,1,478,35,"Etehi saṃvaṇṇanāvisesehi saṃvaṇṇiyesu suttageyyādīsu aññāṇasaṃsayavipallāsā harīyanti, iti aññāṇādiharaṇakāraṇattā‘‘ etehī’’ ti padena niddiṭṭhā saṃvaṇṇanāvisesā hārā nāma, hara-dhātuyā ācariyassa vacībhedasaddo, taṃsamuṭṭhāpako cittuppādo ca mukhyattho, veneyyānaṃ saṃvaṇṇetabbasuttassa atthajānanādiñāṇasampayuttacittuppādo kāraṇūpacārattho, tassa upanissayapaccayabhūtānaṃ saṃvaṇṇanāvisesānaṃ upanissayapaccayasatti phalūpacārattho, iti-saddena sā upanissayapaccayasattiyeva parāmasīyati. "
