1043112,191,462,126,157,1,302,27,"Ottharitvā gamanaṭṭhānaṃ itipi vuccati pavuccati, tathāgatena gocarāsevanena vā bhāvanāsevanena vā nisevitaṃ bhajitaṃ itipi vuccati, tathāgatassa mahāvajirañāṇasabbaññutaññāṇadantehi ārañjitaṃ ārañjitaṭṭhānaṃ itipi vuccati, ato tathāgatapadādibhāvena vattabbabhāvato etaṃ sāsanabrahmacariyaṃ iti paññāyati. "
1043113,191,462,158,170,1,108,11,"Brahmacariyan ti brahmuno sabbasattuttamassa bhagavato cariyaṃ, brahmaṃ vā sabbaseṭṭhaṃ cariyaṃ brahmacariyaṃ. "
1043114,191,462,171,178,1,58,6,{Paññāyatī}ti yathāvuttehi pakārehi ñāyatīti attho veditabbo.
1043115,191,463,2,10,1,101,7,‘ ‘ Imassa sikkhattayassa saṅgahassa sāsanassa paripuṇṇabhāvaparisuddhabhāvasaṅkhātaṃ tathāgatapadabhāvaṃ! 
1043116,191,463,11,46,1,258,25,"Tathāgatapadabhāvaṃ, tathāgatanisevitabhāvaṃ, tathāgataārañjitabhāvaṃ, tehi pakārehi ñāpitabhāvaṃ kathaṃ mayaṃ nikkaṅkhā jānissāmā’’ ti vattabbato‘‘ tenāha bhagavā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ, tabbhāvadīpakena bhagavatā vuttena vacanena tumhehi nikkaṅkhehi jānitabboti vuttaṃ hoti. "
1043117,191,464,2,56,1,317,42,"Yadi bhagavā akkharehi ca padehi ca ugghaṭeti, byañjanehi ca ākārehi ca vipañcayati, niruttīhi ca niddesehi ca vitthāreti, evaṃ sati ācariyena racitena desanāhārena payojanaṃ na bhavati, desanāhārena na vinā bhagavato desanāyameva atthasijjhanatoti codanaṃ manasi katvā‘‘ kesaṃ ayaṃ dhammadesanā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ yogīnan’’ ti āha. "
1043118,191,464,57,66,1,80,8,"Tattha yogīnan ti yujjanti catusaccakammaṭṭhānabhāvanāyanti yogino, tesaṃ yogīnaṃ. "
1043119,191,464,67,82,1,149,15,Tena mayā racitena desanāhārena saṃvaṇṇitā ayaṃ vuttappakārā bhagavato desanā ugghaṭanādikiccaṃ sādhetīti desanāhāro yogīnaṃ sātthakoyevāti daṭṭhabbo.
1043120,191,464,83,107,1,125,14,‘‘ Desanāhārassa assādādidesanāhārabhāvo kena amhehi jānitabbo saddahitabbo’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ tenāha āyasmā… pe… desanāhāro’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1043121,191,464,108,137,1,209,22,"Tattha tena assādādidesanāhārabhāvena āyasmā mahākaccāno‘‘ assādādīnavatā… pe… desanāhāro’’ ti yaṃ vacanaṃ āha, tena vacanena tumhehi desanāhārassa yogīnaṃ assādādidesanāhārabhāvo jānitabbo saddahitabboti vuttaṃ hoti."
1043122,191,465,2,26,1,105,15,"‘ ‘ Kiṃ pana ettāvatā desanāhāro paripuṇṇo, añño niyutto natthī’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ niyutto desanāhāro’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
1043123,191,465,27,44,1,133,15,"Tattha yassaṃ desanāyaṃ assādādayo yena desanāhārena niddhāritā, tassaṃ desanāyaṃ so desanāhāro niddhāretvā yojitoti attho daṭṭhabboti. "
1043124,191,466,2,5,1,45,4,Iti desanāhāravibhaṅge sattibalānurūpā racitā 
1043125,191,467,2,4,1,18,2,Vibhāvanā niṭṭhitā. 
1043126,191,468,2,9,1,84,7,Paṇḍitehi pana aṭṭhakathāṭīkānusārena gambhīrattho vitthārato vibhajitvā gahetabboti.
1043127,191,469,2,4,1,27,2,2 . Vicayahāravibhaṅgavibhāvanā 
1043128,191,470,2,38,1,225,23,"11. Yena yena saṃvaṇṇanāvisesabhūtena desanāhāravibhaṅgena assādādayo suttatthā ācariyena vibhattā, so saṃvaṇṇanāvisesabhūto desanāhāravibhaṅgo paripuṇṇo,‘‘ katamo vicayo hāro’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha katamo vicayo hāro’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1043129,191,470,39,54,1,134,14,Tattha {tatthā}ti tesu niddiṭṭhesu soḷasasu desanāhārādīsu hāresu katamo saṃvaṇṇanāviseso vicayo hāro vicayahāravibhaṅgo nāmāti pucchati.
1043130,191,470,55,80,1,160,17,‘‘ Yaṃ pucchitañca vissajjitañcā’’ tiādiniddesagāthāya idāni mayā vuccamāno‘‘ ayaṃ vicayo hāro kiṃ vicinatī’’ tiādiko saṃvaṇṇanāviseso vicayahāravibhaṅgo nāmāti yojanā.
1043131,191,471,2,40,1,197,28,"‘ ‘ Ayaṃ vicayo hāro kiṃ vicinatī’’ ti iminā yo vicayo vicinitabbo, taṃ vicayaṃ vicinitabbaṃ pucchati, tasmā vicinitabbaṃ visayaṃ visuṃ visuṃ niyametvā dassetuṃ‘‘ padaṃ vicinati, pañhaṃ vicinatī’’ tiādi vuttaṃ."
1043132,191,471,41,63,1,120,13,"‘‘ Kiṃ vicayo padavicayo’’ tiādiṃ avatvā‘‘ kiṃ vicinati, padaṃ vicinatī’’ tiādivacanena vicayasaddassa kattusādhanatthaṃ dasseti. "
1043133,191,471,64,76,1,165,11,Tattha padaṃ {vicinatī}ti navavidhassa suttantassa sabbaṃ padaṃ yāva nigamanā nāmapadādijātisaddādiitthiliṅgādiākārantādipaṭhamavibhatyantādiekavacanādivasena vicinati. 
1043134,191,471,77,82,1,92,4,Pañhaṃ {vicinatī}ti adiṭṭhajotanādisattādhiṭṭhānādisammutivisayādiatītavisayādivasena vicinati. 
1043135,191,471,83,91,1,153,7,Vissajjanaṃ {vicinatī}ti ekaṃsabyākaraṇavissajjanādisāvasesabyākaraṇavissajjanādi sauttarabyākaraṇa vissajjanādi lokiyabyākaraṇavissajjanādivasena vicinati. 
1043136,191,471,92,101,1,57,6,Pubbāparaṃ {vicinatī}ti pubbena aparaṃ saṃsanditvā vicinati. 
1043137,191,471,102,107,1,67,4,Assādaṃ {vicinatī}ti assādakataṇhādiassādetabbasukhādivasena vicinati. 
1043138,191,471,108,116,1,142,7,Ādīnavaṃ {vicinatī}ti dukkhadukkhavipariṇāmadukkhasaṅkhāradukkhavasena vā aniṭṭhānubhavanādiādiantavantatādisaṃkilesabhāgiyādivasena vā vicinati. 
1043139,191,471,117,132,1,132,13,"Nissaraṇaṃ {vicinatī}ti maggavasena vā nibbānavasena vā maggassa vā āgamavasena, nibbānassa asaṅkhatadhātuādipariyāyavasena vā vicinati. "
1043140,191,471,133,148,1,133,13,"Phalaṃ {vicinatī}ti dhammacaraṇassa duggatigamanābhāvena vā maccutaraṇādinā vā desanāya phalaṃ, desanānusārena caraṇassa phalaṃ vicinati. "
1043141,191,471,149,160,1,120,10,Upāyaṃ {vicinatī}ti aniccānupassanādivasena pavattananibbidāñāṇādivasena vā saddhāsativasena vā visuddhiyā upāyaṃ vicinati. 
1043142,191,471,161,170,1,95,8,Āṇattiṃ {vicinatī}ti pāpaparivajjanāṇattivasena vā lokassa suññatāpekkhanāṇattivasena vā vicinati. 
1043143,191,471,171,181,1,89,9,Anugītiṃ {vicinatī}ti vuttānugītivasena vā vuccamānānugītivasena vā anurūpaṃ gītiṃ vicinati. 
1043144,191,471,182,201,1,189,18,Sabbe nava suttante {vicinatī}ti suttageyyādike nava sutte āhaccavacanavasena vā anusandhivacanavasena vā nītatthavacanavasena vā neyyatthavacanavasena vā saṃkilesabhāgiyādivasena vā vicinati. 
1043145,191,472,2,29,1,194,21,"Kiñcāpi padavicayo paṭhamaṃ vibhatto, suttassa pana anupadaṃ vicinitabbatāya atibhāriyo, na sukaro padavicayoti taṃ aggahetvā pañhāvicayavissajjanavicaye tāva vibhajanto‘‘ yathā kiṃ bhave’’ tiādimāha. "
1043146,191,472,30,47,1,117,15,"Tattha yathā kiṃ {bhave}ti yena pakārena so pañhāvicayo pavattetabbo, taṃ pakārajātaṃ kīdisaṃ bhaveyyāti attho daṭṭhabbo. "
1043147,191,472,48,64,1,122,15,"Āyasmā ajito pārāyane bhagavantaṃ pañhaṃ yathā yena pakārena pucchati, tathā tena pakārena pañhāvicayo pavattetabboti attho. "
1043148,191,472,65,69,1,27,3,Tattha {āyasmā}ti piyavacanaṃ. 
1043149,191,472,70,77,1,70,6,{Ajito}ti bāvarībrāhmaṇassa paricārakabhūtānaṃ soḷasannaṃ aññataro ajito. 
1043150,191,472,78,89,1,100,9,"{Pārāyane}ti pāraṃ nibbānaṃ ayati gacchati etenāti pārāyanaṃ, ajitasuttādisoḷasasuttassetaṃ adhivacanaṃ."
1043151,191,473,2,12,1,19,4,"‘ ‘ Kenassu nivuto loko,( iccāyasmā ajito,) "
1043152,191,474,2,4,1,19,2,Kenassu nappakāsati; 
1043153,191,475,2,28,1,49,7,"Kissābhilepanaṃ brūsi, kiṃ su tassa mahabbhayan’’ ti.( su. ni.1038; cūḷani. vatthugāthā57, ajitamāṇavapucchāniddesa1)– "
1043154,191,476,2,19,1,89,12,"Gāthāya ‘‘ kena dhammena loko ariyavajjo satto nivuto paṭicchādito, iti āyasmā ajito pucchati. "
1043155,191,476,20,44,1,165,20,"Kena hetunā yathāvuttaloko nappakāsati, assa yathāvuttalokassa kiṃ abhilepanaṃ iti tvaṃ brūsi, tassa yathāvuttalokassa kiṃ mahabbhayanti tvaṃ brūsīti pucchatī’’ ti attho. "
1043156,191,477,2,50,1,289,36,"Iti iminā pabhedena cattāri imāni gāthāpāda padāni pucchitāni pucchāvasena vuttāni, pucchitatthadīpakāni vā, padhānavasena pana so‘‘ eko pañho’’ ti mato, yadipi catunnaṃ padānaṃ pucchanavasena pavattattā catubbidhoti vattabbo, ñātuṃ pana icchitassa ekasseva atthassa sambhavato‘‘ eko pañho’’ ti vuttaṃ."
1043157,191,477,51,66,1,62,7,‘‘ Kāraṇaṃ vadehī’’ ti vattabbattā kāraṇamāha‘‘ ekavatthupariggahā’’ ti. 
1043158,191,477,67,70,1,16,3,Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti–
1043159,191,477,71,95,1,169,17,"‘‘ yadipi nivāraṇāpakāsanābhilepanamahabbhayasaṅkhātā cattāro atthā pucchāyaṃ gahitā, ekassa pana abhidheyyatthassa gahaṇato‘ eko pañho’ ti padhānavasena gahitoti daṭṭhabbo’’ ti."
1043160,191,477,96,114,1,89,10,‘‘ Ekavatthupariggahaṇaṃ kathaṃ amhehi saddahitabban’’ ti vattabbabhāvato‘‘ evañhi āhā’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1043161,191,477,115,129,1,118,13,"Evaṃ ekavatthupariggahaṇeneva bhagavā hi yasmā āha, iti tasmā ekavatthupariggahaṇaṃ tumhehi saddahitabbanti vuttaṃ hoti."
1043162,191,478,2,17,1,90,11,"‘ ‘ Kenassu nivuto loko’’ ti iminā lokādhiṭṭhānaṃ paṭicchādanaṃ pucchati, na nānādhammādhiṭṭhānaṃ."
1043163,191,478,18,32,1,83,9,"‘‘ Kenassu nappakāsatī’’ ti iminā lokasseva appakāsanaṃ pucchati, na nānāsabhāvadhammassa."
1043164,191,478,33,47,1,85,9,"‘‘ Kissābhilepanaṃ brūsī’’ ti iminā lokasseva abhilepanaṃ pucchati, na nānāsabhāvadhammassa."
1043165,191,478,48,65,1,94,12,"‘‘ Kiṃ su tassa mahabbhayan’’ ti iminā tasseva lokassa mahabbhayaṃ pucchati, na nānāsabhāvadhammassa. "
1043166,191,478,66,86,1,208,14,"Tasmā‘‘ kenassu nivuto loko’’ tiādipañho ekādhiṭṭhānanānādhiṭṭhānesu ekādhiṭṭhāno, dhammādhiṭṭhānasattādhiṭṭhānesu sattādhiṭṭhāno, adiṭṭhajotanādīsu adiṭṭhajotanāpañhotiādinā yathāsambhavaṃ vicinitabboti adhippāyo."
1043167,191,479,2,28,1,99,16,"‘ ‘ Pañhassa yo loko‘ adhiṭṭhāno’ ti gahito, so loko tividho’’ ti vattabbabhāvato‘‘ loko tividho’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1043168,191,479,29,35,1,42,6,Tattha tayo vidhā etassa lokassāti tividho. 
1043169,191,479,36,50,1,97,11,"Kilissati rāgādivasena kāmāvacarasattoti kileso, kileso ca so loko cāti kilesaloko, kāmāvacarasatto. "
1043170,191,479,51,55,1,41,4,So hi rāgādikilesabahulatāya kilesalokoti. 
1043171,191,479,56,69,1,86,11,"Bhavati jhānābhiññāhi buddhīhīti bhavo, bhavo ca so loko cāti bhavaloko, rūpāvacarasatto. "
1043172,191,479,70,74,1,31,4,So hi jhānādibuddhīhi bhavatīti. 
1043173,191,479,75,87,1,84,10,"Indriyena samannāgatoti indriyo, indriyo ca so loko cāti indriyaloko, arūpāvacarasatto. "
1043174,191,479,88,101,1,119,12,"So hi āneñjasamādhibahulatāya visuddhindriyo hotīti lokasamaññā pariyāpannadhammavasena pavattā, tasmā ariyā na gahitāti."
1043175,191,480,2,39,1,186,23,"‘ ‘ Kenassu nivuto loko’’ tiādigāthāya pucchāvicayo hāro ācariyena vibhatto, amhehi ca ñāto,‘‘ vissajjanāvicayo hāro kattha vissajjanāya vibhatto’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha vissajjanā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1043176,191,480,40,52,1,58,7,Tattha {tatthā}ti tassaṃ‘‘ kenassu nivuto loko’’ tiādipucchāyaṃ–
1043177,191,481,2,12,1,20,4,"‘ ‘ Avijjāya nivuto loko,( ajitāti bhagavā,) "
1043178,191,482,2,5,1,27,3,Vivicchā pamādā nappakāsati; 
1043179,191,483,2,25,1,48,5,"Jappābhilepanaṃ brūmi, dukkhamassa mahabbhayan’’ ti.( su. ni.1039; cūḷani. vatthugāthā58, ajitamāṇavapucchāniddesa)– "
1043180,191,484,2,6,1,33,4,Ayaṃ gāthā vissajjanāti daṭṭhabbā. 
1043181,191,484,7,31,1,247,20,"Tattha avijjāya nivuto {loko}ti kāḷapakkhacatuddasī, ghanavanasaṇḍa, meghapaṭalacchādana, aḍḍharattīnaṃ vasena caturaṅgasamannāgatena andhakārena rathaghaṭādi paṭicchādito viya dhammasabhāvapaṭicchādanalakkhaṇāya avijjāya satta loko nivuto paṭicchādito."
1043182,191,484,32,43,1,38,7,‘‘ Ajitā’’ ti ca ālapanaṃ katvā bhagavā āha. 
1043183,191,484,44,51,1,62,6,{Vivicchā}ti vici kicchāya pamādahetu yathāvuttaloko nappakāsati. 
1043184,191,484,52,82,1,177,21,"Jappaṃ taṇhaṃ yathāvuttalokassa‘‘ abhilepanan’’ ti ahaṃ brūmīti bhagavā āha, dukkhaṃ jātiādivaṭṭadukkhaṃ assa yathāvuttalokassa‘‘ mahabbhayan’’ ti ahaṃ brūmīti bhagavā ajitaṃ āhāti attho."
1043185,191,485,2,21,1,88,12,‘ ‘ Imāya vissajjanāya kathaṃ vicineyyā’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ imāni cattāri padānī’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1043186,191,485,22,37,1,90,10,Tattha imāni cattāri {padānī}ti‘‘ kenassu nivuto loko’’ tiādipucchāgāthāyaṃ vuttāni gāthāpadāni. 
1043187,191,485,38,54,1,97,11,Imehi catūhi {padehī}ti‘‘ avijjāya nivuto loko’’ ti vissajjanāgāthāyaṃ vuttehi gāthāpadehi vissajjitāni. 
1043188,191,485,55,56,1,6,1,Kathaṃ? 
1043189,191,485,57,78,1,137,17,"Paṭhamaṃ padaṃ paṭhamena padena, dutiyaṃ padaṃ dutiyena padena, tatiyaṃ padaṃ tatiyena padena, catutthaṃ padaṃ catutthena padena vissajjitaṃ."
1043190,191,486,2,26,1,100,16,"‘ ‘ Kenassu nivuto loko’’ ti paṭhama pañhe‘‘ avijjāya nivuto loko’’ ti paṭhamā vissajjanā katā, na uppaṭipāṭiyā. "
1043191,191,486,27,36,1,62,8,"Vijjāya paṭipakkhā avijjā, tasmā avijjāya ajānako loko bhaveyya. "
1043192,191,486,37,49,1,58,8,Kathaṃ nivuto saddahitabboti āha‘‘ nīvaraṇehi nivuto loko’’ ti. 
1043193,191,486,50,76,1,117,17,Yadi evaṃ‘‘ nīvaraṇena nivuto loko’’ ti vissajjanā kātabbāti codanaṃ manasi katvā vuttaṃ‘‘ avijjānīvaraṇā hi sabbe sattā’’ ti.
1043194,191,486,77,96,1,105,11,‘‘ Sabbasattānaṃ avijjānīvaraṇabhāvo kena vacanena saddahitabbo’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ yathāha bhagavā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ.
1043195,191,487,2,18,1,101,11,"‘ ‘ Sabbasattānaṃ, bhikkhave, sabbapāṇānaṃ sabbabhūtānaṃ, pariyāyato ekameva nīvaraṇaṃ vadāmi, yadidaṃ avijjā. "
1043196,191,487,19,23,1,29,4,Avijjānīvaraṇā hi sabbe sattā. 
1043197,191,487,24,55,1,235,28,"Sabbasova bhikkhave avijjāya nirodhā cāgā paṭinissaggā natthi sattānaṃ nīvaraṇanti vadāmī’’ ti yaṃ vacanaṃ yathā yena pakārena bhagavā āha, tathā tena pakārena vuttena tena vacanena tumhehi sabbasattānaṃ avijjānīvaraṇabhāvo saddahitabboti."
1043198,191,488,2,46,1,193,28,"‘ ‘ Avijjāya nivuto loko’’ ti padena‘‘ kenassu nivuto loko’’ ti paṭhamasseva padassa vissajjanā na siyā,‘‘ kenassu nappakāsatī’’ ti dutiyapadassāpi vissajjanā siyāti codanaṃ manasi katvā‘‘ tena cā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1043199,191,488,47,95,1,225,31,"Tattha tena‘‘ avijjāya nivuto loko’’ ti padena‘‘ kenassu nivuto loko’’ ti paṭhamassa padassa vissajjanā yuttā yuttatarā hoti, yuttatarattā‘‘ kenassu nivuto loko’’ ti pañhe‘‘ avijjāya nivuto loko’’ ti vissajjanāti mayā vattabbāyevāti adhippāyo."
1043200,191,489,2,31,1,148,20,"‘ ‘ Kenassu nappakāsatī’’ ti imasmiṃ pañhe‘‘ vivicchā pamādā nappakāsatī’’ ti ayaṃ vissajjanā kātabbā, vivicchāya pavattattā, pamādā ca loko nappakāsatīti attho. "
1043201,191,489,32,60,1,159,19,"Avijjānīvaraṇāya nivuto loko nappakāsatīti vissajjanā kātabbā,‘‘ kathaṃ vivicchā pamādā loko nappakāsatīti vissajjanā katā’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ yo puggalo’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1043202,191,489,61,75,1,107,12,"Tattha yo puthujjanabhūto puggalo avijjā nīvaraṇehi nivuto, so puthujjanabhūto puggalo vivicchāya vivicchati."
1043203,191,489,76,100,1,111,15,"‘‘ Yāya vivicchāya vivicchati, sā vivicchā katamā nāmā’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ vivicchā nāma vuccati vicikicchā’’ ti vuttaṃ."
1043204,191,489,101,118,1,68,9,‘‘ Tāya kasmā nappakāsatī’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ so vicikicchanto’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1043205,191,489,119,126,1,75,7,Tāya vicikicchanto so puthujjanabhūto puggalo saddahitabbesu nābhisaddahati; 
