1043482,191,549,86,106,1,171,17,"Atha vā nānāvajjanūpacārañāṇaṃ vā paṭisandhiñāṇaṃ vā mūlaṃ assāti ñāṇamūlako, upacārañāṇaṃ pubbaṅgamaṃ assāti ñāṇapubbaṅgamo, appanāñāṇaṃ anuparivatti assāti ñāṇānuparivatti . "
