1043525,191,559,4,41,1,251,33,"Tassāyaṃ attho– idha sāsane ye arahanto saṅkhatadhammā honti, puthū bahūyeva satta janā sekkhā sīlādisikkhamānā honti, tesaṃ arahantāvañceva sekkhānañca iriyaṃ paṭipattiṃ meṃ mahā puṭṭho nipako tvaṃ bhagavā pabrūhi mārisa iti āyasmā ajito pucchanto āhāti. "
1043526,191,560,2,22,1,71,9,15. Tassaṃ gāthāyaṃ‘‘ kittakāni pucchitānī’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ imānī’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
