1043531,191,561,2,49,1,251,33,"‘ ‘ Ye ca saṅkhatadhammāse’’ ti iminā asekkhānaṃ arahattaṃ pucchati,‘‘ ye ca sekkhā puthū idhā’’ ti iminā sekkhāsekkhānaṃ sekkhasikkhanaṃ pucchati,‘‘ tesaṃ me nipako iriyaṃ, puṭṭho pabrūhi mārisā’’ ti iminā sekkhāsekkhānaṃ vipassanā pubbabhāge tadaṅgappahānaṃ pucchati."
