1043589,191,571,91,108,1,148,16,Tattha evaṃ pañcindriyānaṃ nibbattidassanena sekho puggalo sabbehi kusalehi dhammehi appamattoti bhagavatā vutto thomito anāvilatāya manasāti yojanā.
1043590,191,571,109,129,1,95,12,‘‘ Sekkhassa anāvilatā kena saddahitabbā’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ tenāha bhagavā manasānāvilo siyā’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
