1043628,191,577,11,68,1,435,45,"Yā {parijānanā}tiādīsu‘‘ idaṃ anavajjaṃ kusalaṃ, idaṃ sāvajjaṃ akusalaṃ, idaṃ akusalavipākajanakaṃ sāvajjaṃ, idaṃ kusalavipākajanakaṃ anavajjaṃ, idaṃ saṃkiliṭṭhaṃ kaṇhaṃ, idaṃ asaṃkiliṭṭhaṃ sukkaṃ, idaṃ kusalaṃ anavajjādikaṃ sevitabbaṃ, idaṃ akusalaṃ sāvajjādikaṃ na sevitabban’’ ti evaṃ aniccādito kalāpasammasanādivasena gahitā sammasitā ime vipassanāya ārammaṇabhūtā saṅkhata dhammā idaṃ udayabbayañāṇādiphalaṃ ānisaṃsaṃ anukkamena nibbattāpenti. "
