1043669,191,588,39,60,1,191,19,"Tattha imassa {suttassā}ti yaṃ suttaṃ vicinituṃ niddhāritaṃ, imassa suttassa catusaccavinimuttassa suttatthassa abhāvato sabbāni saccāni tasseva suttassa ādimajjhapariyosāne passitabbānīti attho. "
