1043671,191,589,16,39,1,118,13,‘‘ Na yathāvuttapucchādīnaṃ pavicetabbabhāvo amhehi jānitabbo saddahitabbo’’ ti vattabbabhāvato‘‘ tenāha… pe… anugītī’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1043672,191,589,40,69,1,198,22,"Tattha tena yathāvuttapucchādīnaṃ vicetabbabhāvena āyasmā mahākaccāno‘‘ yaṃ pucchitañca… pe… anugītī’’ tiādikaṃ yaṃ vacanaṃ āha, tena vacanena vicetabbabhāvo tumhehi jānitabbo saddahitabbovāti vuttaṃ hoti."
1043673,191,590,2,30,1,139,20,"‘ ‘ Yathāvuttappakāro ca vicayo hāro paripuṇṇo kiṃ, udāhu aññopi niddhāretvā yojetabbo atthi kin’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ niyutto vicayo hāro’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
1043674,191,590,31,45,1,174,12,"Tattha pucchāvicayavissajjanavicayapubbāparavicayaanugītivicayasuttavicayā sarūpato vibhattā, tehi avaseso assādādivicayopi yathārahaṃ niddhāretvā yutto yuñjitabboti adhippāyo. "
1043675,191,591,2,5,1,45,4,Iti vicayahāravibhaṅge sattibalānurūpā racitā 
1043676,191,592,2,4,1,18,2,Vibhāvanā niṭṭhitā. 
1043677,191,593,2,9,1,84,7,Paṇḍitehi pana aṭṭhakathāṭīkānusārena gambhīrattho vitthārato vibhajitvā gahetabboti.
1043678,191,594,2,4,1,26,2,3 . Yuttihāravibhaṅgavibhāvanā 
1043679,191,595,2,34,1,210,19,"18. Yena yena saṃvaṇṇanāvisesabhūtena vicayahāravibhaṅgena padapañhādayo vicitā, so saṃvaṇṇanāvisesabhūto vicayahāravibhaṅgo paripuṇṇo,‘‘ katamo yuttihāravibhaṅgo’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha katamo yuttihāro’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1043680,191,595,35,47,1,109,11,Tattha {tatthā}ti tesu niddiṭṭhesu soḷasasu hāresu katamo saṃvaṇṇanāviseso yuttihāro yuttihāravibhaṅgoti pucchi.
1043681,191,595,48,68,1,132,12,‘‘ Sabbesaṃ hārānan’’ tiādiniddesassa idāni vuccamāno‘‘ ayaṃ yuttihāro’’ tiādiko vitthārasaṃvaṇṇanāviseso yuttihāravibhaṅgo nāmāti viññeyyo. 
1043682,191,595,69,87,1,61,7,Tena vuttaṃ‘‘ tattha katamo yuttihārotiādi yuttihāravibhaṅgo’’ ti( netti. aṭṭha.18). 
1043683,191,595,88,100,1,94,10,Ayaṃ yuttihāro kiṃ nāma suttatthaṃ yuttāyuttivasena {yojayatī}ti yuñjitabbaṃ suttatthaṃ pucchati. 
1043684,191,595,101,110,1,75,8,"Suttattho pana duvidho atathākārena gayhamāno, tathākārena gayhamāno atthoti. "
1043685,191,595,111,123,1,116,11,"Tattha atathākārena gayhamānova attho yāthāvato yuttiniddhāraṇena yojetabbo, itaro pana bhūtakathanamattena yojetabbo. "
1043686,191,595,124,149,1,182,20,"Yasmā panāyaṃ yuttigavesanā nāma saṃvaṇṇanā mahāpadesehi vinā na sambhavati, tasmā yuttihāraṃ vibhajanto tassa yuttihārassa lakkhaṇaṃ paṭhamaṃ upadisituṃ‘‘ cattāro mahāpadesā’’ tiādimāha. "
1043687,191,595,150,164,1,112,12,"Tattha {mahāpadesā}ti mahante buddhādayo apadisitvā vuttāni kāraṇāni, mahantāni vā dhammassa apadesāni patiṭṭhānāni. "
1043688,191,595,165,173,1,68,7,"Apadisīyateti apadeso, buddho apadeso etassa kāraṇassāti buddhāpadeso. "
1043689,191,595,174,178,1,27,4,Sesesupi eseva nayo netabbo.
1043690,191,595,179,203,1,167,18,"‘‘ Buddhassa sammukhā etaṃ suttaṃ mayā sutan’’ ti vatvā ābhatassa ganthassa suttavinayehi saṃsandanaṃ dhammo, asaṃsandanaṃ adhammoti vinicchayakāraṇaṃ mahāpadesoti adhippāyo."
1043691,191,595,204,247,1,330,34,"‘‘ Buddhassa sammukhā mayā ābhataṃ, saṅghassa sammukhā mayā ābhataṃ, sambahulattherānaṃ sammukhā mayā ābhataṃ, ekattherassa sammukhā mayā ābhatan’’ ti vatvā ābhatassa ganthassa yāni byañjanapadaatthapadāni santi, tāni padabyañjanāni bhagavatā desite sutte otarayitabbāni anuppavesitāni, vinaye rāgādivinaye sandassayitabbāni saṃsandetabbāni. "
1043692,191,595,248,251,1,46,3,Dhammatāyaṃ upanikkhipitabbāni pakkhipitabbāni. 
1043693,191,595,252,271,1,153,16,"Yadi suttatthena, vinayatthena, dhammatāya ca aviruddhāni honti, evaṃ sati tava ābhatapadabyañjanāni yuttānīti vinicchayantehi vatvā gahetabbānīti adhippāyo. "
1043694,191,596,2,31,1,185,18,"Suttavinayadhammatāsu otarayitabbāni sandassayitabbāni upanikkhipitabbānīti ācariyena vuttāni,‘‘ kattha sutte, kattha vinaye, kattha dhammatāyan’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ katamasmiṃ sutte’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1043695,191,596,32,40,1,71,7,Tattha catūsu {ariyasaccesū}ti catunnaṃ ariyasaccānaṃ dassanakesu suttesu. 
1043696,191,596,41,50,1,64,8,"Rāgo vinassati vūpasamati etena asubhādināti rāgavinayaṃ, kiṃ taṃ? "
1043697,191,596,51,60,1,50,7,"Asubhādinimittaṃ, taṃ assa atthīti rāgavinayo, ko so? "
1043698,191,596,61,63,1,39,2,Asubhādinimittadassanako suttantaviseso. 
1043699,191,596,64,68,1,28,3,Esa nayo {dosavinayo}tiādīsupi. 
1043700,191,596,69,83,1,203,12,Paṭiccasamuppādo nāma sassatadiṭṭhiucchedadiṭṭhiṃ vivajjetvā ekattanayādīnaṃ dīpanena avijjādisaṅkhārādisabhāvadhammānaṃ paccayapaccayuppannabhāvadīpakoti vuttaṃ‘‘ katamissaṃ dhammatāyaṃ upanikkhipitabbāni? 
1043701,191,596,84,88,1,19,2,Paṭiccasamuppāde’’ ti.
1043702,191,597,2,23,1,92,13,‘ ‘ Suttādīsu avatarante sandissante avilomente kiṃ na janetī’’ ti vattabbato‘‘ catūsū’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1043703,191,597,24,47,1,136,18,"Tattha‘‘ buddhādīnaṃ sammukhā mayā ābhatan’’ ti vatvā ābhatagantho catūsu ariyasaccesu yadi avatarati, evaṃ sati ābhatagantho āsave na janeti. "
1043704,191,597,48,58,1,73,9,"Rāgādikilesavinaye yadi sandissati, evaṃ sati ābhatagantho āsave na janeti. "
1043705,191,597,59,72,1,85,12,"Dhammatañca yadi na vilometi, evaṃ sati ābhatagantho āsave na janetīti attho daṭṭhabbo."
1043706,191,598,2,20,1,99,11,‘ ‘ Kimatthaṃ yuttihāravibhaṅge cattāro mahāpadesā ābhatā’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ catūhi mahāpadesehī’’ tiādimāha. 
1043707,191,598,21,45,1,164,22,"Tattha ābhataganthe yaṃ yaṃ atthajātaṃ, yaṃ yaṃ dhammajātaṃ vā catūhi mahāpadesehi yujjati, taṃ taṃ atthajātaṃ vā taṃ taṃ dhammajātaṃ vā saṃvaṇṇetabbasutte gahetabbaṃ. "
1043708,191,598,46,60,1,112,13,"Yena yena kāraṇena ca catūhi mahāpadesehi yujjati, taṃ taṃ kāraṇaṃ saṃvaṇṇanāvasena saṃvaṇṇetabbasutte gahetabbaṃ. "
1043709,191,598,61,74,1,107,12,"Yathā yathā pakārena catūhi mahāpadesehi yujjati, so so pakāro saṃvaṇṇanāvasena saṃvaṇṇetabbasutte gahetabbo. "
1043710,191,598,75,81,1,50,6,Evaṃ gāhaṇatthaṃ cattāro mahāpadesā ābhatāti attho. 
1043711,191,599,2,35,1,171,20,"19. Catūhi mahāpadesehi yuttaṃ aviruddhaṃ taṃ taṃ atthajātaṃ gahetabbanti ācariyena vuttaṃ,‘‘ kattha kena yuttiniddhāraṇaṃ kātabban’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ pañhaṃ pucchitenā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1043712,191,599,36,42,1,61,6,Pañhe pañhaṃ pucchitena puggalena yuttiniddhāraṇaṃ kātabbanti. 
