1043718,191,599,88,106,1,126,16,"Tattha sabbāni {padānī}ti pucchitapāṭhe niravasesāni padāni ekaṃ samānaṃ atthaṃ yadi abhivadanti, evaṃ sati atthavasena eko pañho. "
