1043731,191,603,19,27,1,40,4,‘‘ Katamā vissajjanagāthā’’ ti pucchitabbattā–
1043732,191,604,2,10,1,38,5,"‘ ‘ Maccunābbhāhato loko, jarāya parivārito; "
