1043735,191,606,2,3,1,6,1,Vuttaṃ . 
1043736,191,606,4,50,1,364,42,"Tassaṃ vissajjanagāthāyaṃ– coraghātakena manussena coro abbhāhato viya maccunā satta loko sadā abbhāhato, māluvalatāya attano nissitarukkho parivārito ajjhotthaṭo viya jarāya satta loko sadā parivārito ajjhotthaṭo, visappītakhurappena sallena otiṇṇo anupaviṭṭho viya taṇhāsallena satta loko sadā otiṇṇo anupaviṭṭho, icchāya satta loko sadā dhūpāyito santāpitoti yojanā. "
1043737,191,607,2,24,1,69,10,"20.‘‘ Katamaṃ maccu, katamā jarā’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha jarā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1043738,191,607,25,30,1,41,4,Tattha {tatthā}ti tissaṃ vissajjanagāthāyaṃ. 
1043739,191,607,31,54,1,183,21,"Dutiyapade vuttā jarā ca paṭhamapade vuttaṃ maraṇa ñca imāni dve saṅkhatassa khandhapañcakassa saṅkhatalakkhaṇāni honti, saṅkhataṃ khandhapañcakaṃ muñcitvā visuṃ na upalabbhatīti attho."
1043740,191,607,55,74,1,102,11,‘‘ Saṅkhatalakkhaṇānaṃ jarāmaraṇānaṃ kathaṃ bhedo jānitabbo’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ jarāyaṃ ṭhitassā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1043741,191,607,75,91,1,123,14,"Tattha jarāyaṃ ṭhitassa aññathattan ti ṭhitassa khandhappabandhassa yaṃ aññathattaṃ, ayaṃ pākaṭajarā nāma, na khaṇaṭṭhitijarā. "
1043742,191,607,92,104,1,82,9,"Maraṇaṃ {vayo}ti sammutimaraṇaṃ cutiyeva hoti, na khaṇikamaraṇaṃ, na samucchedamaraṇaṃ. "
1043743,191,607,105,142,1,77,10,"Tena vuttaṃ‘‘ uppādo paññāyati, vayo paññāyati, ṭhitassa aññathattaṃ paññāyatī’’ ti( saṃ. ni.3.38; a. ni.3.47; kathā.214). "
1043744,191,608,2,37,1,170,25,"Yadi ṭhitasseva maraṇaṃ siyā, evaṃ sati jarāmaraṇānaṃ nānattaṃ yuttaṃ na siyā, ayutte sati‘‘ te tayo pañhā’’ ti vacanampi ayuttamevāti vattabbato‘‘ tattha jarāya cā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1043745,191,608,38,52,1,105,13,Tattha {tatthā}ti tissaṃ vissajjanagāthāyaṃ vuttāya jarāya ca vuttassa maraṇassa ca atthato nānattaṃ yuttaṃ.
1043746,191,609,2,25,1,112,15,"‘ ‘ Kena kāraṇena yuttaṃ, kathaṃ kāraṇena nānattaṃ sampaṭicchitabban’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ gabbhagatāpi hi mīyantī’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
1043747,191,609,26,37,1,82,10,"Jaraṃ appattā gabbhagatāpi sattā hi yasmā mīyanti, tasmā nānattaṃ sampaṭicchitabbaṃ."
1043748,191,609,38,58,1,82,12,‘‘ Gabbhagatāpi jarappattā bhaveyyun’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ na ca te jiṇṇā bhavantī’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1043749,191,609,59,78,1,163,17,"Jarappattāpi ajiṇṇattā jiṇṇajaraṃ appattāva mīyanti, evaṃ idhādhippetassa jiṇṇajarāvirahitassa maraṇassa sambhavato aññā jarā, aññaṃ maraṇanti ñātabbanti vuttaṃ hoti."
1043750,191,609,79,105,1,124,16,"‘‘ Na gabbhagatānaṃyeva jiṇṇajaraṃ appattaṃ maraṇaṃ atthi, aññesampi atthī’’ ti vattabbabhāvato ‘‘ atthi ca devānaṃ maraṇan’’ ti vuttaṃ."
1043751,191,609,106,128,1,101,14,‘‘ Devāpi cirakālasambhavato jaraṃ pattā bhaveyyun’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ na ca tesaṃ sarīrāni jīrantī’’ ti vuttaṃ.
1043752,191,609,129,150,1,105,13,‘‘ Jarāmaraṇānaṃ nānatte kāraṇaṃ ettakamevā’’ ti vattabbattā aññampi atthīti dassetuṃ‘‘ sakkate vā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1043753,191,609,151,170,1,161,17,"Tattha jiṇṇajarāya paṭikammaṃ kātuṃ sakkateva, maraṇassa pana paṭikammassa kātuṃ na sakkateva, imināpi kāraṇena jarāmaraṇānaṃ nānattaṃ sampaṭicchitabbamevāti attho."
1043754,191,609,171,204,1,196,24,"‘‘ Na sakkate maraṇassa paṭikammaṃ kātun’’ ti kasmā vuttaṃ, nanu iddhipādabhāvanāya vasībhāve sati sakkā maraṇassāpi paṭikammaṃ kātunti codanaṃ manasi katvā‘‘ aññatreva iddhimantānaṃ iddhivisayā’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
1043755,191,610,2,36,1,180,23,"Jarāmaraṇānaṃ aññamaññaṃ nānābhāvo ācariyena dassito, amhehi ca ñāto,‘‘ kathaṃ pana taṇhāya jarāmaraṇehi nānābhāvo’’ ti vattabbato tehi taṇhāya nānattaṃ dassetuṃ‘‘ yaṃ panāhā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1043756,191,610,37,50,1,120,12,"Taṇhāya avijjamānāyapi jīrantāpi mīyantāpi vītarāgā yasmā dissanti, tasmā taṇhāya jarāmaraṇehi nānābhāvo sampaṭicchitabbo."
1043757,191,611,2,28,1,131,19,‘ ‘ Taṇhāya jīraṇabhijjanalakkhaṇaṃ atthīti tehi taṇhāya anaññatte ko nāma doso siyā’’ ti vattabbato dosaṃ dassetuṃ‘‘ yadi cā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1043758,191,611,29,39,1,100,9,"Jarāmaraṇaṃ yathā yena jīraṇabhijjanalakkhaṇena pākaṭaṃ, evaṃ jīraṇabhijjanalakkhaṇena taṇhāpi pākaṭā. "
1043759,191,611,40,43,1,12,3,Yadi ca siyā; 
1043760,191,611,44,59,1,106,13,"evaṃ sante yobbanaṭṭhāpi sabbe māṇavā vigatataṇhā siyuṃ, na ca vigatataṇhā, tasmā nānābhāvo sampaṭicchitabbo. "
1043761,191,611,60,75,1,76,11,Tato aññopi doso āpajjeyyāti dassetuṃ‘‘ yathā ca taṇhā dukkhassā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1043762,191,611,76,90,1,123,13,"Tattha jarāmaraṇānaṃ taṇhāya anaññatte sati taṇhāya bhavataṇhāya dukkhasamudayo hoti, evaṃ jarāmaraṇampi dukkhasamudayo siyā. "
1043763,191,611,91,101,1,82,9,"Yasmā na jarāmaraṇaṃ dukkhasamudayo, tasmā jarāmaraṇehi taṇhāya nānattaṃ veditabbaṃ. "
1043764,191,612,2,20,1,98,14,Tehi tāya anaññatte sati evampi doso āpajjeyyāti dassetuṃ‘‘ yathā ca taṇhā maggavajjhā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1043765,191,612,21,35,1,97,13,"Tattha tehi tāya anaññatte sati yathā taṇhā maggavajjhā hoti, evaṃ jarāmaraṇampi maggavajjhaṃ siyā. "
1043766,191,612,36,59,1,163,20,"Yathā jarāmaraṇaṃ maggavajjhaṃ na hoti, evaṃ taṇhāpi maggavajjhā na siyā, tathā ca na hoti pahātabbāpahātabbabhāvato, tasmāpi jarāmaraṇehi taṇhāya nānattaṃ veditabbaṃ."
1043767,191,613,2,31,1,173,21,‘ ‘ Yadi cātiādinā vuttāya yuttiyā upapattiyā eva jarāmaraṇehi taṇhāya aññattaṃ gavesitabban’’ ti vattabbattā aññehipi kāraṇehi gavesitabbanti dassetuṃ‘‘ imāya yuttiyā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1043768,191,613,32,49,1,81,12,Tattha imāya {yuttiyā}ti yā yutti‘‘ yadi cā’’ tiādinā vuttāya imāya yuttiyā upapattiyā. 
1043769,191,613,50,61,1,110,11,Aññamaññehi kāraṇehi aññehi aññehi kāraṇabhūtehi upapattīhi jarāmaraṇehi taṇhāya aññattaṃ gavesitabbanti attho.
1043770,191,613,62,91,1,146,19,"‘‘ Aññamaññehi kāraṇehi gavesitabban’’ ti kasmā vuttaṃ, nanu yuttiyā, atthato ca aññattaṃ sandissatīti codanaṃ manasi katvā‘‘ yadi ca sandissatī’’ tiādimāha. "
