1043943,191,661,2,9,1,84,7,Paṇḍitehi pana aṭṭhakathāṭīkānusārena gambhīrattho vitthārato vibhajitvā gahetabboti.
1043944,191,662,2,4,1,29,2,5 . Lakkhaṇahāravibhaṅgavibhāvanā 
1043945,191,663,2,37,1,236,21,"23. Yena yena saṃvaṇṇanāvisesabhūtena padaṭṭhānavibhaṅgena avijjādīnaṃ padaṭṭhānāni vibhattāni, so saṃvaṇṇanāvisesabhūto padaṭṭhānahāravibhaṅgo paripuṇṇo,‘‘ katamo lakkhaṇahāravibhaṅgo’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha katamo lakkhaṇo hāro’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1043946,191,663,38,43,1,36,5,Tattha tattha -saddassa attho vuttova. 
1043947,191,663,44,50,1,69,6,Katamo saṃvaṇṇanāviseso lakkhaṇo hāro lakkhaṇahāravibhaṅgoti pucchati.
1043948,191,663,51,74,1,153,15,‘‘ Vuttamhi ekadhamme’’ tiādiniddesassa idāni mayā vuccamāno‘‘ ye dhammā’’ tiādiko vitthārasaṃvaṇṇanāviseso lakkhaṇo hāro lakkhaṇahāravibhaṅgo nāmāti viññeyyoti. 
1043949,191,663,75,77,1,11,2,Tena vuttaṃ–
1043950,191,663,78,96,1,61,7,‘‘ tattha katamo lakkhaṇo hārotiādi lakkhaṇahāravibhaṅgo nāmā’’ ti( netti. aṭṭha.23). 
1043951,191,663,97,125,1,210,24,Ayaṃ idāni vuccamāno vitthārabhūto lakkhaṇo hāro piṭakattaye desitesu dhammesu kiṃ nāma lakkhitabbaṃ dhammaṃ lakkhīyatīti pucchitvā pucchite lakkhaṇahāravicaye dhamme saṅkhepena dassetuṃ‘‘ ye dhammā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1043952,191,663,126,133,1,35,6,Tattha ye {dhammā}ti ye samūhā dhammā. 
1043953,191,663,134,137,1,28,2,{Ekalakkhaṇā}ti samānalakkhaṇā. 
1043954,191,663,138,147,1,75,8,"Tesaṃ dhammānan ti samānalakkhaṇānaṃ tesaṃ samūhadhammānaṃ, niddhāraṇe cetaṃ. "
1043955,191,663,148,167,1,160,16,"Ekasmiṃ {dhamme}ti samānalakkhaṇe ekasmiṃ dhamme, pāḷiyaṃ bhagavatā vutte sati vuttadhammato avasiṭṭhasamānalakkhaṇā dhammā samānalakkhaṇena vuttā bhavantīti attho. "
1043956,191,664,2,23,1,148,17,Lakkhaṇahāravisaye dhamme vitthārato imasmiṃ dhamme vutte ime samānalakkhaṇā dhammāpi vuttā bhavantīti niyametvā dassetuṃ‘‘ yathā kiṃ bhave’’ tiādimāha. 
1043957,191,664,24,37,1,75,11,"Tassattho– yathā yena pakārena vuttā bhavanti, so pakāro kiṃ bhaveti pucchati. "
1043958,191,664,38,50,1,81,11,"Yathā yena pakārena vuttā bhavanti, so pakāro samānalakkhaṇāti bhāvo bhaveti attho. "
1043959,191,664,51,54,1,17,3,Kinti bhagavā āha?
1043960,191,664,55,64,1,37,5,‘‘ Cakkhuṃ bhikkhave’’ tiādiṃ bhagavā āha.
1043961,191,664,65,88,1,109,11,"‘‘ Cakkhuṃ, bhikkhave, anavaṭṭhitan’’ tiādimhi vutte‘‘ sotaṃ, bhikkhave, anavaṭṭhitan’’ tiādivacanampi vuttameva bhavati."
1043962,191,665,2,28,1,208,19,‘ ‘ Anavaṭṭhitādilakkhaṇena samānalakkhaṇattā vā ajjhattikāyatanabhāvena samānalakkhaṇattā vāti āyatanavaseneva ekalakkhaṇaṃ vattabban’’ ti vattabbattā khandhavasenapi ekalakkhaṇaṃ dassetuṃ‘‘ yathā cāhā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ.
1043963,191,665,29,85,1,324,39,"‘‘ Atīte, rādha, rūpe anapekkho hoti, anāgataṃ rūpaṃ mā abhinandi , paccuppannassa rūpassa nibbidāya virāgāya nirodhāya cāgāya paṭinissaggāya paṭipajjā’’ ti vutte‘‘ atītāya, rādha, vedanāya anapekkho hoti, anāgataṃ vedanaṃ mā abhinandi, paccuppannāya vedanāya nibbidāya virāgāya nirodhāya cāgāya paṭinissaggāya paṭipajjā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ bhave."
