1044065,191,689,2,4,1,18,2,Vibhāvanā niṭṭhitā. 
1044066,191,690,2,9,1,84,7,Paṇḍitehi pana aṭṭhakathāṭīkānusārena gambhīrattho vitthārato vibhajitvā gahetabboti.
1044067,191,691,2,4,1,30,2,6 . Catubyūhahāravibhaṅgavibhāvanā 
1044068,191,692,2,36,1,234,21,"25. Yena yena saṃvaṇṇanāvisesabhūtena lakkhaṇahāravibhaṅgena suttatthehi samānatthā vibhattā, so saṃvaṇṇanāvisesabhūto lakkhaṇahāravibhaṅgo paripuṇṇo,‘‘ katamo catubyūhahāravibhaṅgo’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha katamo catubyūho hāro’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1044069,191,692,37,44,1,56,6,Tattha {tatthā}ti tesu niddiṭṭhesu soḷasasu desanāhārādīsu. 
1044070,191,692,45,54,1,85,8,{Katamo}ti katamo saṃvaṇṇanāviseso catubyūho hāro catubyūhahāravibhaṅgo nāmāti viññeyyo. 
1044071,191,692,55,57,1,11,2,Tena vuttaṃ–
1044072,191,692,58,75,1,55,6,‘‘ tattha katamo catubyūho hāroti catubyūhahāravibhaṅgo’’ ti( netti. aṭṭha.25).
1044073,191,692,76,95,1,98,10,‘‘ Iminā catubyūhahārena katamassa neruttādayo gavesitabbā’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ byañjanenā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1044074,191,692,96,128,1,244,24,"Tattha {byañjanenā}ti catubyūhahārassa suttassa visesato byañjanavicayabhāvato‘‘ byañjanā’’ ti vohāritena iminā catubyūhahārena suttassa neruttañca, suttassa adhippāyo ca, suttassa nidānañca, suttassa pubbāparasandhi ca saṃvaṇṇentehi gavesitabboti attho."
1044075,191,693,2,25,1,136,15,‘ ‘ Catubyūhahārena gavesitabbesu neruttādīsu katamaṃ suttassa gavesitabbaṃ neruttan’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha katamaṃ neruttan’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1044076,191,693,26,41,1,126,14,Tassattho– tattha tesu iminā catubyūhahārena gavesitabbesu neruttādīsu katamaṃ suttassa neruttaṃ nibbacanaṃ nāmāti ce puccheyya? 
1044077,191,693,42,55,1,118,12,"Suttassa yā nirutti niddhāretvā vuttā sabhāvapaññatti gavesitabbā, idaṃ sabhāvaniruttibhūtaṃ nibbacanaṃ neruttaṃ nāmāti."
1044078,191,693,56,79,1,91,14,"‘‘ Yā nirutti neruttaṃ nāmāti vuttā, kā pana sā niruttī’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ padasaṃhitā’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
1044079,191,693,80,84,1,32,4,Padesu saṃhitā yuttā padasaṃhitā. 
1044080,191,693,85,102,1,120,15,"Yathā yathā suttattho vattabbo, tathā tathā yā sabhāvanirutti pavattā, sā pavattā sabhāvaniruttiyeva nirutti nāmāti yojanā."
1044081,191,693,103,124,1,83,13,‘‘ Kā pana sā sabhāvaniruttī’’ ti pucchitabbattā ca‘‘ yaṃ dhammānaṃ nāmaso ñāṇan’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1044082,191,693,125,152,1,245,26,"Yaṃ yāya kāraṇabhūtāya nāmapaññattiyā dhammānaṃ neyyānaṃ nāmaso pathavīnāmādinā vā phassanāmādinā vā khandhanāmādinā vā vividhena nāmena atthadhammādīsu kusalassa puggalassa ñāṇaṃ pavattati, sā kāraṇabhūtā nāmapaññatti sabhāvanirutti nāmāti attho. "
1044083,191,693,153,160,1,37,6,"Yan ti ca liṅgavipallāso, yāyāti attho."
1044084,191,693,161,181,1,101,12,‘‘ Liṅgapakatidhammānaṃ nāmaso pavattamānaṃ ñāṇaṃ vivaritvā kathehī’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ yadā hī’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1044085,191,693,182,209,1,101,14,Aṭṭhakathāyaṃ pana‘‘ yadā hi bhikkhūtiādinā‘ dhammānaṃ nāmaso ñāṇan’ ti padassa atthaṃ vivaratī’’ ti( netti. aṭṭha.25) vuttaṃ. 
1044086,191,693,210,216,1,56,6,Tassattho aṭṭhakathāyaṃ vibhajitvā vuttovāti na vicārito. 
1044087,191,694,2,32,1,145,18,"26. Neruttaṃ ācariyena vibhattaṃ, amhehi ca ñātaṃ‘‘ katamo sutte gavesitabbo bhagavato adhippāyo’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha katamo adhippāyo’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1044088,191,694,33,35,1,16,2,Tassattho pākaṭo. 
1044089,191,694,36,58,1,147,17,"Apica‘‘ dhammo have rakkhatī’’ tiādīsu yena puggalena attanā rakkhitena dhammena rakkhitabbabhāvo icchito, so dhammaṃ rakkhissatīti bhagavato adhippāyo. "
1044090,191,694,59,69,1,77,9,"Yo puggalo duggatito muccitukāmo, so dhammaṃ rakkhissatīti bhagavato adhippāyo. "
1044091,191,695,2,18,1,115,14,"Coro yathā sandhimukhe {gahito}tiādīsu yo coro ghātanato muccitukāmo, so corakammaṃ na karissatīti bhagavato adhippāyo. "
1044092,191,695,19,30,1,87,10,"Yo puggalo apāyādidukkhato muccitukāmo, so pāpakammaṃ na karissatīti bhagavato adhippāyo. "
1044093,191,696,2,16,1,98,10,"{Sukhakāmānī}tiādīsu ye puggalā sukhaṃ icchanti, te parahiṃsanato vivajjissantīti bhagavato adhippāyo. "
1044094,191,697,2,39,1,317,29,"Middhī yadā hoti mahagghaso {cā}tiādīsu ye puggalā punappunaṃ pavattamānajātijarāmaraṇato muccitukāmā, te bhojane mattaññuno bhavissanti, santuṭṭhā bhavissanti, suddhājīvā bhavissanti, pātimokkhasaṃvarasīlasampannā bhavissanti, atandino bhavissanti, vipassakā bhavissanti, sagāravā sappatissā bhavissantīti bhagavato adhippāyo. "
1044095,191,698,2,19,1,151,15,"Appamādo amatapadan tiādīsu ye puggalā maccuno bhāyanti, nibbānamicchanti, te puggalā dānasīlabhāvanākammesu appamattā bhavissantīti bhagavato adhippāyo. "
1044096,191,699,2,34,1,157,19,"27. Sutte gavesitabbo adhippāyo ācariyena vibhatto, amhehi ca viññāto,‘‘ katamaṃ suttassa gavesitabbaṃ nidānan’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha katamaṃ nidānan’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1044097,191,699,35,42,1,49,7,Tattha nidānan ti phalaṃ nīharitvā detīti nidānaṃ. 
