1044255,191,736,2,4,1,27,2,7 . Āvaṭṭahāravibhaṅgavibhāvanā 
1044256,191,737,2,36,1,201,21,"29. Yena yena saṃvaṇṇanāvisesabhūtena catubyūhahāravibhaṅgena neruttādayo vibhattā, so… pe… catubyūhahāravibhaṅgo paripuṇṇo,‘‘ katamo āvaṭṭo hāravibhaṅgo’’ ti pucchitabbattā tattha katamo āvaṭṭo hāro’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1044257,191,737,37,51,1,127,13,Tattha {tatthā}ti tesu niddiṭṭhesu soḷasasu desanāhārādīsu katamo saṃvaṇṇanāviseso āvaṭṭo hāro āvaṭṭahāravibhaṅgo nāmāti pucchati.
1044258,191,737,52,72,1,134,12,‘‘ Ekamhi padaṭṭhānen’’ tiādiniddesassa idāni mayā vuccamāno‘‘ ārambhathā’’ tiādiko vitthārasaṃvaṇṇanāviseso āvaṭṭahāravibhaṅgo nāmāti gahito.
1044259,191,737,73,94,1,132,14,"‘‘ Tattha desanāyaṃ ekasmiṃ padaṭṭhāne desanāruḷhe sesakaṃ padaṭṭhānaṃ pariyesati, pariyesitvā kathaṃ paṭipakkhe āvaṭṭetī’’ ti vattabbattā–"
1044260,191,738,2,9,1,43,5,"‘ ‘ Ārambhatha nikkamatha, yuñjatha buddhasāsane; "
1044261,191,739,2,11,1,45,6,"Dhunātha maccuno senaṃ, naḷāgāraṃva kuñjaro’’ ti."
1044262,191,739,12,12,1,0,0,– 
1044263,191,740,2,4,1,11,2,Gāthā vuttā. 
1044264,191,740,5,15,1,89,10,Idha gāthāyaṃ ekasmiṃ padaṭṭhāne desanāruḷhe sesakaṃ padaṭṭhānaṃ pariyesatīti vuttaṃ hoti. 
1044265,191,740,16,27,1,34,4,Gāthāttho pana aṭṭhakathāyaṃ( netti. aṭṭha.29) vutto.
1044266,191,741,2,28,1,173,18,‘ ‘ Ārambhathā’ tiādigāthāyaṃ katarasmiṃ padaṭṭhāne desanāruḷhe katamaṃ sesakaṃ padaṭṭhānaṃ pariyesatī’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ ārambhatha nikkamathāti vīriyassa padaṭṭhānan’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1044267,191,741,29,58,1,321,23,"Tattha‘‘ vīriyassa padaṭṭhānan’’ ti sāmaññavasena vuttampi ārambhadhātusaṅkhātaṃ vīriyaṃ nikkamadhātusaṅkhātassa vīriyassa padaṭṭhānaṃ, nikkamadhātusaṅkhātaṃ vīriyaṃ parakkamadhātusaṅkhātassa vīriyassa padaṭṭhānaṃ, parakkamadhātusaṅkhātaṃ vīriyaṃ samathabhāvanāsahitassa vīriyassa padaṭṭhānantiādinā pariyesitabbanti gahetabbaṃ."
1044268,191,741,59,85,1,178,17,"‘‘ Yuñjathā’’ ti iminā vuttaṃ samathabhāvanāsahitaṃ vīriyaṃ‘‘ buddhasāsane’’ ti iminā vuttassa mahaggatasamādhissa padaṭṭhānaṃ, desanāruḷhaṃ sukhādikaṃ sesakampi padaṭṭhānaṃ pariyesitabbaṃ."
1044269,191,741,86,108,1,174,17,"‘‘ Dhunātha maccuno senan’’ ti padena gahitaṃ vipassanāsahitaṃ vīriyaṃ kilesadhunane samatthāya paññāya padaṭṭhānaṃ, desanāruḷhaṃ samādhiādikaṃ sesakampi padaṭṭhānaṃ pariyesitabbaṃ."
1044270,191,742,2,38,1,243,26,"‘ ‘ Yadi‘ ārambhathā’ tiādikaṃ vuttaṃ vīriyaṃ sāmaññabhūtānaṃ vīriyasamādhipaññānaṃyeva padaṭṭhānaṃ siyā, evaṃ sati kathaṃ vaṭṭamūlaṃ chinditvā vivaṭṭaṃ pāpessantī’’ ti vattabbattā puna‘‘ ārambhatha nikkamathāti vīriyindriyassa padaṭṭhānan’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1044271,191,742,39,51,1,138,12,Ādhipaccakiccatāya yuttassāpi vīriyādhikassa padaṭṭhānattā ārabhantā yogāvacarapuggalā vaṭṭamūlaṃ chinditvā vivaṭṭaṃ pāpentīti vuttaṃ hoti.
1044272,191,742,52,79,1,173,18,"‘‘ Ārambhathā’’ tiādikā pana yasmā vīriyārambhavatthuādidesanā hoti, tasmā ārambhavatthuādīniyeva saṃvaṇṇitāni padaṭṭhānanti codanaṃ manasi katvā āha‘‘ imāni padaṭṭhānāni desanā’’ ti."
1044273,191,742,80,97,1,128,11,"‘‘ Ārambhathā’’ tiādikā yathāvuttapadaṭṭhānāni desanā hoti, na vīriyārambhavatthuādīni, tasmā padaṭṭhānaṃyeva saṃvaṇṇitanti daṭṭhabbaṃ. "
1044274,191,743,2,39,1,184,21,"Evaṃ ‘‘ ārambhathā’’ tiādidesanāya padaṭṭhānavasena attho vibhatto, amhehi ca ñāto,‘‘ kathaṃ tassāyeva desanāya paṭipakkhavasena attho vibhajitabbo’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ ayuñjantānaṃ vā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1044275,191,743,40,58,1,148,14,Tattha yoge bhāvanāyaṃ ayuñjantānaṃ sattānaṃ aparipakkañāṇānaṃ yoge yogahetu vāsanābhāgiyavasena āyatiṃ jānanatthāya‘‘ ārambhathā’’ tiādidesanā āraddhā. 
1044276,191,743,59,74,1,122,11,Yuñjantānaṃ paripakkañāṇānaṃ sattānaṃ ārambhe ārambhahetu diṭṭheva dhamme parijānanatthāya‘‘ ārambhathā’’ tiādidesanā āraddhā. 
1044277,191,744,2,33,1,241,28,"Tattha tesu yuñjantāyuñjantesu paripakkāparipakkañāṇesu ye aparipakkañāṇā sattā na yuñjanti, te aparipakkañāṇā sattā pamādamūlakā hutvā yoge bhāvanāyaṃ yena pamādena na yuñjanti, so pamādo taṇhāmūlako pamādo, avijjāmūlako pamādoti dubbidho hoti. "
1044278,191,744,34,63,1,209,24,"Tattha tasmiṃ dubbidhe pamāde aññāṇena nivuto avijjāmūlako satto yena pamādena ñeyyaṭṭhānaṃ‘‘ ime uppādavayadhammā pañcakkhandhā ñeyyaṭṭhānaṃ nāmā’’ ti nappajānāti, ayaṃ aññāṇahetuko pamādo avijjāmūlako pamādā nāma. "
1044279,191,744,64,115,1,351,45,"Yo pamādo taṇhāmūlako, so pamādo tividho anuppannānaṃ bhogānaṃ uppādāya pariyesanto taṇhiko satto yaṃ pamādaṃ āpajjati, ayaṃ pamādo ca, uppannānaṃ bhogānaṃ ṭhitatthāya rakkhanto taṇhiko satto ārakkhanimittaṃ yaṃ pamādaṃ āpajjati, ayaṃ pamādo ca, ṭhitaṃ bhogaṃ paribhuñjanto taṇhiko satto paribhoganimittaṃ yaṃ pamādaṃ āpajjati, ayaṃ pamādo cāti tividho hoti. "
1044280,191,744,116,130,1,113,13,"Iti loke ayaṃ pamādo catubbidho avijjāpadaṭṭhāno ekavidho pamādo, taṇhāpadaṭṭhāno tividho pamādoti catubbidho hoti. "
1044281,191,744,131,144,1,129,12,"Tattha tāsu avijjātaṇhāsu nāmakāyo phassādināmasamūho avijjāya padaṭṭhānaṃ, rūpakāyo pathavīādirūpasamūho taṇhāya padaṭṭhānaṃ hoti. "
1044282,191,744,145,166,1,197,18,"Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti– ārambhadhātunikkamadhātusaṅkhātassa vīriyassa paṭipakkho catubbidho pamādo niddhāretabbo, niddhāretvā ekavidhassa pamādassa avijjā padaṭṭhānaṃ, tividhassa pamādassa taṇhā padaṭṭhānaṃ. "
1044283,191,744,167,178,1,110,10,"Avijjāya nāmakāyo padaṭṭhānaṃ, taṇhāya rūpakāyo padaṭṭhānanti paṭipakkhe āvaṭṭetvā padaṭṭhānaṃ pariyesitabbanti."
1044284,191,745,2,40,1,178,24,"‘ ‘ Kasmā nāmakāyo avijjāya padaṭṭhānaṃ bhavati, rūpakāyo taṇhāya padaṭṭhānaṃ bhavatī’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ taṃ kissa hetū’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ rūpīsu bhavesu ajjhosānaṃ, arūpīsu sammoho’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
1044285,191,745,41,57,1,143,15,"Rūpīsu bhavesu rūpadhammesu ahaṃmamādivasena ajjhosānaṃ taṇhābhiniveso sattesu patiṭṭhito yasmā hoti, tasmā rūpakāyo taṇhāya padaṭṭhānaṃ bhavati. "
1044286,191,745,58,64,1,63,6,Anamatagge hi saṃsāre itthipurisā aññamaññarūpābhirāmā bhavanti. 
1044287,191,745,65,81,1,132,15,"Arūpīsu phassādīsu sukhumabhāvato sammoho sattesu patiṭṭhito yasmā hoti, tasmā nāmakāyo avijjāya padaṭṭhānaṃ bhavatīti yojanā kātabbā. "
1044288,191,745,82,102,1,168,17,"Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti– rūpakāyanāmakāyesu ārammaṇakaraṇavasena taṇhāya ca avijjāya ca uppajjanato rūpakāyo taṇhāya padaṭṭhānaṃ, nāmakāyo avijjāya padaṭṭhānanti nīharitabbāvāti."
1044289,191,746,2,27,1,121,16,"‘ ‘ Katamo rūpakāyo, katamo nāmakāyo’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha rūpakāyo rūpakkhandho, nāmakāyo cattāro arūpino khandhā’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
1044290,191,746,28,43,1,124,14,"Tattha tesu rūpakāyanāmakāyesu rūpakāyo rūpasamūho nāma rūpakkhandho hoti, nāmakāyo nāmasamūho nāma cattāro arūpino khandhāti. "
1044291,191,746,44,71,1,197,20,"Ime pañcakkhandhā avijjātaṇhānaṃ ārammaṇattā saupādānā bhaveyyuṃ,‘‘ katamena upādānena saupādānā bhavantī’’ ti pucchitabbattā tatheva pucchitvā vissajjetuṃ‘‘ ime pañcakkhandhā katamena upādānena saupādānā? "
1044292,191,746,72,80,1,32,6,Taṇhāya ca avijjāya cā’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1044293,191,746,81,95,1,118,14,Tattha upādānabhūtāya taṇhāya ca upādānabhūtāya avijjāya ca ime pañcakkhandhā saupādānā nāma bhavantīti yojanā kātabbā.
