1044403,191,766,144,156,1,151,11,Samathavipassanāya nīvaraṇappahānañca ariyamaggabhāvanāya anusayasamugghāto cāti pariyodāpanassa duvidhattā pañcakkhandhā pariyodāpitā bhavantīti attho. 
