1044625,191,818,2,37,1,257,22,"‘ ‘ Tattha yasmā saṃvaṇṇiyamāne sutte yathāniddiṭṭhānaṃ kusalākusaladhammānaṃ paṭipakkhabhūte akusalakusaladhamme pahātabbabhāvādivasena niddhāraṇaṃ paṭipakkhato parivattanaṃ, tasmā‘ sammādiṭṭhissa purisapuggalassa micchādiṭṭhi nijjiṇṇā bhavatī’ tiādi āraddhan’’ ti( netti. aṭṭha.35)– "
