1044628,191,819,20,30,1,84,9,Tattha {sammādiṭṭhissā}ti sammā sundarā pasatthā diṭṭhi yassa puggalassāti sammādiṭṭhi. 
1044629,191,819,31,35,1,32,4,Puggalapadaṭṭhānā hi ayaṃ desanā. 
