1044897,191,894,50,61,1,89,10,"Nissitassa puggalassa calitaṃ calanaṃ atthi, anissitassa puggalassa calitaṃ calanaṃ natthi. "
1044898,191,894,62,129,1,459,56,"Calite calane asati passaddhi bhavati, passaddhiyā sati vijjamānāya nati na hoti, natiyā asati avijjamānāya āgatigati na hoti, āgatigatiyā asati avijjamānāya cutūpapāto na hoti, cutūpapāte asati avijjamāne idha chasu ajjhattikāyatanesu attānaṃ neva passati, huraṃ vā chasu bāhirāyatanesu attānaṃ na passati, ubhayaṃ antarena vajjetvā phassādisamudāyesu dhammesu attānaṃ na passati, esova paṭiccasamuppādo‘‘ avijjānirodhā’’ tiādiko dukkhassa anto avasānaṃ karotīti attho. "
