1044920,191,902,2,45,1,193,24,"‘ ‘ Ye keci sokā’’ tiādigāthāpāṭhe otaraṇā ācariyena vibhattā, amhehi ca ñātā ,‘‘ kāmaṃ kāmayamānassā’’ tiādigāthāpāṭhe‘‘ katame niddhāretvā katamehi otaratī’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ kāmaṃ kāmayamānassā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1044921,191,902,46,51,1,36,5,Tassaṃ gāthāyaṃ attho heṭṭhā vuttova. 
1044922,191,903,2,22,1,98,14,"{Tatthā}ti tasmiṃ‘‘ pītimano hotī’’ ti pāṭhe yā pītimanatā vuttā niddhāritā, ayaṃ pītimanatā anunayo hoti."
1044923,191,903,23,45,1,116,16,"‘‘ Sallaviddhova ruppatī’’ ti pāṭhe yaṃ ruppanaṃ āha, idaṃ ruppanaṃ paṭighaṃ hoti, anunayo ca paṭighañca niddhāritāti attho."
1044924,191,904,2,26,1,118,17,‘ ‘ Anunaye ca paṭighe ca niddhārite katamo dhammo niddhārito’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ anunayo paṭighañca pana taṇhāpakkho’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1044925,191,904,27,32,1,45,4,{Taṇhāpakkho}ti taṇhāpakkhattā taṇhā niddhāritā.
1044926,191,904,33,49,1,73,11,"‘‘ Anunayo taṇhāpakkho hotu, paṭighaṃ pana taṇhāpakkhaṃ na siyā’’ ti ce vadeyya? "
1044927,191,904,50,56,1,68,6,Paṭighassa attasinehavasena pavattanato paṭighampi taṇhāpakkhaṃ hoti.
1044928,191,904,57,76,1,83,11,‘‘ Taṇhāya niddhāritāya katamo niddhārito’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ taṇhāya ca panā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1044929,191,904,77,85,1,79,8,Dasannaṃ rūpāyatanānaṃ taṇhāya padaṭṭhānattā dasa rūpāni āyatanāni niddhāritāni. 
1044930,191,904,86,92,1,48,6,Ayaṃ vuttappakārā otaraṇā āyatanehi otaraṇā nāma. 
1044931,191,904,93,129,1,318,31,"Sutte āgatā paṭiccasamuppādādayo tena saṃvaṇṇanāvisesena nayena niddhāritā, suttatthamukhena vā niddhāritā, tena… pe… nayena niddhāritesu paṭiccasamuppādādīsu yo saṃvaṇṇanānayaviseso tadatthavācakavasena vā tadatthañāpakavasena vā otarati pavisati samosarati, so saṃvaṇṇanānayaviseso otaraṇo hāro nāmāti adhippāyo daṭṭhabbo. "
1044932,191,904,130,134,1,44,4,Sesesupi vuttanayānusārena otaraṇā gahetabbā.
1044933,191,904,135,155,1,115,12,‘‘ Tenāha āyasmā’’ tiādyānusandhyādiattho ceva‘‘ niyutto otaraṇo hāro’’ ti anusandhyādiattho ca vuttanayānusārena veditabbo. 
1044934,191,905,2,5,1,46,4,Iti otaraṇahāravibhaṅge sattibalānurūpā racitā 
1044935,191,906,2,4,1,18,2,Vibhāvanā niṭṭhitā. 
1044936,191,907,2,9,1,84,7,Paṇḍitehi pana aṭṭhakathāṭīkānusārena gambhīrattho vitthārato vibhajitvā gahetabboti.
1044937,191,908,2,4,1,28,2,13 . Sodhanahāravibhaṅgavibhāvanā 
1044938,191,909,2,38,1,215,21,"45. Yena yena saṃvaṇṇanāvisesabhūtena otaraṇahāravibhaṅgena otaretabbā suttatthā vibhattā, so saṃvaṇṇanāvisesabhūto vibhaṅgo paripuṇṇo,‘‘ katamo sodhanahāravibhaṅgo’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha katamo sodhano hāro’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1044939,191,909,39,53,1,129,13,Tattha {tatthā}ti tesu niddiṭṭhesu soḷasasu desanāhārādīsu katamo saṃvaṇṇanāviseso sodhano hāro sodhanahāravibhaṅgo nāmāti pucchati.
1044940,191,909,54,76,1,147,14,‘‘ Vissajjitamhi pañhe’’ tiādiniddesassa idāni mayā vuccamāno‘‘ yathā āyasmā ajito’’ tiādiko vitthārasaṃvaṇṇanāviseso sodhanahāravibhaṅgo nāmāti gahetabbo.
1044941,191,909,77,97,1,85,12,‘‘ Kathaṃ tattha pañhe sodhano hāro viññātabbo’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ yathā āyasmā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1044942,191,909,98,117,1,140,18,"Yathā yena pakārena āyasmā ajito pārāyane bhagavantaṃ pañhaṃ pucchati, tathā tena pakārena vissajjitamhi pañhe ayaṃ sodhano hāro viññātabboti."
1044943,191,909,118,135,1,77,9,‘‘ Niyametvā vibhajehī’’ ti vattabbattā niyametvā vibhajituṃ‘‘ kenassū’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1044944,191,909,136,138,1,17,2,Gāthāttho vuttova.
1044945,191,910,2,10,1,39,6,"‘ ‘ Kenassu nivuto loko, kenassu nappakāsati; "
1044946,191,911,2,11,1,48,6,"Kissābhilepanaṃ brūsi, kiṃsu tassa mahabbhayan’’ ti."
1044947,191,911,12,12,1,0,0,– 
1044948,191,912,2,4,1,30,2,Pucchāvasena pavattagāthāyañca–
1044949,191,913,2,12,1,20,4,"‘ ‘ Avijjāya nivuto loko,( ajitāti bhagavā,) "
1044950,191,914,2,5,1,27,3,Vivicchā pamādā nappakāsati; 
1044951,191,915,2,10,1,48,5,"Jappābhilepanaṃ brūmi, dukkhamassa mahabbhayan’’ ti."
1044952,191,915,11,11,1,0,0,– 
1044953,191,916,2,43,1,233,29,Vissajjanavasena pavattagāthāyañcāti imāsu dvīsu gāthāsu‘‘ kenassu nivuto loko’’ ti iminā padena pañhe pucchite‘‘ avijjāya nivuto loko’’ ti iminā padena bhagavā‘‘ kenassu nivuto loko’’ ti padaṃ tadatthe aññāṇasaṃsayādimalānaṃ apanayanena sodheti. 
1044954,191,916,44,58,1,107,13,"Tadatthe hi vissajjite aññāṇasaṃsayādīnaṃ abhāvato attho sodhito nāma, atthe ca sodhite padampi sodhitaṃyeva. "
1044955,191,916,59,61,1,20,2,Tenāha aṭṭhakathāyaṃ–
1044956,191,916,62,87,1,95,9,"‘‘ tadatthassa vissajjanato’’ ti( netti. aṭṭha.45), ṭīkāya ñca‘‘ tabbisayaaññāṇasaṃsayādimalāpanayanena sodhetī’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
1044957,191,916,88,119,1,195,23,"No ca ārambhan ti pucchituṃ ārabhitabbaṃ sabbagāthāpadaṃ, gāthātthaṃ vā, ñātuṃ icchitassa sabbassa atthassa vissajjanavasena apariyositattā bhagavā‘‘ avijjāya nivuto loko’’ ti ettakeneva padena sodheti. "
1044958,191,916,120,123,1,17,3,Sesesupi esa nayo.
1044959,191,917,2,30,1,146,21,‘ ‘ Kiṃsu tassa mahabbhayan’’ ti iminā padena pañhe pucchite‘‘ dukkhamassa mahabbhayan’’ ti padena bhagavatā ārambho ñātuṃ icchito attho suddho sodhito hoti. 
1044960,191,917,31,34,1,24,3,Sesagāthāsupi eseva nayo. 
1044961,191,918,2,16,1,111,13,"Yattha pañhe evaṃ niravasesavissajjanavasena ārambho suddho sodhito bhavati, so pañho vissajjito sodhito bhavati. "
1044962,191,918,17,35,1,135,17,"Yattha pañhe evaṃ niravasesavissajjanavasena ārambho yāva asuddho asodhito bhavati, tāva so pañho vissajjito sodhito na bhavatīti yojanā."
1044963,191,918,36,55,1,108,11,‘‘ Tenāhā’’ tiādyānusandhyādyattho ceva‘‘ niyutto sodhano hāro’’ ti anusandhyādyattho ca vuttanayānusārena veditabbo. 
