1044967,191,922,2,4,1,31,2,14 . Adhiṭṭhānahāravibhaṅgavibhāvanā 
1044968,191,923,2,34,1,189,19,"46. Yena yena saṃvaṇṇanāvisesabhūtena vibhaṅgena pañhādayo sodhitā, so saṃvaṇṇanāvisesabhūto paripuṇṇo,‘‘ katamo adhiṭṭhānahāravibhaṅgo’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha katamo adhiṭṭhāno hāro’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1044969,191,923,35,50,1,149,14,Tattha {tatthā}ti tesu niddiṭṭhesu soḷasasu desanāhārādīsu katamo saṃvaṇṇanāviseso paṭiniddesato adhiṭṭhāno hāro adhiṭṭhānahāravibhaṅgo nāmāti pucchati.
1044970,191,923,51,82,1,201,21,"‘‘ Ekattatāya dhammā, yepi ca vemattatāya niddiṭṭhā’’ tiādiniddesassa idāni mayā vuccamāno‘‘ ye tattha niddiṭṭhā, tathā te dhārayitabbā’’ tiādiko vitthārasaṃvaṇṇanāviseso adhiṭṭhānahāravibhaṅgo nāmāti gahetabbo."
1044971,191,924,2,37,1,169,24,"‘ ‘ Ye dhammā suttesu ekattatāya ca vemattatāya ca niddiṭṭhā, te dhammā kiṃ pana tatheva dhārayitabbā , udāhu aññathāpi vikappayitabbā’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ ye tatthā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1044972,191,924,38,64,1,202,24,"Tattha tesu suttantesu ye dukkhasaccādayo dhammā ekattatāya ca vemattatāya ca niddiṭṭhā, te dukkhasaccādayo dhammā tathā ekattatāya ca vemattatāya ca dhārayitabbā upalakkhitabbā, na aññathā vikappayitabbā."
1044973,191,925,2,24,1,128,14,"‘ ‘ Sāmaññakappanāya vohārabhāvena anavaṭṭhānato katamā ekattatā, katamā vemattatā’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ dukkhanti ekattatā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1044974,191,925,25,38,1,110,12,"Dukkhan ti jātiādivisesamanapekkhitvā yā dukkhasāmaññatā vuttā, sā ayaṃ dukkhasāmaññatā dukkhassa ekattatā nāma."
