1045007,191,938,52,64,1,50,5,Padatthādiko viseso aṭṭhakathāyaṃ( netti. aṭṭha.47) vitthārato vutto. 
1045008,191,939,2,17,1,120,11,Vuttappakārassa dukkhasamudayādikassa dhammassa ekattatādilakkhaṇaṃ nigamanavasena dassetuṃ‘‘ evaṃ yo dhammo’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1045009,191,939,18,28,1,52,8,Tattha evan ti iminā mayā vuttena‘‘ dukkhanti ekattatā. 
1045010,191,939,29,32,1,22,3,Tattha katamaṃ dukkhaṃ? 
1045011,191,939,33,41,1,38,5,"Jāti dukkhā, jarā dukkhā’’ tiādivacanena. "
1045012,191,939,42,48,1,49,5,Yo {dhammo}ti yo koci jātijarābyādhyādivisesadhammo. 
1045013,191,939,49,56,1,74,6,Yassa {dhammassā}ti tato jātiādivisesadhammato aññassa jarādivisesadhammassa. 
1045014,191,939,57,63,1,83,5,{Samānabhāvo}ti jātiādivisesadhammena jarādivisesadhammassa dukkhabhāvena samānabhāvo. 
1045015,191,939,64,68,1,39,3,Tassa {dhammassā}ti jarādivisesadhammassa. 
1045016,191,939,69,75,1,77,4,{Ekattatāyā}ti dukkhasamudayatādisamānatāya dukkhasamudayādibhāvānaṃ ekībhāvena. 
1045017,191,939,76,88,1,98,7,{Ekībhavatī}ti jātiādivisesabhedena anekopi‘‘ dukkhasamudayo’’ tiādinā ekasaddābhidheyyatāya ekībhavati. 
1045018,191,939,89,99,1,56,9,"Yena yena vā pana vilakkhaṇo, tena tena vemattaṃ gacchati. "
1045019,191,939,100,132,1,361,30,"Yassa jātiādidhammassa yena yena abhinibbattanaparipācanādisabhāvena yo jātiādidhammo jarādidhammena vilakkhaṇo visadiso hoti, tassa jātiādidhammassa tena tena abhinibbattanaparipācanādisabhāvena so jātiādidhammo jarādidhammena vemattataṃ visadisattaṃ gacchati, dukkhasamudayādibhāvena samānopi jātiādidhammo jarādidhammassa visiṭṭhataṃ gacchatīti attho daṭṭhabbo. "
1045020,191,940,2,38,1,240,26,"Dukkhasamudayādidhammassa ekattavemattatā ācariyena vibhattā, amhehi ca ñātā,‘‘ tāya ekattavemattatāya kattha pucchite sati adhiṭṭhānaṃ vīmaṃsitabban’’ ti pucchitabbattā suttādike pucchite sati vīmaṃsitabbanti dassetuṃ‘‘ evaṃ sutte vā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1045021,191,940,39,57,1,129,16,"Tattha evaṃ iminā vuttappakārena sutte vā pucchite, veyyākaraṇe vā pucchite, gāthāyaṃ vā pucchitāyaṃ sati adhiṭṭhānaṃ vīmaṃsitabbaṃ."
1045022,191,940,58,81,1,111,14,"‘‘ Kiṃ vīmaṃsitabban’’ ti puccheyya‘‘ ekattatāya pucchati kiṃ, udāhu vemattatāya pucchati kin’’ ti vīmaṃsitabbanti yojanā. "
1045023,191,940,82,84,1,18,2,Aṭṭhakathāyaṃ pana–
1045024,191,940,85,111,1,99,13,‘‘ idāni tāva ekattavemattatāvisaye niyojetvā dassetuṃ‘ sutte vā veyyākaraṇe vā’ tiādi vuttan’’ ti( netti. aṭṭha.48) vuttaṃ.
1045025,191,940,112,132,1,83,10,"‘‘ Kathaṃ pucchitaṃ, kathaṃ vissajjitabban’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ yadi ekattatāyā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ."
1045026,191,940,133,153,1,110,12,‘‘ Tenāhā’’ tiādyānusandhyādiko ca‘‘ niyutto adhiṭṭhāno hāro’’ ti imassa anusandhyādiko ca vuttanayānusārena veditabbo. 
