1045098,191,954,25,30,1,64,5,Titthaññutā dīnaṃ attho padaṭṭhānahāravibhaṅgavaṇṇanāyaṃ vuttova. 
1045099,191,955,2,29,1,117,17,"Sabhāvo hetūti ācariyena vutto,‘‘ kīdiso so sabhāvo hetū’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ yathā vā pana cakkhuñca paṭiccā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ . "
1045100,191,955,30,41,1,102,11,Cakkhuviññāṇaṃ cakkhuñca cakkhundriyañca paṭicca nissayaṃ katvā rūpe paṭicca ārammaṇaṃ katvā uppajjati. 
1045101,191,955,42,60,1,195,15,"Tattha cakkhādīsu cakkhundriyaṃ ādhipateyyapaccayatāya indriyapaccayatāya cakkhuviññāṇassa paccayo, rūpārammaṇaṃ purejātārammaṇapaccayatāya paccayo, āloko sannissayatāya upanissayatāya paccayo hoti. "
1045102,191,955,61,76,1,99,14,"So paccayo honto phalena cakkhuviññāṇena asamānattā sabhāvo hetu na hoti, paccayo ca hoti manasikāro. "
1045103,191,955,77,98,1,181,20,"Kiriyamanodhātu pana phalena cakkhuviññāṇena viññāṇabhāvena samānattā sabhāvo hetu hoti yathā, evaṃ saṅkhārā nāmakkhandhabhāvena samānattā viññāṇassa paccayā hontā sabhāvo hetu honti. "
1045104,191,955,99,109,1,91,10,Viññāṇaṃ nāmarūpena ekasantativasena samānattā nāmarūpassa paccayo hontaṃ sabhāvo hetu hoti. 
1045105,191,955,110,121,1,63,7,Iminā nayena‘‘ nāmarūpaṃ saḷāyatanassā’’ tiādīsupi attho veditabbo. 
1045106,191,955,122,148,1,229,23,"Evaṃ vuttappakāro hetu, paccayo janako, upatthambhako ca yo koci upanissayo balavapaccayo hoti, sabbo so hetupaccayo janakaupatthambhako janitabbupatthambhiyassa phalassa parikkharaṇato abhisaṅkharaṇato nippariyāyato parikkhāro nāma."
1045107,191,956,2,22,1,103,13,‘ ‘ Vuttappakāro hetupaccayo parikkhāro nāmāti kena amhehi saddahitabbo’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ tenāhā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1045108,191,956,23,63,1,243,30,"Tena kāraṇabhūtena sabbassa hetupaccayassa parikkhārabhāvena āyasmā mahākaccāno‘‘ ye dhammā yaṃ dhammaṃ janayantī’’ ti yaṃ vacanaṃ āha, tena vacanena saddahitabbo,‘‘ ye dhammā yaṃ dhammaṃ janayantī’’ ti vacanaṃ nissāya tumhehi sallakkhetabboti adhippāyo."
1045109,191,957,2,35,1,168,24,"‘ ‘ Ettakova parikkhāro hāro yuñjitabbo’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ niyutto parikkhāro hāro’’ ti vuttaṃ, yo yo parikkhāro hāro yuñjitabbo, so so parikkhāro hāro nīharitvā yutto yuñjitabboti. "
1045110,191,958,2,5,1,49,4,Iti parikkhārahāravibhaṅge sattibalānurūpā racitā 
1045111,191,959,2,4,1,18,2,Vibhāvanā niṭṭhitā. 
1045112,191,960,2,9,1,84,7,Paṇḍitehi pana aṭṭhakathāṭīkānusārena gambhīrattho vitthārato vibhajitvā gahetabboti.
1045113,191,961,2,4,1,31,2,16 . Samāropanahāravibhaṅgavibhāvanā 
1045114,191,962,2,40,1,209,21,"50. Yena yena saṃvaṇṇanāvisesabhūtena parikkhārahāravibhaṅgena suttatthānaṃ hetupaccayo vibhatto, so… pe… vibhaṅgo paripuṇṇo,‘‘ katamo samāropanahāravibhaṅgo’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha katamo samāropano hāro’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1045115,191,962,41,53,1,126,12,Tattha tesu niddiṭṭhesu soḷasasu desanāhārādīsu katamo saṃvaṇṇanāviseso samāropano hāro samāropanahāravibhaṅgo nāmāti pucchati.
1045116,191,962,54,78,1,168,16,‘‘ Ye dhammā yaṃmūlā’’ tiādiniddesassa idāni mayā vuccamāno‘‘ ekasmiṃ padaṭṭhāne yattakāni padaṭṭhānāni otarantī’’ tiādiko vitthārasaṃvaṇṇanāviseso samāropanahāravibhaṅgo nāma.
1045117,191,963,2,23,1,122,14,‘ ‘ Kittake padaṭṭhāne sutte vutte kittakāni padaṭṭhānāni samāropayitabbānī’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ ekasmiṃ padaṭṭhāne’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1045118,191,963,24,46,1,190,21,"Ekasmiṃ padaṭṭhāne sutte vutte sati avuttāni yattakāni padaṭṭhānāni otaranti samosaranti, sabbāni tāni avuttāni padaṭṭhānāni sutte vuttāni viya niddhāraṇavasena ānetvā desanāya āropayitabbāni."
1045119,191,963,47,64,1,69,9,‘‘ Kāni viya samāropayitabbānī’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ yathā āvaṭṭe’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1045120,191,963,65,92,1,222,25,"Āvaṭṭe hāre ekasmiṃ padaṭṭhāne sutte vutte sati sutte avuttāni bahukāni padaṭṭhānāni otaranti, tāni bahukāni padaṭṭhānāni pariyesitabbāni yathā, evaṃ samāropane hārepi bahukāni padaṭṭhānāni desanāya samāropayitabbānīti attho."
1045121,191,964,2,23,1,143,17,"‘ ‘ Kevalaṃ pana padaṭṭhānavaseneva samāropanā kātabbā kiṃ, udāhu aññavasenāpi samāropanā kātabbā kin’’ ti vattabbattā aññavasenāpi samāropanā kātabbā; "
1045122,191,964,24,37,1,86,9,tasmā samāropanā catubbidhā kātabbāti dassento‘‘ tattha samāropanā catubbidhā’’ tiādimāha. 
1045123,191,964,38,61,1,211,18,"Tattha {tatthā}ti tāsu samāropayitabbasamāropanāsu padaṭṭhānaṃ padaṭṭhānasamāropanā, vevacanaṃ vevacanasamāropanā, bhāvanā bhāvanāsamāropanā, pahānaṃ pahānasamāropanā, iti iminā pabhedena samāropanā catubbidhā kātabbā."
1045124,191,965,2,26,1,151,16,‘ ‘ Tāsu catubbidhāsu samāropanāsu katamā padaṭṭhānasamāropanā’’ ti pucchitabbattā tathā pucchitvā padaṭṭhānasamāropanaṃ dassetuṃ‘‘ tattha katamā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1045125,191,965,27,36,1,85,9,Sutte vuttena padaṭṭhānena sutte avuttānaṃ padaṭṭhānānaṃ samāropanā katamāti pucchati. 
1045126,191,966,2,37,1,220,30,"Sabbapāpassa akusalassa yaṃ akaraṇaṃ akaraṇahetu sāsanaṃ atthi, etaṃ sāsanaṃ buddhānaṃ sāsanaṃ ovādo hoti, atha vā akaraṇaṃ akaraṇatthāya yaṃ sāsanaṃ atthi, etaṃ buddhānaṃ sāsanaṃ ovādo hoti, na yassa kassaci sāsananti attho. "
1045127,191,966,38,53,1,86,11,Akaraṇan ti hi sampadānatthe pavattaṃ paccattavacanaṃ yathā‘‘ kissa atthāya kimatthan’’ ti. 
1045128,191,966,54,64,1,68,9,"Kusalassa sampadā sampadāya yaṃ sāsanaṃ atthi, etaṃ buddhānaṃ sāsanaṃ. "
1045129,191,966,65,75,1,91,9,"Sacittapariyodāpanaṃ sacittapariyodāpanatthaṃ yaṃ sāsanaṃ atthi, etaṃ buddhānaṃ sāsanaṃ hoti. "
1045130,191,967,2,14,1,102,12,Iti evaṃpakārena vuttassa tassa sāsanassa kiṃ padaṭṭhānan ti visesassa visesapadaṭṭhānaṃ puna pucchati. 
1045131,191,967,15,32,1,123,13,Idaṃ sucaritattayaṃ sāsanassa ovādassa padaṭṭhānaṃ sucaritattayena hetunā sāsanattāti daṭṭhabbaṃ yathā‘‘ annena vasatī’’ tiādi.
1045132,191,967,33,54,1,120,13,‘‘ Sucaritattaye padaṭṭhāne vutte katamaṃ padaṭṭhānaṃ samāropayitabban’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha yaṃ kāyikañcā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1045133,191,967,55,81,1,174,17,"Idaṃ khandhattayaṃ sāsanassa padaṭṭhānaṃ samāropayitabbaṃ,‘‘ khandhattaye padaṭṭhāne samāropayite katamaṃ samāropayitabban’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha sīlakkhandho cā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1045134,191,967,82,87,1,66,5,Idaṃ samathavipassanādvayaṃ sāsanassa padaṭṭhānaṃ samāropayitabbaṃ.
1045135,191,967,88,109,1,139,13,‘‘ Samathavipassanādvaye padaṭṭhāne samāropayite katamaṃ padaṭṭhānaṃ samāropayitabban’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha samathassa phalan’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1045136,191,967,110,115,1,55,5,Idaṃ phaladvayaṃ sāsanassa padaṭṭhānaṃ samāropayitabbaṃ. 
1045137,191,968,2,32,1,194,20,"Sāsanassa padaṭṭhānāni samāropayitabbānīti ācariyena niddhāretvā vibhattāni, amhehi ca ñātāni,‘‘ idāni katamassa katamaṃ padaṭṭhānaṃ samāropayitabban’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ vanaṃ vanathassā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1045138,191,968,33,84,1,291,34,"Idaṃ kāmaguṇapañcakaṃ vanaṃ taṇhābhūtassa vanathassa padaṭṭhānaṃ taṇhāvatthubhāvato,‘‘ itthī’’ ti vā‘‘ puriso’’ ti vā nimittaggāhasaṅkhātaṃ idaṃ vanaṃ‘‘ aho cakkhu, aho sotaṃ, aho ghānaṃ, aho jivhā, aho kāyo’’ ti tesaṃ tesaṃ aṅgapaccaṅgānaṃ anubyañjanaggāhasaṅkhātassa vanathassa padaṭṭhānaṃ samāropayitabbaṃ. "
1045139,191,968,85,105,1,235,18,"Apariññātaṃ dvādasāyatanasaṅkhātaṃ idaṃ vanaṃ saṃyojanasaṅkhātassa vanathassa padaṭṭhānaṃ samāropayitabbaṃ, āyatanaṃ paṭicca saṃyojanuppajjanato anusayasaṅkhātaṃ idaṃ vanaṃ pariyuṭṭhānasaṅkhātassa vanathassa padaṭṭhānaṃ samāropayitabbaṃ."
1045140,191,968,106,129,1,127,15,‘‘ Pañcakāmaguṇādīnaṃ vanabhāvo ca taṇhādīnaṃ vanathabhāvo ca kena amhehi saddahitabbo’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ tenāha bhagavā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1045141,191,968,130,155,1,174,20,"Tena pañcakāmaguṇādīnaṃ vanabhāvena ca taṇhādīnaṃ vanathabhāvena ca bhagavā‘‘ chetvā vanañca vanathañcā’’ ti yaṃ vacanaṃ āha, tena bhagavato vacanena vacanānusārena saddahitabboti. "
1045142,191,968,156,166,1,48,6,Ayan ti ayaṃ‘‘ ekasmiṃ padaṭṭhāne’’ tiādisaṃvaṇṇanā. 
1045143,191,968,167,171,1,35,3,{Padaṭṭhānenā}ti ekekena padaṭṭhānena. 
1045144,191,968,172,177,1,44,3,{Samāropanā}ti tadaññapadaṭṭhānānaṃ samāropanā . 
1045145,191,968,178,188,1,73,6,Samāropenti samāropayitabbāni etāya saṃvaṇṇanāyāti {samāropanā}ti viggahoti.(1) 
1045146,191,969,2,32,1,144,17,"51. Padaṭṭhānena samāropanā ācariyena niddiṭṭhā, amhehi ca ñātā,‘‘ katamā vevacanena samāropanā’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha katamā vevacanenā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1045147,191,969,33,46,1,127,11,{Tatthā}ti tāsu catūsu padaṭṭhānasamāropanādīsu samāropanāsu vevacanena ekekena rotadaññavevacanānaṃ samāropanā {katamā}ti pucchati.
1045148,191,969,47,73,1,117,14,‘‘ Rāgavirāgā’’ ti ca‘‘ cetovimuttī’’ ti ca‘‘ sekkhaphalan’’ ti ca idaṃ vacanattayaṃ anāgāmiphalatthattā anāgāmiphalassa vevacanaṃ.
1045149,191,969,74,100,1,123,14,‘‘ Avijjāvirāgā’’ ti ca‘‘ paññāvimuttī’’ ti ca‘‘ asekkhaphalan’’ ti ca idaṃ vacanattayaṃ arahattaphalatthattā arahattaphalassa vevacanaṃ. 
1045150,191,969,101,109,1,34,5,Iminā nayena sesesu yojanā kātabbā.(2) 
1045151,191,970,2,29,1,140,17,"Vevacanena samāropanā ācariyena niddiṭṭhā, amhehi ca ñātā,‘‘ katamā bhāvanāya samāropanā’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha katamā bhāvanāyā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1045152,191,970,30,44,1,128,12,{Tatthā}ti tāsu catūsu padaṭṭhānasamāropanādīsu katamāya desitāya bhāvanāya katamesānaṃ adesitānaṃ bhāvanāropanā {katamā}ti pucchati. 
1045153,191,970,45,96,1,227,28,"Yathā yena pakārena yaṃ bhāvanaṃ bhagavā‘‘ tasmātiha, tvaṃ bhikkhu, kāye kāyānupassī viharati, ātāpī sampajāno satimā vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassan’’ ti( saṃ. ni.5.369,371,395,415) āha, tathā tena pakārena tāya bhāvanāya tadaññabhāvanāpi samāropayitabbāti attho."
1045154,191,971,2,26,1,84,12,‘ ‘ Tasmātihā’’ tiādipāṭhe ‘‘ kiṃ bhāvanaṃ bhagavā āhā’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ ātāpī’’ tiādi vuttaṃ.
1045155,191,971,27,37,1,43,6,‘‘ Ātāpī’’ ti vacanena vīriyindriyaṃ bhagavā āha.
1045156,191,971,38,48,1,46,6,‘‘ Sampajāno’’ ti vacanena paññindriyaṃ bhagavā āha.
1045157,191,971,49,58,1,34,5,‘‘ Satimā’’ ti vacanena satindriyaṃ āha.
1045158,191,971,59,70,1,62,7,‘‘ Vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassan’’ ti vacanena samādhindriyaṃ āha.
1045159,191,971,71,96,1,150,17,‘‘ Evaṃ vutte katamā bhāvanā samāropayitabbā’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ evaṃ kāye kāyānupassino viharato cattāro satipaṭṭhānā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchantī’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1045160,191,971,97,104,1,81,7,Evaṃ vuttāya vīriyindriyādibhāvanāya cattāro satipaṭṭhānā samāropayitabbāti attho. 
1045161,191,971,105,110,1,51,5,Kena kāraṇena bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchantīti pucchati. 
1045162,191,971,111,121,1,110,9,"Catunnaṃ indriyānaṃ indriyabhāvena, bhāvetabbabhāvena vā ekalakkhaṇattā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchantīti vissajjeti."
1045163,191,971,122,139,1,79,9,‘‘ Tesu samāropitesu katame samāropayitabbā’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ catūsū’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1045164,191,971,140,150,1,128,10,Catūsu satipaṭṭhānesu bhāviyamānesu samāropayitabbesu cattāro sammappadhānā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchantīti samāropayitabbāti attho. 
1045165,191,971,151,154,1,32,3,Sesesupi evameva samāropayitabbā. 
1045166,191,972,2,29,1,127,16,"Bhāvanāya samāropanā ācariyena vibhattā, amhehi ca ñātā,‘‘ katamā pahānena samāropanā’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha katamā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1045167,191,972,30,45,1,132,13,{Tatthā}ti tāsu catūsu padaṭṭhānasamāropanādīsu katamena desitena pahānena katamesaṃ adesitānaṃ pahānānaṃ katamā {samāropanā}ti pucchati.
1045168,191,972,46,72,1,184,16,‘‘ Kāye kāyānupassī viharanto asubhe‘ subhan’ ti vipallāsaṃ pajahatī’’ ti desitena‘‘ subhan’’ ti vipallāsappahānena kabaḷīkārāhārapariññāya paribandhakilesakāmupādānappahānādayopi samāropayitabbā.
1045169,191,973,2,28,1,187,17,‘ ‘ Vedanāsu vedanānupassī viharanto dukkhe‘ sukhan’ ti vipallāsaṃ pajahatī’’ ti desitena‘‘ sukhan’’ ti vipallāsappahānena phassāhārapariññāya paribandhakilesabhavupādānappahānādayopi samāropayitabbā.
1045170,191,974,2,28,1,185,17,‘ ‘ Citte cittānupassī viharanto anicce‘ niccan’ ti vipallāsaṃ pajahatī’’ ti desitena‘‘ niccan’’ ti vipallāsappahānena viññāṇāhārapariññāya paribandhakilesadiṭṭhupādānappahānādayopi samāropayitabbā.
1045171,191,975,2,27,1,135,15,‘ ‘ Dhammesu dhammānupassī viharanto anattani‘ attā’ ti vipallāsaṃ pajahatī’’ ti desitena‘‘ attā’’ ti vipallāsappahānena manosañcetanāhārapariññāya? 
1045172,191,975,28,35,1,98,4,Manosañcetanāhārapariññāya paribandhakilesaattavādupādānappahānādayopi samāropayitabbāti adhippāyo.(4) 
