1045206,191,997,36,53,1,79,11,Tasmā‘‘ soḷasa hārā paṭhaman’’ ti gāthaṃ paccāmasitvā‘‘ tassā niddeso kuhiṃ daṭṭhabbo? 
1045207,191,997,54,59,1,20,3,Hārasampāteti āhā’’ ti– 
1045208,191,998,2,3,1,6,1,Vuttaṃ . 
1045209,191,998,4,7,1,37,3,Gāthāttho niddesavibhāvanāyaṃ vuttova.
1045210,191,998,8,51,1,261,33,"‘‘ Soḷasa… pe… suttan’’ ti yā gāthā niddese ācariyena vuttā, tassā gāthāya niddeso kuhiṃ daṭṭhabbo, hāravibhaṅgassa ādimhi ācariyena na vibhatto, hārasampāte vā paccāmasitvā vibhattoti daṭṭhabbo kiṃ, udāhu nayasamuṭṭhāne vā paccāmasitvā vibhattoti daṭṭhabbo kinti pucchati. "
1045211,191,998,52,57,1,58,5,Hārasampāte paccāmasitvā vibhattoti daṭṭhabboti vissajjanā. 
1045212,191,999,2,46,1,362,34,"Hārasampāte tassā gāthāya niddeso daṭṭhabboti ācariyena vutto, so hārasampāto desanāhārasampātabhedena soḷasavidho,‘‘ tattha katamo hārasampāto desanāhārasampāto’’ ti pucchitabbattā imasmiṃ sutte saṃvaṇṇetabbe saṃvaṇṇanābhāvena mayā vibhajiyamāno hārasampātabhūto saṃvaṇṇanāviseso desanāhārasampāto nāmāti tathā vibhajituṃ‘‘ tattha katamo desanāhārasampāto’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1045213,191,999,47,53,1,61,5,{Tatthā}ti tasmiṃ soḷasavidhe desanāhārasampātādike hārasampāte. 
1045214,191,999,54,60,1,74,6,Katamo hārasampātabhūto saṃvaṇṇanāviseso desanāhārasampāto nāmāti pucchati.
1045215,191,1000,2,9,1,41,5,"‘ ‘ Arakkhitena cittena, micchādiṭṭhihatena ca; "
1045216,191,1001,2,10,1,47,5,"Thinamiddhābhibhūtena , vasaṃ mārassa gacchatī’’ ti."
1045217,191,1001,11,11,1,0,0,– 
1045218,191,1002,2,24,1,129,13,Sutte ‘‘ arakkhitena cittenāti kiṃdesayatī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ pamādaṃ desayatī’’ tiādisaṃvaṇṇanāviseso desanāhārasampāto nāmāti vuttaṃ hoti. 
1045219,191,1002,25,35,1,32,3,Gāthāttho aṭṭhakathāyaṃ( netti. aṭṭha.52) vibhatto. 
1045220,191,1002,36,46,1,96,10,Yojanattho pana arakkhitena cittena arakkhitacittasamaṅgī puggalo mārassa maccuno vasaṃ gacchati. 
1045221,191,1002,47,54,1,78,7,Micchādiṭṭhihatena vipallāsena vipallāsasamaṅgī puggalo mārassa vasaṃ gacchati. 
1045222,191,1002,55,64,1,120,9,Thinamiddhābhibhūtena sasaṅkhārikacittena kusītacittena taṃcittasamaṅgī puggalo mārassa kilesādimārassa vasaṃ gacchatīti.
1045223,191,1003,2,28,1,114,17,‘ ‘ Arakkhitena cittenā’ ti padena desitaṃ taṃ pamādadhammajātaṃ kassa padan’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ taṃ maccuno padan’’ ti vuttaṃ.
1045224,191,1003,29,68,1,209,25,"‘‘ Arakkhitena cittenā’’ ti iminā suttappadesena desito attho ācariyena vibhatto, amhehi ca ñāto,‘‘ micchādiṭṭhihatena cāti suttappadesena desito attho kathaṃ vibhatto’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ micchādiṭṭhihatena cā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1045225,191,1003,69,93,1,106,15,"Yena vipallāsena yadā anicce‘‘ niccan’’ ti passati, tadā pavatto so vipallāso‘‘ micchādiṭṭhihataṃ nāmā’’ ti vuccati."
1045226,191,1003,94,114,1,105,12,‘‘ So pana vipallāso kiṃlakkhaṇo’’ ti pucchitabbattā tathā pucchitvā‘‘ viparītaggāhalakkhaṇo vipallāso’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1045227,191,1004,2,14,1,116,7,{Viparītaggāhalakkhaṇo}ti asubhādīnaṃyeva subhādiviparītaggāhalakkhaṇo vipallāso‘‘ vipallāsayatī’’ ti kāritatthasambhavato. 
1045228,191,1004,15,18,1,35,3,Kiṃ vipallāso viparītaggāhalakkhaṇo? 
1045229,191,1004,19,29,1,80,8,"So vipallāso saññaṃ vipallāsayati, cittampi vipallāsayati, diṭṭhimpi vipallāsayati. "
1045230,191,1004,30,39,1,86,9,Iti tayo dhamme vipallāsayatīti vipallāsetabbānaṃ tividhattā vipallāsāpi tividhā honti. 
1045231,191,1004,40,57,1,206,16,"Tesu saññāvipallāso muduko dubbalo subhādivasena upaṭṭhitākāraggahaṇamattattā, cittavipallāso saññāvipallāsato balavā subhādivasena upaṭṭhahantānaṃ rūpakkhandhādīnaṃ subhādivasena sanniṭṭhānaṃ katvā gahaṇato. "
1045232,191,1004,58,67,1,100,8,"Diṭṭhivipallāso saññāvipallāsacittavipallāsehi balavataro, yaṃ yaṃ ārammaṇaṃ subhādiākārena upaṭṭhāti. "
1045233,191,1004,68,74,1,56,6,Taṃ taṃ ārammaṇaṃ sassatādivasena abhinivisitvā gahaṇato. 
1045234,191,1004,75,86,1,98,9,"Tasmā saññāvipallāso paṭhamaṃ vutto, tadanantaraṃ cittavipallāso, tadanantaraṃ diṭṭhivipallāso vutto. "
1045235,191,1004,87,94,1,90,7,Vitthārato pana ekekassa subhasukhaattaniccaggahaṇavasena catubbidhattā dvādasavidhā honti. 
1045236,191,1005,2,33,1,221,21,"Vipallāsā ācariyena vibhattā, amhehi ca ñātā,‘‘ katame vipallāsapavattiṭṭhānavisayā’’ ti pucchitabbattā imāni attabhāvavatthūni vipallāsapavattiṭṭhānavisayānīti dassetuṃ‘‘ so kuhiṃ vipallāsayati catūsu attabhāvavatthūsū’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
1045237,191,1005,34,42,1,112,8,Catūsu rūpakāyavedanācittadhammasaṅkhātesu attabhāvavatthūsu so sabbo vipallāso saññācittadiṭṭhiyo vipallāsayati.
1045238,191,1005,43,62,1,97,10,‘‘ Kathaṃ samanupassantassa vipallāsayatī’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ rūpaṃ attato samanupassatī’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
