1045264,191,1009,126,137,1,87,11,Na hi tāsu taṇhāavijjāsu arahattamaggena pahīnāsu koci saṃkileso appahīno nāma natthīti.
1045265,191,1010,2,42,1,283,31,"‘ ‘ Vuttappakārā taṇhāavijjā vuttappakārānaṃ vipallāsānaṃyeva mūlakāraṇaṃ honti kiṃ, udāhu sakalassa vaṭṭassāpi mūlakāraṇaṃ honti kin’’ ti vattabbattā vuttappakārā taṇhāavijjā vuttappakārānaṃ mūlakāraṇaṃ honti yathā, evaṃ sakalassa vaṭṭassāpi mūlakāraṇaṃ hontīti dassetuṃ‘‘ tesan’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1045266,191,1010,43,54,1,83,9,"Tattha yesaṃ puggalānaṃ cittaṃ arakkhitaṃ, micchādiṭṭhihatañca hoti, tesaṃ puggalānaṃ. "
1045267,191,1010,55,106,1,441,45,"Yesaṃ avijjānīvaraṇānaṃ taṇhāsaṃyojanānaṃ pubbakoṭi na paññāyati, tehi avijjānīvaraṇehi taṇhāsaṃyojanehi saṃsāre sandhāvantānaṃ saṃsarantānaṃ puggalānaṃ sakiṃ nirayaṃ māravasagamanena sandhāvanaṃ saṃsaraṇaṃ hoti, sakiṃ tiracchānayoniṃ sandhāvanaṃ saṃsaraṇaṃ hoti, sakiṃ pettivisayaṃ sandhāvanaṃ saṃsaraṇaṃ hoti, sakiṃ asurakāyaṃ sandhāvanaṃ saṃsaraṇaṃ hoti, sakiṃ deve sandhāvanaṃ saṃsaraṇaṃ hoti, sakiṃ manusse sandhāvanaṃ saṃsaraṇaṃ hotīti attho."
