1045269,191,1011,39,51,1,101,11,"Cittassa viññāṇakkhandhassa yā akallatā akammaniyatā atthi, idaṃ akallattaṃ akammaniyattaṃ thinaṃ nāma. "
1045270,191,1011,52,65,1,122,12,"Yaṃ kāyassa līnattaṃ vedanādikkhandhattayalīnattaṃ atthi, idaṃ kāyassa līnattaṃ middhaṃ nāmāti thinamiddhasarūpameva vuttaṃ. "
1045271,191,1011,66,96,1,274,27,"Tehi thinamiddhehi cittassa abhibhūtabhāvādiko pana suviññeyyattā na vutto, avuttepi yesaṃ puggalānaṃ cittaṃ thinamiddhehi abhibhūtaṃ, tesaṃ puggalānaṃ tena cittena cittasīsena saṃyojanena saṃsāre māravasagamanena sandhāvanaṃ saṃsaraṇaṃ pariyosānasabhāvo vitthāretvā gahetabbo."
