1045278,191,1012,103,111,1,71,7,{Gacchatī}ti upagacchati upeti anuvattati anugacchati nātikkamatīti attho.
1045279,191,1012,112,129,1,55,9,‘‘ Kasmā vasaṃ gacchatī’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ so hī’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1045280,191,1012,130,159,1,232,26,"Yo satto arakkhitacittena ca micchādiṭṭhihatacittena ca thinamiddhābhibhūtacittena ca samannāgato hoti, so satto avijjānīvaraṇādīhi nivuto hutvā saṃsārābhimukho hi yasmā hoti, na visaṅkhārābhimukho, tasmā mārassa vasaṃ gacchatīti attho."
1045281,191,1013,2,30,1,158,18,"‘ ‘ Arakkhitenātiādikassa yassa suttassa attho vibhatto, tena‘ arakkhitenā’ tiādikena suttena kittakāni saccāni desitānī’’ tivattabbattā‘‘ imāni bhagavatā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ."
1045282,191,1013,31,46,1,84,10,"‘‘ Arakkhitenā’’ tiādisuttena bhagavatā imāni dve saccāni desitāni dukkhaṃ, samudayo cāti. "
1045283,191,1013,47,49,1,15,2,Kathaṃ desitāni? 
1045284,191,1013,50,57,1,70,7,Abhidhammanissitāya kathāya ceva suttantanissitāya kathāya ca desitāni. 
1045285,191,1013,58,87,1,196,23,"Tāsu kathāsu abhidhammanissitāya kathāya desite sati‘‘ arakkhitena cittenā’’ ti iminā padena arakkhitaṃ rattampi cittaṃ, arakkhitaṃ duṭṭhampi cittaṃ, arakkhitaṃ mūḷhampi cittaṃ bhagavatā desitaṃ ñāpitaṃ. "
1045286,191,1013,88,101,1,175,11,"Tattha rattacittaṃ lobhasahagatacittuppādavasena aṭṭhavidhaṃ, duṭṭhacittaṃ paṭighasampayuttacittuppādavasena dubbidhaṃ, mūḷhacittaṃ momūhacittuppādavasena dubbidhanti veditabbaṃ. "
1045287,191,1013,102,118,1,140,15,"Imesañhi cittuppādānaṃ vasena yā cakkhundriyādīnaṃ agutti anārakkhā uppannā, tāya aguttiyā anārakkhāya cittaṃ arakkhitaṃ hoti phalūpacārenāti."
1045288,191,1014,2,19,1,134,12,"‘ ‘ Micchādiṭṭhihatenā’’ ti iminā padena micchādiṭṭhisaṃsaṭṭhaṃ cittaṃ desitaṃ, taṃ diṭṭhisampayuttacittuppādavasena catubbidhanti veditabbaṃ. "
1045289,191,1014,20,26,1,88,6,Tañhi micchādiṭṭhiyā saṃsaṭṭhabhāvena micchādiṭṭhivasānugatattā micchādiṭṭhihataṃ nāmāti.
1045290,191,1014,27,44,1,135,12,"‘‘ Thinamiddhābhibhūtenā’’ ti iminā padena thinamiddhena saṃsaṭṭhaṃ cittaṃ desitaṃ, taṃ sasaṅkhārikacittuppādavasena pañcavidhanti veditabbaṃ. "
1045291,191,1014,45,60,1,149,13,Tañhi thinamiddhena saṃsaṭṭhabhāvena thinamiddhavasānugatattā thinamiddhābhibhūtaṃ nāmāti evaṃ ye dvādasākusalā cittuppādakaṇḍe‘‘ katame dhammā akusalā? 
