1045310,191,1018,50,63,1,100,11,"Yena arahattamaggena parijānāti, yena arahattamaggena pajahati ca, ayaṃ arahattamaggo maggasaccaṃ nāma. "
1045311,191,1018,64,79,1,108,13,"Yaṃ nibbānadhammaṃ ārabbha taṇhāya, avijjāya ca pahānaṃ jātaṃ, ayaṃ nibbānadhammo nirodho nirodhasaccaṃ nāmāti. "
1045312,191,1018,80,85,1,39,5,Evaṃ cattāri saccāni bhagavatā desitāni.
1045313,191,1019,2,21,1,81,11,‘ ‘ Catunnaṃ saccānaṃ desitabhāvo kena viññātabbo’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ tenāhā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1045314,191,1019,22,44,1,205,18,"Tesu catūsu saccesu samudayasaccena assādo gahito, dukkhasaccena ādīnavo gahito, maggasaccanirodhasaccehi nissaraṇaṃ gahitaṃ, samudayappahānavasena sabbagatipajahanaṃ jātaṃ, sabbagatipajahanaṃ phalanti gahitaṃ. "
1045315,191,1019,45,76,1,295,25,"Yena rakkhitacittatādikena sabbagatipajahanaṃ jātaṃ, so rakkhitacittatādiko upāyoti gahito, arakkhitacittatādikassa paṭisedhanamukhena rakkhitacittatādikassa niyojanaṃ bhagavato āṇattīti gahitanti desanāhārena nānāsuttesu dassitā assādādayo‘‘ arakkhitenā’’ tiādike ekasmiṃyeva sutte nīharitvā dassitā."
1045316,191,1020,2,21,1,99,12,‘ ‘ Assādādīnaṃ nīharitvā dassitabhāvo kena viññātabbo saddahitabbo’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ tenāhā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1045317,191,1020,22,35,1,117,12,"Ettha ca yena saṃvaṇṇanāvisesena nānāsuttesu assādādayo nīharitvā dassitā, so saṃvaṇṇanāviseso desanāhāravibhaṅgo nāma. "
1045318,191,1020,36,50,1,132,13,"Yena saṃvaṇṇanāvisesena ekasmiṃyeva sutte assādādayo nīharitvā dassitā, so saṃvaṇṇanāviseso desanāhārasampāto nāmāti viseso daṭṭhabbo."
1045319,191,1021,2,19,1,87,10,‘ ‘ Ettakova desanāhārasampāto paripuṇṇo’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ niyutto desanāhārasampāto’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1045320,191,1021,20,42,1,216,20,"Ekekasmiṃyeva sutte assādādayo yena yena saṃvaṇṇanāvisesabhūtena desanāhārasampātena nīharitvā yathārahaṃ dassitā, so so saṃvaṇṇanāvisesabhūto desanāhārasampāto niyutto yathārahaṃ niddhāretvā yujjitabboti attho gahito. "
1045321,191,1022,2,5,1,44,4,Iti desanāhārasampāte sattibalānurūpā racitā 
