1045324,191,1025,2,4,1,26,2,2 . Vicayahārasampātavibhāvanā 
1045325,191,1026,2,38,1,190,21,"53. Yena desanāhārasampātena assādādayo ācariyena vibhattā, amhehi ca ñātā, so desanāhārasampāto paripuṇṇo,‘‘ katamo vicayahārasampāto’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha katamo vicayo hārasampāto’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1045326,191,1026,39,50,1,116,10,{Tatthā}ti tesu desanāhārasampātādīsu soḷasasu hārasampātesu katamo saṃvaṇṇanāviseso vicayahārasampāto nāmāti pucchati. 
1045327,191,1026,51,73,1,155,17,"Imesu dhammesu ayaṃ dhammo yena saṃvaṇṇanāvisesena vicayitabbo, so saṃvaṇṇanāviseso vicayahārasampāto nāmāti niyametvā vibhajituṃ‘‘ tattha taṇhā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1045328,191,1026,74,76,1,18,2,Aṭṭhakathāyaṃ pana–
1045329,191,1027,2,39,1,266,24,"‘ ‘ Evaṃ desanāhārasampātaṃ dassetvā idāni vicayahārasampātaṃ dassento yasmā desanāhārapadatthavicayo vicayahāro, tasmā desanāhāre vipallāsahetubhāvena niddhāritāya taṇhāya kusalādivibhāgapavicayamukhena vicayahārasampātaṃ dassetuṃ‘ tattha taṇhā duvidhā’ tiādi āraddhan’’ ti( netti. aṭṭha.53)– "
1045330,191,1028,2,3,1,6,1,Vuttaṃ . 
1045331,191,1028,4,26,1,134,13,Tattha {tatthā}ti tasmiṃ‘‘ arakkhitena cittenā’’ tiādisuttatthe desanāhārasampātena saṃvaṇṇite akusaladhamme‘‘ taṇhā’’ ti niddhāritā sabbataṇhā. 
1045332,191,1028,27,34,1,53,6,{Kusalāpī}ti catubhūmake kusale uddissa pavattā taṇhāpi. 
1045333,191,1028,35,44,1,78,8,{Akusalāpī}ti akusaladhamme uddissa pavattā taṇhāpīti duvidhā hotīti vicayitabbā. 
1045334,191,1028,45,48,1,19,3,Tena vuttaṃ ṭīkāyaṃ–
1045335,191,1028,49,73,1,159,16,"‘‘ kusaladhammārammaṇāti kusaladhamme uddissa pavattamattaṃ sandhāya vuttaṃ, na tesaṃ ārammaṇapaccayataṃ, idha‘ kusalā dhammā’ ti lokuttaradhammānampi adhippetattā’’ ti."
1045336,191,1029,2,25,1,101,14,"‘ ‘ Kusalā taṇhā kiṃgāminī, akusalā taṇhā kiṃ gāminī’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ akusalā saṃsāragāminī’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1045337,191,1029,26,45,1,96,11,Atha vā‘‘ katamo kusalākusalataṇhānaṃ viseso’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ akusalā saṃsāragāminī’’ tiādi vuttaṃ.
1045338,191,1029,46,87,1,243,28,"‘‘ Taṇhā nāma saṃsāragāminī hotu, kathaṃ apacayagāminī’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ pahānataṇhā’’ ti vuttaṃ, pahānassa hetubhūtā taṇhā {pahānataṇhā}ti attho, pahātabbataṇhaṃ āgamma yaṃ pahānaṃ pavattetabbaṃ, tena pavattetabbena pahānena apacayaṃ gacchatīti vuttaṃ hoti."
1045339,191,1030,2,26,1,115,15,"‘ ‘ Kiṃ pana taṇhāyeva kusalākusalāti dubbidhā, udāhu aññopi kusalākusalāti dubbidho’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ mānopī’’ tiādi vuttaṃ."
1045340,191,1030,27,51,1,106,16,"‘‘ Katamo māno kusalo, katamo māno akusalo’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ yaṃ mānaṃ nissāya mānaṃ pajahati, ayaṃ māno kusalo. "
1045341,191,1030,52,65,1,61,10,"Yo pana māno dukkhaṃ nibbattayati, ayaṃ māno akusalo’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
1045342,191,1030,66,93,1,182,22,"Tattha yaṃ mānaṃ… pe… {kusalo}ti yaṃ mānaṃ nissāya upanissāya pahānaṃ pavattitaṃ, tena pahānena santāne uppajjanārahaṃ mānaṃ pajahati, ayaṃ upanissayapaccayabhūto māno phalūpacārena kusalo. "
1045343,191,1030,94,119,1,153,21,"Yo pana… pe… {akusalo}ti yo pana māno parahiṃsanādivasena pavattamāno hutvā attano ca parassa ca dukkhaṃ nibbattayati, ayaṃ māno akusaloti vicayitvā veditabbo."
1045344,191,1031,2,34,1,169,21,‘ ‘ Saṃsārāpacayagāminīsu tāsu taṇhāsu katamā apacayagāminī taṇhā kusalā’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ kusalā’’ ti vuttāya taṇhāya sarūpaṃ dassetuṃ‘‘ tattha yaṃ nekkhammasitan’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1045345,191,1031,35,41,1,63,5,{Tatthā}ti tāsu saṃsārāpacayagāminīsu taṇhābhūtāsu kusalākusalāsu. 
1045346,191,1031,42,46,1,29,4,Ayaṃ taṇhā kusalāti sambandho.
1045347,191,1031,47,91,1,301,33,"‘‘ Ariyā puggalā santaṃ āyatanaṃ yaṃ ariyaphaladhammaṃ sacchikatvā upasampajja viharanti, taṃ āyatanaṃ ariyaphaladhammaṃ ahaṃ kudāssu sacchikatvā viharissan’’ ti patthayantassa tassa kulaputtassa tasmiṃ ariyaphale pihā uppajjati, pihāpaccayā yaṃ domanassaṃ uppajjati, idaṃ domanassaṃ‘‘ nekkhammasitan’’ ti vuccati. "
1045348,191,1031,92,102,1,110,10,Ayaṃ ariyaphale pihāsaṅkhātā taṇhā kusalā anavajjā anavajjaariyaphaladhammaṃ uddissa pavattattāti vicayitabbaṃ.
1045349,191,1032,2,17,1,54,8,‘ ‘ Kathaṃ pavattā’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ rāgavirāgā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1045350,191,1032,18,22,1,34,4,Yā rāgavirāgā cetovimutti pattabbā. 
1045351,191,1032,23,46,1,184,21,"Tadārammaṇā taṃ cetovimuttiṃ āgamma pavattā taṇhā kusalā anavajjā, yā avijjāvirāgā paññāvimutti pattabbā, tadārammaṇā taṃ paññāvimuttiṃ āgamma pavattā taṇhā kusalā anavajjāti vicayitabbā. "
1045352,191,1032,47,51,1,36,4,Tāya paññāvimuttiyā vasena bhagavatā–
