1045355,191,1035,2,25,1,49,6,"Thinamiddhābhibhū bhikkhu, sabbā duggatiyo jahe’’ ti.( udā.32; netti.31,65,78)– "
1045356,191,1036,2,39,1,155,22,"Gāthāyaṃ ‘‘ sabbā duggatiyo jahe’’ ti padaṃ vuttaṃ,‘‘ tassā paññāvimuttiyā yo pavicayo kātabbo, katamo so pavicayo’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tassā ko pavicayo’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1045357,191,1036,40,64,1,182,19,Tassā paññāvimuttiyā ko pavicayoti ce puccheyya‘‘ aṭṭha maggaṅgāni– sammādiṭṭhi sammāsaṅkappo sammāvācā sammākammanto sammāājīvo sammāvāyāmo sammāsati sammāsamādhī’’ ti pavicayo veditabbo.
1045358,191,1036,65,83,1,70,10,‘‘ So pavicayo kattha daṭṭhabbo’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ so katthā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1045359,191,1036,84,92,1,68,8,So paññāvimuttiyā pavicayo kattha kasmiṃ dhamme daṭṭhabboti pucchati. 
1045360,191,1036,93,101,1,85,8,Catutthe jhāne pāramitāya ukkaṃsagatāya catutthajjhānabhāvanāya so pavicayo daṭṭhabbo.
1045361,191,1037,2,21,1,83,12,‘ ‘ Catutthe jhāne pāramitāyā’’ ti vuttamatthaṃ vivarituṃ‘‘ catutthe hi jhāne’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1045362,191,1037,22,51,1,269,27,"Yo so catutthajjhānalābhī puggalo catutthe jhāne parisuddhaṃ pariyodātaṃ anaṅgaṇaṃ vigatūpakkilesaṃ mudu kammaniyaṃ ṭhitaṃ āneñjappattaṃ, iti aṭṭhaṅgasamannāgataṃ cittaṃ bhāvayati, so catutthajjhānalābhī puggalo tattha catutthe jhāne aṭṭhavidhaṃ vijjācaraṇaṃ adhigacchati. "
1045363,191,1037,52,54,1,19,2,Katamaṃ aṭṭhavidhaṃ? 
1045364,191,1037,55,64,1,50,8,"Cha abhiññā, dve ca visese vā adhigacchatīti yojanā. "
1045365,191,1037,65,74,1,74,8,"Iddhividhādayo pañca, lokiyābhiññā ceva arahattamaggapaññā cāti cha abhiññā. "
1045366,191,1037,75,82,1,56,7,Manomayiddhi ceva vipassanāñāṇañcāti dve ca visesā honti.
1045367,191,1038,2,27,1,123,16,‘ ‘ Taṃ catutthajjhānacittaṃ kuto parisuddhaṃ… pe… kuto āneñjappattan’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ taṃ cittaṃ yato parisuddhan’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1045368,191,1038,28,38,1,107,9,"Taṃ cittaṃ yato upekkhāsatipārisuddhibhāvato parisuddhaṃ, tato upekkhāsatipārisuddhibhāvato pariyodātaṃ hoti. "
1045369,191,1038,39,48,1,114,8,"Sukhādīnaṃ paccayaghātena yato vītarāgādianaṅgaṇabhāvato anaṅgaṇaṃ, tato vītarāgādianaṅgaṇabhāvato vigatūpakkilesaṃ. "
1045370,191,1038,49,56,1,59,6,"Yato subhāvitabhāvato mudu, tato subhāvitabhāvato kammaniyaṃ. "
1045371,191,1038,57,79,1,140,14,"Yato parisuddhādīsu ṭhitabhāvato ṭhitaṃ, tato parisuddhādīsu ṭhitabhāvato āneñjappattaṃ hotītipi yojanā yuttā aṭṭhakathāyaṃ( netti. aṭṭha.53) yugaḷato āgatattā. "
1045372,191,1038,80,83,1,69,3,Saddhāvīriyasatisamādhipaññāobhāsehi pariggahitabhāvato āneñjappattaṃ. 
1045373,191,1038,84,134,1,350,43,"Saddhāya hi pariggahitaṃ cittaṃ paṭipakkhe assaddhiye na iñjati na calati, vīriyena pariggahitaṃ cittaṃ paṭipakkhe kosajje na iñjati, satiyā pariggahitaṃ cittaṃ paṭipakkhe pamāde na iñjati, samādhinā pariggahitaṃ cittaṃ paṭipakkhe uddhacce na iñjati, paññāya pariggahitaṃ cittaṃ paṭipakkhāya avijjāya na iñjati, obhāsagataṃ cittaṃ kilesandhakāre na iñjati. "
1045374,191,1038,135,143,1,77,8,Iti imehi chahi dhammehi pariggahitaṃ catutthajjhānacittaṃ āneñjappattaṃ hoti. 
1045375,191,1038,144,159,1,196,14,"Evaṃ aṭṭhaṅgasamannāgatattā catutthajjhānacittaṃ channaṃ abhiññāñāṇānañca manomayiddhivipassanāñāṇānañca adhigamūpāyo hoti, tasmā so paññāvimuttiparicayo catutthajjhāne daṭṭhabboyevāti saṅkhepattho. "
1045376,191,1038,160,190,1,128,15,Vitthārato pana aṭṭhakathāyaṃ( netti. aṭṭha.53)‘‘ tattha upekkhāsatipārisuddhibhāvenā’’ tiādinā vā‘‘ aparo nayo’’ tiādinā vā vuttoyevāti amhehi na vutto.
1045377,191,1039,2,40,1,248,27,"‘ ‘ Yesaṃ rāgādiaṅgaṇānaṃ abhāvena anaṅgaṇaṃ, yesaṃ abhijjhādiupakkilesānaṃ abhāvena vigatūpakkilesaṃ, yāya cittassa ṭhitiyā abhāvena ṭhitaṃ, iñjanāya abhāvena āneñjappattaṃ, te rāgādiaṅgaṇādayo katamāya pakkhā’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha aṅgaṇā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1045378,191,1039,41,63,1,236,19,"{Tatthā}ti tesu rāgādiaṅgaṇādīsu aṅgaṇā ca rāgādiaṅgaṇā ca upakkilesā abhijjhādiupakkilesā ca santi, tadubhayaṃ rāgādiaṅgaṇaabhijjhādiupakkilesadvayaṃ taṇhāpakkho rāgādiaṅgaṇānaṃ taṇhāsabhāvattā, abhijjhādiupakkilesānañca taṇhāya anulomattā. "
1045379,191,1039,64,85,1,164,20,"Yā iñjanā phandanā yā ca cittassa aṭṭhiti anavaṭṭhānaṃ atthi, ayaṃ iñjanā aṭṭhiti diṭṭhipakkho iñjanāya ca aṭṭhitiyā ca micchābhinivesahetubhāvatoti pavicayo kātabbo."
1045380,191,1040,2,25,1,176,16,‘ ‘ Kiṃ pana catutthajjhānacittaṃ aṭṭhaṅgasamannāgatattāyeva channaṃ abhiññāñāṇānañca manomayiddhivipassanāñāṇānañca adhigamūpāyo hotī’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ cattāri indriyānī’’ ti vuttaṃ.
1045381,191,1040,26,92,1,574,51,"‘‘ Tassa catutthajjhānalābhino, dukkhindriyaṃ domanassindriyaṃ sukhindriyaṃ somanassindriyaṃ iti cattārindriyāni catutthajjhāne nirujjhanti, tassa catutthajjhānalābhino upekkhindriyaṃ avasiṭṭhaṃ bhavati, tasmāpi catutthajjhānacittaṃ vuttappakārānaṃ aṭṭhannaṃ ñāṇānaṃ adhigamūpāyo hoti, so ca adhigamūpāyabhāvo ciṇṇavasībhāvasseva bhaveyya, kathaṃ catutthajjhānamattalābhino ciṇṇavasībhāvo siyā’’ ti vattabbattā so catutthajjhānalābhī catutthajjhāneyeva aṭṭhatvā arūpasamāpattiyopi evaṃ katvā nibbatteti bhāveti, tasmā ciṇṇavasībhāvo hotīti dassetuṃ‘‘ so uparimaṃ samāpattin’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1045382,191,1040,93,108,1,69,7,"Tassattho aṭṭhakathāyaṃ( netti. aṭṭha.53) vitthārato vutto, tasmā yojanamattaṃ karissāma. "
1045383,191,1041,2,14,1,150,11,So rūpāvacaracatutthajjhānalābhī yogāvacaro rūpāvacaracatutthajjhānasamāpattito uparimaṃ ākāsānañcāyatana samāpattiṃ santato santatarato manasi karoti. 
1045384,191,1041,15,68,1,477,47,"Yathāvuttaṃ uparimaṃ samāpattiṃ santato manasi karoto tassa catutthajjhānalābhino yogāvacarassa catutthajjhāne saññā saññāpadhānā samāpatti oḷārikā viya hutvā saṇṭhahati, paṭighasaññā ca ukkaṇṭhā anabhirati hutvā saṇṭhahati, so yathāvuttena vidhinā manasi karonto yogāvacaro sabbaso niravasesato rūpasaññānaṃ samatikkamā paṭighasaññānaṃ atthaṅgamā nānattasaññānaṃ amanasikārā‘‘ ākāsaṃ anantan’’ ti manasi katvā pavattamānaṃ ākāsānañcāyatanasamāpattiṃ sacchikatvā upasampajja viharati. "
1045385,191,1041,69,74,1,58,5,Rūpasaññā rūpāvacarasaññā pañcavidha abhiññābhinīhāro hoti. 
1045386,191,1041,75,80,1,51,5,Nānattasaññā nānārammaṇesu vokāro akusalo pavattati. 
1045387,191,1041,81,96,1,145,14,"Evaṃ rūpāvacarajjhāne ādīnavadassī hutvā tā rūpasaññānānattasaññāyo ārammaṇe samatikkamati, assa yogāvacarassa paṭighasaññā ca abbhatthaṃ gacchati. "
1045388,191,1041,97,110,1,151,12,"Evaṃ iminā vuttanayena samatikkamena samāhitassa, santavuttinā arūpāvacarasamādhinā samāhitassa yogāvacarassa obhāso rūpāvacarajjhānobhāso antaradhāyati. "
1045389,191,1041,111,117,1,69,6,Rūpānaṃ kasiṇarūpānaṃ jhānacakkhunā dassanañca antaradhāyatīti yojanā.
1045390,191,1042,2,35,1,188,23,"‘ ‘ Yena samādhinā samāhitassa, samāhitassa obhāso ca rūpānaṃ dassanañca antaradhāyati, so samādhi kittakehi aṅgehi samannāgato, kathaṃ paccavekkhitabbo’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ so samādhī’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1045391,191,1042,36,66,1,283,27,"So {samādhī}ti yena rūpārūpāvacarasamādhinā samāhito, so duvidhopi samādhi anabhijjhābyāpādavīriyārambhehi tīhi upakārakaṅgehi ca passaddhisatīhi dvīhi parikkhāraṅgehi ca avikkhittena ekena sabhāvaṅgena ca chahi aṅgehi samannāgatoti paccavekkhitabbo punappunaṃ cintetabbo sallakkhetabbo ."
1045392,191,1042,67,86,1,103,11,‘‘ Kathaṃ kattha paccavekkhitabbo’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ anabhijjhāsahagataṃ me mānasaṃ sabbaloke’’ tiādi vuttaṃ.
1045393,191,1042,87,115,1,141,18,"‘‘ Tesu chasu aṅgesu kittako samatho, kittakā vipassanā’’ ti pucchitabbattā ettako samatho, ettakā vipassanāti vibhajituṃ‘‘ tattha yañcā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1045394,191,1043,2,42,1,260,24,"54.‘‘ Paññāvimuttī’’ ti vuttassa arahattaphalassa samādhissa samathavipassanāsaṅkhātā pubbabhāgapaṭipadā samādhimukhena ācariyena vibhattā,‘‘ tāya paṭipadāya labhitabbo arahattaphalasamādhi kittakena veditabbo’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ so samādhi pañcavidhena veditabbo’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
1045395,191,1043,43,53,1,122,9,"Yo arahattaphalasamādhi samathavipassanāpaṭipadāya labhitabbo, so arahattaphalasamādhi pañcavidhena ñāṇadassanena veditabbo."
1045396,191,1044,2,21,1,94,11,‘ ‘ Kathaṃ pañcavidhañāṇadassanaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ bhavatī’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ ayaṃ samādhī’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1045397,191,1044,22,37,1,172,14,"Ayaṃ arahattaphalasamādhi appitappitakkhaṇe phalasamāpattisukhattā paccuppannasukho hoti, iti paccavekkhantassa assa arahato paccattameva ñāṇadassanaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ bhavati. "
1045398,191,1044,38,54,1,152,13,"Ayaṃ arahattaphalasamādhi āyatiṃ samāpajjitabbassa arahattaphalasamādhissa upanissayapaccayattā āyatiṃ sukhavipāko hoti, iti paccavekkhantassa… pe… bhavati. "
1045399,191,1044,55,73,1,140,14,"Ayaṃ arahattaphalasamādhi kilesaarīhi ārakattā ariyo, kāmāmisavaṭṭāmisalokāmisānaṃ abhāvato nirāmiso ca hoti, iti paccavekkhantassa… pe… bhavati. "
1045400,191,1044,74,88,1,146,11,"Ayaṃ arahattaphalasamādhi akāpurisehi sammāsambuddhapaccekabuddhasāvakabuddhehi sevitabbattā akāpurisasevito hoti, iti paccavekkhantassa… pe… bhavati. "
1045401,191,1044,89,142,1,623,49,"Ayaṃ arahattaphalasamādhi aṅgasantakilesadarathasantattā santo ceva divasampi samāpajjantassa atittikaraṇato paṇīto ca paṭippassaddhakilesena arahatā puggalena laddhattā paṭippassaddhiladdho ca arahattamaggasamādhisaṅkhātena ekodibhāvena adhigatattā ekodibhāvādhigato ca sasaṅkhārena sapayogena adhigatattā, nīvaraṇādipaccanīkadhamme niggayha anadhigatattā, aññe kilese vāretvā anadhigatattā, arahattamaggaphalabhāveneva pavattattā nasasaṅkhāraniggayhavāritagato hoti, iti paccavekkhantassa assa arahato paccattameva ñāṇadassanaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ bhavatīti pañcavidhena ñāṇadassanena so arahattaphalasamādhi vicayitvā veditabboti."
1045402,191,1045,2,27,1,134,16,"‘ ‘ Paccuppannasukhādīsu samādhīsu kittako samatho, kittakā vipassanā’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha yo ca samādhi paccuppannasukho’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1045403,191,1045,28,38,1,96,7,"Samatho, {vipassanā}ti ca arahattaphalasamathavipassanāva adhippetā, na pubbabhāgasamathavipassanāti. "
1045404,191,1045,39,68,1,209,20,"Arahattaphalasamādhi pañcavidhena veditabboti ācariyena vutto,‘‘ tassa arahattaphalasamādhissa pubbabhāgapaṭipadāyaṃ vutto samādhi kittakena veditabbo’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ so samādhi pañcavidhena veditabbo’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
1045405,191,1045,69,79,1,129,9,"Yo rūpāvacaracatutthajjhānasamādhi pubbabhāgapaṭipadāyaṃ vutto, so rūpāvacaracatutthajjhānasamādhi pañcavidhena pakārena veditabbo."
