1045414,191,1046,2,32,1,140,16,"55. Sampayogavasena samādhi ācariyena vibhatto, amhehi ca ñāto,‘‘ kathaṃ ārammaṇavasena vibhatto’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ dasa kasiṇāyatanānī’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
