1045490,191,1073,2,4,1,25,2,3 . Yuttihārasampātavibhāvanā 
1045491,191,1074,2,38,1,201,21,"65. Yena yena vicayahārasampātena suttappadesatthā ācariyena vicayitabbā, amhehi ca ñātā, so vicayahārasampāto paripuṇṇo,‘‘ katamo yuttihārasampāto’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha katamo yuttihārasampāto’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1045492,191,1074,39,41,1,18,2,Aṭṭhakathāyaṃ pana–
1045493,191,1074,42,69,1,139,14,‘‘ evaṃ nānānayehi vicayahārasampātaṃ vitthāretvā idāni yuttihārasampātādīni dassetuṃ‘ tattha katamo yuttihārasampāto’ tiādi āraddhan’’ ti( netti. aṭṭha.65) vuttaṃ. 
1045494,191,1074,70,94,1,214,20,"{Tatthā}ti tesu desanāhārasampātādīsu soḷasasu hārasampātesu katamo saṃvaṇṇanāviseso yuttihārasampāto nāmāti pucchati, pucchitvā yasmiṃ suttappadese vuttānaṃ atthānaṃ yuttibhāvo vicāretabbo, taṃ suttappadesaṃ nīharituṃ–"
1045495,191,1075,2,8,1,42,4,"‘ ‘ Tasmā rakkhitacittassa, sammāsaṅkappagocaro; "
1045496,191,1076,2,6,1,41,3,"Sammādiṭṭhipurekkhāro , ñatvāna udayabbayaṃ; "
1045497,191,1077,2,23,1,49,6,"Thinamiddhābhibhū bhikkhu, sabbā duggatiyo jahe’’ ti.( udā.32; netti.31,78)– "
1045498,191,1078,2,3,1,6,1,Vuttaṃ . 
1045499,191,1078,4,53,1,556,45,"Tassaṃ gāthāyaṃ tasmā arakkhitacittassa māravasānugatattā satisaṃvaraindriyasaṃvarādivasena bhikkhu rakkhitacitto assa bhaveyya, tasmā kāmavitakkādimicchāsaṅkappagocarassa māravasānugatattā nekkhammasaṅkappādivasena bhikkhu sammāsaṅkappagocaro assa bhaveyya, tasmā micchādiṭṭhihatacittassa māravasānugatattā yonisomanasikārena bhikkhu udayabbayaṃ ñatvāna sammādiṭṭhipurekkhāro assa bhaveyya, tasmā thinamiddhena hatacittassa māravasānugatattā vīriyavasena bhikkhu thinamiddhābhibhū assa bhaveyya, tādiso bhikkhu sabbā duggatiyo jahe jahissatīti attho veditabbo."
1045500,191,1079,2,21,1,97,12,‘ ‘ Tassaṃ gāthāyaṃ kathaṃ yuttibhāvo vicāretabbo’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ tasmā rakkhitacittassā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1045501,191,1079,22,32,1,81,9,"Rakkhitacittassa sammāsaṅkappagocaro bhavissatīti attho yujjati eva, no na yujjati. "
1045502,191,1079,33,44,1,166,11,Micchāsaṅkappānampi jahitattā sammādiṭṭhipurekkhāro hutvā viharanto udayabbayaṃ paṭivijjhissatīti attho yujjati sammādiṭṭhipurekkhārassa udayabbayānupassanāsambhavato. 
1045503,191,1079,45,55,1,117,9,Udayabbayaṃ paṭivijjhanto sabbā duggatiyo jahissatīti attho yujjati udayabbayānupassanānukkamena ariyamaggasambhavato. 
1045504,191,1079,56,67,1,134,11,Sabbā duggatiyo jahanto sabbāni duggativinipātabhayāni samatikkamissatīti attho yujjati sabbesaṃ duggativinipātabhayānaṃ anuppajjanato.
1045505,191,1080,2,19,1,85,10,‘ ‘ Ettakova yuttihārasampāto paripuṇṇo’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ niyutto yuttihārasampāto’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1045506,191,1080,20,39,1,202,17,"Yena yena saṃvaṇṇanāvisesabhūtena yuttihārasampātena suttappadesatthānaṃ yuttibhāvo vicāretabbo , so so saṃvaṇṇanāvisesabhūto yuttihārasampāto niyutto yathārahaṃ niddhāretvā yujjitabboti attho gahetabboti. "
