1045608,191,1127,20,61,1,233,30,"Yā‘‘ tasmā… pe… gocaro’’ ti gāthā vuttā, tāya gāthāya yā samathavipassanā niddhāritā, tāya samathavipassanāya bhāvitāya akusalānaṃ nirodho phalaṃ payojanaṃ hoti, pariññātaṃ dukkhaṃ hoti, samudayo pahīno hoti, maggo bhāvito hotīti parivattetabbo. "
1045609,191,1127,62,79,1,142,14,"Paṭipakkhena pana samathavipassanāya abhāvitāya akusalānaṃ anirodho, apariññātaṃ dukkhaṃ, samudayo appahīno, maggo abhāvito hotīti parivattetabbo."
1045610,191,1128,2,20,1,98,11,‘ ‘ Ettakova parivattanahārasampāto paripuṇṇo’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ niyutto parivattano hārasampāto’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1045611,191,1128,21,38,1,201,16,"Yena yena saṃvaṇṇanāvisesabhūtena parivattanahārasampātena suttappadesatthā parivattetabbā, so so saṃvaṇṇanāvisesabhūto parivattanahārasampāto niyutto yathārahaṃ nīharitvā yujjitabboti attho gahetabboti. "
