1045615,191,1132,2,4,1,28,2,10 . Vevacanahārasampātavibhāvanā 
1045616,191,1133,2,36,1,200,20,"72. Yena yena parivattanahārasampātena suttappadesatthā parivattetabbā, so parivattano hārasampātoti paripuṇṇo,‘‘ katamo vevacano hārasampāto’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha katamo vevacano hārasampāto’’ tiādi vuttaṃ."
1045617,191,1134,2,23,1,103,12,"‘ ‘ Katamesaṃ suttappadesatthānaṃ, suttapadānaṃ vā katamāni vevacanānī’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tasmā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1045618,191,1134,24,96,1,256,35,"Yā‘‘ tasmā… pe… gocaro’’ ti gāthā vuttā, tāya gāthāya‘‘ rakkhitacittassā’’ ti padena vuttassa cittassa,‘‘ rakkhitacittassā’’ ti ettha cittassa padassa vā‘‘ cittaṃ… pe… vijānitattan’’ ti yaṃ vacanaṃ vuttaṃ, idaṃ vacanaṃ vevacanaṃ,‘‘ mānasaṃ hadayan’’ tiādivacanampi( dha. sa.17,63) cittassa vevacanaṃ."
1045619,191,1134,97,138,1,200,20,"‘‘ Sammāsaṅkappagocaro’’ ti ettha sammāsaṅkappassa‘‘ nekkhammasaṅkappo abyāpādasaṅkappo avihiṃsāsaṅkappo’’ ti yaṃ vacanaṃ vuttaṃ, idaṃ vacanaṃ vevacanaṃ,‘‘ takko vitakko’’ tiādi( dha. sa.7) vacanampi sammāsaṅkappassa vevacanaṃ."
1045620,191,1134,139,185,1,241,25,"‘‘ Sammādiṭṭhipurekkhāro’’ ti ettha sammādiṭṭhipadassa‘‘ sammādiṭṭhi nāma paññāsatthaṃ paññākhaggo paññāratanaṃ paññāpatodo paññāpāsādo’’ ti yaṃ vacanaṃ vuttaṃ, idaṃ vacanaṃ vevacanaṃ,‘‘ paññā pajānanā vicayo’’ tiādi( dha. sa.16) vacanampi sammādiṭṭhipadassa vevacanaṃ."
1045621,191,1134,186,217,1,148,18,"‘‘ Thinaṃ thiyanā thiyitattaṃ cittassa, cittassa akallatā akammaññatā onāho pariyonāho antosaṅkoco’’ ti( dha. sa.1162-1163) yaṃ vacanaṃ vuttaṃ, idaṃ vacanaṃ thinassa vevacanaṃ."
1045622,191,1134,218,245,1,121,15,"‘‘ Kāyassa akallatā akammaññatā kāyālasiyaṃ soppaṃ supanā suppitattan’’ ti( dha. sa.1163) yaṃ vacanaṃ vuttaṃ, idaṃ vacanaṃ middhassa vevacanaṃ."
1045623,191,1134,246,270,1,84,10,"‘‘ Bhikkhako bhikkhū’’ tiādikaṃ( pārā.45; vibha.510) yaṃ vacanaṃ vuttaṃ, idaṃ vacanaṃ bhikkhupadassa vevacanaṃ."
1045624,191,1134,271,289,1,110,13,"‘‘ Duggati apāyo vinipāto vaṭṭadukkhaṃ saṃsāro’’ tiādikaṃ yaṃ vacanaṃ vuttaṃ, idaṃ vacanaṃ duggatipadassa vevacanaṃ. "
