1045631,191,1139,2,4,1,28,2,11 . Paññattihārasampātavibhāvanā 
1045632,191,1140,2,33,1,181,17,"73. Yena yena vevacanahārasampātena vevacanāni niddhāritāni, so vevacanahārasampāto paripuṇṇo,‘‘ katamo paññattihārasampāto’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha katamo paññattihārasampāto’’ tiādi vuttaṃ."
1045633,191,1141,2,21,1,100,12,‘ ‘ Katamā suttappadesabhūtā paññatti katamesaṃ dhammānaṃ paññattī’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tasmā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ.
1045634,191,1141,22,38,1,122,12,‘‘ Tasmā rakkhitacittassā’’ ti paññatti satiyā padaṭṭhānassa rakkhitabbassa cittassa paññāpanato satiyā padaṭṭhānapaññatti nāma. 
1045635,191,1141,39,47,1,65,8,Satiyā hi rakkhitabbaṃ cittaṃ satiyā padaṭṭhānaṃ adhiṭṭhānaṃ nāma. 
