1045638,191,1141,66,79,1,96,9,‘‘ Sammāsaṅkappagocaro’’ ti paññatti samathassa bhāvanāya paññāpanato samathassa bhāvanāpaññatti nāma.
1045639,191,1141,80,95,1,114,10,"‘‘ Sammādiṭṭhipurekkhāro, ñatvāna udayabbayan’’ ti paññatti dassanabhūmiyā nikkhepassa paññāpanato nikkhepapaññatti nāma."
1045640,191,1141,96,108,1,102,8,‘‘ Thinamiddhābhibhū bhikkhū’’ ti samudayassa anavasesappahānassa paññāpanato anavasesappahānapaññatti nāma.
1045641,191,1141,109,124,1,98,11,‘‘ Sabbā duggatiyo jahe’’ ti paññatti maggassa ariyamaggassa bhāvanāya paññāpanato bhāvanāpaññatti nāma.
