1045647,191,1146,2,4,1,27,2,12 . Otaraṇahārasampātavibhāvanā 
1045648,191,1147,2,34,1,182,18,"74. Yena yena paññattihārasampātena paññattippabhedā niddhāritā, so paññattihārasampāto paripuṇṇo,‘‘ katamo otaraṇo hārasampāto’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha katamo otaraṇo hārasampāto’’ tiādimāha."
1045649,191,1148,2,25,1,130,16,‘ ‘ Tattha tissaṃ gāthāyaṃ katamāni indriyāni niddhāretvā katamehi niddhāritehi dhammehi otaratī’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tasmā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1045650,191,1148,26,58,1,193,20,"Yā‘‘ tasmā rakkhitacittassā’’ tiādigāthā vuttā, tissaṃ gāthāyaṃ‘‘ tasmā… pe… purekkhāro’’ ti suttappadesena sammādiṭṭhi gahitā, sammādiṭṭhiyā gahitāya pañcindriyāni saddhādipañcindriyāni gahitāni bhavanti. "
1045651,191,1149,2,29,1,244,23,"Tāniyeva saddhādipañcindriyāni vijjāya upakārattā vā padaṭṭhānattā vā vijjā bhavanti, vijjuppādā tādisāya vijjāya uppādā uppādahetuto avijjānirodho sambhavati, avijjānirodhā saṅkhāranirodho sambhavati… pe… jātinirodhā jarāmaraṇanirodho sambhavatīti. "
1045652,191,1149,30,36,1,59,6,Ayaṃ otaraṇā paṭiccasamuppādena pañcindriyānaṃ otaraṇā nāma. 
1045653,191,1150,2,17,1,165,14,"Tāniyeva pañcindriyāni sīlakkhandhena samādhikkhandhena paññākkhandhena tīhi khandhehi saṅgahitāni bhavanti saddhāvīriyehi sīlasambhavato, satiyā ca paññānuvattakattā. "
1045654,191,1150,18,24,1,50,6,Ayaṃ otaraṇā khandhehi pañcindriyānaṃ otaraṇā nāma. 
1045655,191,1151,2,6,1,53,4,Tāniyeva pañcindriyāni saṅkhārapariyāpannāni bhavanti. 
1045656,191,1151,7,24,1,136,15,"Ye saṅkhārā anāsavā bhavanti, bhavaṅgā bhavahetū no bhavanti, te anāsavā saṅkhārā dhammadhātusaṅgahitā bhavanti dhammadhātuyā antogadhattā. "
1045657,191,1151,25,31,1,48,6,Ayaṃ otaraṇā dhātūhi pañcindriyānaṃ otaraṇā nāma. 
1045658,191,1152,2,18,1,115,13,"Sā anāsavā dhammadhātu dhammāyatanapariyāpannā bhavati, yaṃ āyatanaṃ anāsavaṃ bhavati, bhavaṅgaṃ bhavahetu no bhavati. "
1045659,191,1152,19,25,1,49,6,Ayaṃ otaraṇā āyatanehi dhammadhātuyā otaraṇā nāma.
