1045667,191,1158,2,4,1,27,2,13 . Sodhanahārasampātavibhāvanā 
1045668,191,1159,2,9,1,21,3,75. {Yatthā}ti yasmiṃ pañhe. 
1045669,191,1159,10,20,1,71,9,"Ārambho attho suddho paripuṇṇo, so pañho niravasesato vissajjito bhavati. "
1045670,191,1159,21,39,1,117,17,"Yattha pañhe pana ārambho attho na suddho aparipuṇṇo koci vissajjetabbo avasiṭṭho, so pañho tāva vissajjito na bhavati."
1045671,191,1160,2,4,1,30,2,15 . Parikkhārahārasampātavibhāvanā 
1045672,191,1161,2,21,1,92,11,"77.‘‘ Tasmā rakkhitacittassā’’ ti padena yo satisaṃvaro vutto, ayaṃ satisaṃvaro samathassa parikkhāro."
1045673,191,1161,22,39,1,115,12,"‘‘ Sammāsaṅkappagocaro’’ ti padena yo sammāsaṅkappo vutto, so sammāsaṅkappo vipassanāya parikkhāroti vibhajitvā yojetabbo."
1045674,191,1162,2,4,1,30,2,16 . Samāropanahārasampātavibhāvanā 
1045675,191,1163,2,25,1,117,13,"78.‘‘ Tasmā rakkhitacittassā’’ ti padena yaṃ rakkhitacittaṃ vuttaṃ, taṃ rakkhitacittaṃ tiṇṇaṃ sucaritānaṃ kammānaṃ padaṭṭhānaṃ. "
1045676,191,1163,26,38,1,105,11,"Sammādiṭṭhiyā bhāvitāya ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo bhāvito bhavati ekato bhāvitabbattā, padaṭṭhānakāraṇattā ca. "
1045677,191,1163,39,41,1,11,2,Tena vuttaṃ–
1045678,191,1163,42,49,1,23,3,‘‘ sammādiṭṭhito hī’’ tiādi. 
1045679,191,1163,50,64,1,112,12,"Yassa arahato samādhivimutti bhavati, ayaṃ arahā anupādiseso puggalo, ayaṃ samādhivimutti anupādisesā nibbānadhātu."
1045680,191,1164,2,27,1,178,17,"‘ ‘ Desanāhārasampātādiko hārasampāto yena soḷasappabhedabhāvena suttappadesatthe niddhāretvā yujjito, soḷasappabhedabhāvo kena amhehi saddahitabbo’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ tenāhā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1045681,191,1164,28,51,1,136,16,"Tena soḷasappabhedabhāvena āyasmā mahākaccāno‘‘ soḷasa… pe… suttan’’ ti yaṃ vacanaṃ āha, tena vacanena soḷasappabhedabhāvo tumhehi saddahitabbo."
1045682,191,1165,2,19,1,75,10,‘ ‘ Ettakova hārasampāto paripuṇṇo’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ niyutto hārasampāto’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
