1045687,191,1169,2,2,1,23,1,Nayasamuṭṭhānavibhāvanā 
1045688,191,1170,2,37,1,265,21,"79. Yena yena saṃvaṇṇanāvisesabhūtena desanāhārasampātādinā hārasampātena ekasuttappadesatthā niddhāretvā vibhattā, so saṃvaṇṇanāvisesabhūto desanāhārasampātādihārasampāto paripuṇṇo,‘‘ katamaṃ nayasamuṭṭhānan’’ ti pucchitabbattā‘‘ tattha katamaṃ nayasamuṭṭhānan’’ tiādi āraddhaṃ. "
1045689,191,1170,38,40,1,18,2,Aṭṭhakathāyaṃ pana–
1045690,191,1170,41,72,1,143,16,"‘‘ evaṃ nānāsuttavasena, ekasuttavasena ca hāravicāraṃ dassetvā idāni nayavicāraṃ dassetuṃ‘ tattha katamaṃ nayasamuṭṭhānan’ tiādi āraddhan’’ ti( netti. aṭṭha.79) vuttaṃ."
1045691,191,1170,73,93,1,129,12,‘‘ Tattha katamo nandiyāvaṭṭanayo’’ tiādiṃ anārabhitvā‘‘ tattha katamaṃ nayasamuṭṭhānan’’ tiādiārambhane kāraṇaṃ aṭṭhakathāyaṃ vuttameva. 
1045692,191,1170,94,116,1,145,16,"Tattha {tatthā}ti tesu hārādīsu yo atthanayo saṃvaṇṇanānayena niddiṭṭho, tasseva atthanayassa samuṭṭhānaṃ bhūmiṃ pucchati‘‘ katamaṃ nayasamuṭṭhānan’’ ti. "
1045693,191,1171,2,13,1,109,10,"Kiñcāpi saṃvaṇṇanānayā niddiṭṭhā, tathāpi atthanayasaṃvaṇṇanānayānaṃ visesassa pākaṭaṃ kātuṃ puna kathayissāma. "
1045694,191,1171,14,31,1,234,17,Taṇhāavijjāhi saṃkilesapakkhassa suttatthassa catusaccayojanamukhena nayanalakkhaṇo saṃvaṇṇanāviseso ceva samathavipassanāhi vodānapakkhassa suttatthassa catusaccayojanamukhena nayanalakkhaṇo saṃvaṇṇanāviseso ca nandiyāvaṭṭo nayo nāma. 
1045695,191,1171,32,53,1,257,21,Tīhi akusalamūlehi lobhādīhi saṃkilesapakkhassa suttatthassa catusaccayojanamukhena nayanalakkhaṇo saṃvaṇṇanāviseso ceva tīhi kusalamūlehi alobhādīhi vodānapakkhassa suttatthassa catusaccayojanamukhena nayanalakkhaṇo saṃvaṇṇanāviseso ca tipukkhalo nayo nāma. 
1045696,191,1171,54,83,1,344,28,"Catūhi subhasaññādīhi vipallāsehi sakalasaṃkilesapakkhassa suttatthassa catusaccayojanamukhena nayanalakkhaṇo saṃvaṇṇanāviseso ceva catūhi asubhasaññādīhi avipallāsehi satipaṭṭhānehi, saddhindriyehi vā vodānapakkhassa suttatthassa catusaccayojanamukhena nayanalakkhaṇo saṃvaṇṇanāviseso ca sīhavikkīḷito nayo nāmāti vuttā nayā saṃvaṇṇanānayā nāma. "
1045697,191,1171,84,95,1,71,7,Tesaṃ saṃvaṇṇanānayānaṃ samuṭṭhānaṃ pucchati‘‘ katamaṃ nayasamuṭṭhānan’’ ti. 
1045698,191,1172,2,12,1,116,10,Nayā pana nānāsuttato niddhāritehi taṇhāavijjādīhi mūlapadehi catusaccayojanāya nayato anubujjhiyamāno dukkhādiattho. 
1045699,191,1172,13,29,1,67,11,"So hi maggañāṇaṃ nayati sampāpetīti‘‘ nayo’’ ti vutto, so atthanayo nāma. "
1045700,191,1172,30,41,1,68,7,Tasseva atthanayassa samuṭṭhānaṃ pucchati‘‘ katamaṃ nayasamuṭṭhānan’’ ti? 
1045701,191,1172,42,52,1,69,8,"Tasmā catusaccayojanāya nayaggāhato nīyati anupucchīyatīti nayo, ko so? "
1045702,191,1172,53,56,1,31,3,Suttatthabhūto dukkhādiko attho. 
1045703,191,1172,57,65,1,53,7,"Nayati maggañāṇaṃ pāpetīti vā nayo, dukkhādiko atthova. "
1045704,191,1172,66,67,1,6,1,Tenāha–
1045705,191,1172,68,72,1,29,2,‘‘ anubujjhiyamāno dukkhādiattho. 
1045706,191,1172,73,89,1,43,7,So hi maggañāṇaṃ nayati sampāpetīti nayo’’ ti( netti. aṭṭha.79). 
1045707,191,1172,90,97,1,46,6,"Samuṭṭhahanti nayā etenāti samuṭṭhānaṃ, kiṃ taṃ? "
1045708,191,1172,98,103,1,44,4,"Avijjātaṇhādikāraṇaṃ, taṃdīpanā saṃvaṇṇanā ca. "
1045709,191,1172,104,108,1,48,4,Avijjātaṇhādinā hi dukkhādiatthanayā sambhavanti. 
1045710,191,1172,109,115,1,56,6,Atha vā avijjātaṇhādīhi catusaccayojanā samuṭṭhānaṃ nāma. 
