1045943,191,1210,92,97,1,30,4,{Tatthā}ti tesu catūsu puggalesu. 
1045944,191,1210,98,102,1,24,3,{Yo}ti udatto diṭṭhicarito. 
1045945,191,1210,103,109,1,39,6,Ayan ti ayaṃ niyato udatto diṭṭhicarito. 
1045946,191,1210,110,119,1,55,8,Puna {yo}ti udattova taṇhācarito ca mando diṭṭhicarito ca. 
1045947,191,1210,120,130,1,88,9,{Sādhāraṇāyā}ti dukkhāya paṭipadāya khippābhiññāya ca sukhāya paṭipadāya dandhābhiññāya ca.
