1045949,191,1211,33,62,1,185,19,"Atha vā‘‘ paṭipadābhedena puggalabhedo ācariyena vibhāvito, kathaṃ desanābhedena puggalabhedo vibhāvito’’ ti vattabbattā desanābhedenapi puggalabhedaṃ vibhāvetuṃ‘‘ tattha bhagavā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1045950,191,1211,63,69,1,46,5,{Tatthā}ti tesu tīsu ugghaṭitaññuādīsu puggalesu.
