1046539,191,1454,22,24,1,12,2,Kinti vadati? 
1046540,191,1454,25,70,1,230,31,"Attanā phuṭṭhaṃ dukkhaṃ abhāvitakāyatāya adhivāsetuṃ asakkonto hutvā‘‘ aho dukkhaṃ, īdisaṃ dukkhaṃ mayhaṃ sattunopi mā hotū’’ tiādinā rodanto vilapanto vadati,‘‘ kasmā evaṃ vadatī’’ ti vattabbattā‘‘ attato yena yena hi maññantī’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1046541,191,1454,71,93,1,158,21,"Ete sattā yena yena kāmajjhosādinā pakārena attato dukkhassa paṭikāraṃ maññanti, tato pakārato aññathā aññena pakārena taṃ dukkhaṃ tikicchitabbaṃ hi yasmā hoti. "
1046542,191,1455,2,24,1,148,19,"{Aññathābhāvī}ti yasmā rodaṃ rodanto vadati, yena yena vā paravihiṃsādipakārena attano vaḍḍhiṃ maññanti āsīsanti, tato pakārato aññathā avaḍḍhi eva hoti. "
1046543,191,1455,25,49,1,178,22,"Taṃ āsīsitabbaṃ aññathābhāvi avaḍḍhitabhāvi eva hi yasmā hoti, tasmā maññitabbassa āsīsitabbassa aññathā bhavanasīlattā rodaṃ rodanto vadati, ayaṃ sattaloko rodanto ca hutvā vadati."
