1049503,192,407,56,90,1,294,30,"Tathā veneyyānaṃ sabbaso ekadesato ca maññanānaṃ appahānaṃ, tattha ca ādīnavādassanaṃ, niraṅkusānaṃ maññanānaṃ anekākāravohārassa sakkāye pavattivisesassa ajānanaṃ, tattha ca pahīnamaññanānaṃ paṭipattiyā ajānanaṃ, taṇhāmukhena paccayākārassa ca anavabodhoti evamādīni ca payojanāni idha veditabbāni. "
1049504,192,408,2,15,1,251,13,Bhūmittayapariyāpannesu asaṅkhātadhammavippakatapariññādikiccasaṅkhātadhammānaṃ sammāsambuddhassa ca paṭipattiṃ ajānantā asaddhammassavanadhāraṇaparicayamanasikāraparā saddhammassavana-dhāraṇaparicayapaṭivedhavimukhā ca veneyyā imissā desanāya bhājanaṃ. 
1049505,192,408,16,44,1,477,22,Piṇḍatthā pana‘‘ assutavā’’ tiādinā ayonisomanasikārabahulīkāro akusalamūla-samāyogo olīyanātidhāvanāpariggaho upāyavinibaddhānubrūhanā micchābhinivesasamannāgamo avijjātaṇhā-parisuddhi vaṭṭattayānuparamo āsavoghayogaganthāgatitaṇhuppādupādānāviyogo cetokhila-cetovinibaddhaabhinandana-nīvaraṇasaṅgānatikkamo vivādamūlāpariccāgo anusayānupacchedo micchattānativattanaṃ taṇhāmūladhammasannissayatā akusalakammapathānuyogo sabbakilesa-pariḷāhasāraddhakāyacittatāti evamādayo dīpitā honti.
1049506,192,408,45,66,1,256,17,‘‘ Pathaviṃ pathavito sañjānātī’’ tiādinā taṇhāvicaritaniddeso mānajappanā vipariyesābhiniveso saṃkileso sakkāyapariggaho bālalakkhaṇāpadeso vaṅkattayavibhāvanānuyogo bahukārapaṭipakkhadīpanā tividhanissayasaṃsūcanā āsavakkhayakathananti evamādayo dīpitā honti. 
1049507,192,409,2,2,1,17,1,Soḷasahāravaṇṇanā 
1049508,192,410,2,4,1,17,2,1 . Desanāhāravaṇṇanā 
1049509,192,411,2,17,1,188,14,"Tattha ye upādānakkhandhadhamme upādāya pathavīādibhūtādibhedā paññatti, te paññattipaṭipādanabhāvena jātijarāmaraṇavisesanadukkhapariyāyena ca vuttā taṇhāvajjā tebhūmakadhammā dukkhasaccaṃ. "
1049510,192,411,18,22,1,59,4,Maññanābhinandananandīpariyāyehi vuttā taṇhā samudayasaccaṃ. 
1049511,192,411,23,26,1,22,3,Ayaṃ tāva suttantanayo. 
1049512,192,411,27,51,1,195,18,"Abhidhammanaye pana yathāvuttataṇhāya saddhiṃ‘‘ assutavā’’ tiādinā dīpitā avijjādayo, maññanāpariyāyena gahitā mānadiṭṭhiyo, bhavapadena gahito kammabhavo cāti sabbepi kilesābhisaṅkhārā samudayasaccaṃ. "
1049513,192,411,52,55,1,32,3,Ubhinnaṃ appavatti nirodhasaccaṃ. 
1049514,192,411,56,65,1,112,6,"Ariyadhammaggahaṇena, pariññābhikkhusekkhābhiññāgahaṇehi, rāgādikhayavacanehi, sammāsambodhigahaṇena ca maggasaccaṃ. "
1049515,192,411,66,79,1,138,12,"Keci pana taṇhākkhayādivacanehi nirodhasaccaṃ uddharanti, taṃ aṭṭhakathāya virujjhati tattha taṇhākkhayādīnaṃ maggakiccabhāvassa uddhaṭattā. "
1049516,192,412,2,26,1,164,16,"Tattha samudayena assādo, dukkhena ādīnavo, magganirodhehi nissaraṇaṃ, tesaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ mānabhañjanaṃ phalaṃ, tathā‘‘ yathāvuttavibhāgāvabodho’’ tiādinā vuttaṃ payojanañca. "
1049517,192,412,27,52,1,239,21,"Tassa nipphattikāraṇattā desanāya vicittatā catunnaṃ puggalānaṃ yāthāvato sabhāvūpadhāraṇañca upāyo , pathavīādīsu puthujjanādīnaṃ pavattidassanāpadesena pathavīādayo ekantato parijānitabbā, maññanā ca pahātabbāti ayamettha bhagavato {āṇattī}ti. "
1049518,192,412,53,55,1,15,2,Ayaṃ desanāhāro.
1049519,192,413,2,4,1,17,2,2 . Vicayahāravaṇṇanā 
1049520,192,414,2,49,1,365,32,"Maññanānaṃ sakkāyassa avisesahetubhāvato, kassacipi tattha asesitabbato ca sabbagahaṇaṃ, sabhāvadhāraṇato nissattanijjīvato ca dhammaggahaṇaṃ, patiṭṭhābhāvato āveṇikahetubhāvato ca mūlaggahaṇaṃ, kāraṇabhāvato desanatthasambhavato ca pariyāyaggahaṇaṃ, sammukhabhāvato sampadānatthasambhavato ca‘‘ vo’’ ti vacanaṃ, tathārūpaguṇayogato abhimukhīkaraṇato ca‘‘ bhikkhave’’ ti ālapanaṃ. "
1049521,192,414,50,88,1,221,22,"Desetuṃ samatthabhāvato tesaṃ satuppādanatthañca‘‘ desessāmī’’ ti paṭijānanaṃ, desetabbatāya paṭiññātabhāvato, yathāpaṭiññañca desanato‘‘ tan’’ ti paccāmasanaṃ, sotabbabhāvato, savanatthassa ca ekantena nipphādanato‘‘ suṇāthā’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
1049522,192,414,89,102,1,72,8,"Sakkātabbato, sakkaccakiriyāya eva ca tadatthasiddhito‘‘ sādhukan’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
1049523,192,414,103,128,1,175,17,Dhammassa manasikaraṇīyato tadadhīnattā ca sabbasampattīnaṃ‘‘ manasi karothā’’ ti vuttaṃ yathāpariññātāya desanāya paribyattabhāvato vitthāratthasambhavato ca‘‘ bhāsissāmī’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1049524,192,414,129,145,1,111,11,"Bhagavato sadevakena lokena sirasā sampaṭicchitabbavacanattā, tassa ca yathādhippetatthasādhanato‘‘ evan’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
1049525,192,414,146,160,1,87,9,"Satthu uttamagāravaṭṭhānabhāvato, tattha ca gāravassa uḷārapuññabhāvato‘‘ bhante’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
1049526,192,414,161,173,1,73,8,Bhikkhūnaṃ tathākiriyāya nicchitabhāvato vacanālaṅkārato ca‘‘ kho’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1049527,192,414,174,200,1,136,16,"Savanassa paṭijānitabbato, tathā tehi paṭipannattā ca‘‘ paccassosun’’ ti vuttaṃ paccakkhabhāvato, sakalassapi ekajjhaṃ karaṇato‘‘ etan’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
1049528,192,415,2,16,1,87,10,Vuccamānassa puggalassa lokapariyāpannattā lokādhārattā ca lokaṃ upādāya‘‘ idhā’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1049529,192,415,17,27,1,73,6,Paṭivedhabāhusaccābhāvato pariyattibāhusaccābhāvato ca‘‘ assutavā’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1049530,192,415,28,40,1,49,7,"Puthūsu, puthu vā janabhāvato‘‘ puthujjano’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
1049531,192,415,41,51,1,68,6,Anariyadhammavirahato ariyadhammasamannāgamato ca‘‘ ariyānan’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1049532,192,415,52,66,1,98,9,"Ariyabhāvakarāya paṭipattiyā abhāvato, tattha kosalladamathābhāvato‘‘ ariyānaṃ adassāvī’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1049533,192,415,67,80,1,91,8,Asantadhammassavanato santadhammasamannāgamato sabbhi pāsaṃsiyato ca‘‘ sappurisānan’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1049534,192,415,81,96,1,109,10,"Sappurisabhāvakarāya paṭipattiyā abhāvato, tattha ca kosalladamathābhāvato‘‘ sappurisānaṃ adassāvī’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. "
1049535,192,415,97,113,1,126,11,"Pathavīvatthukānaṃ maññanānaṃ, upari vuccamānānañcamaññanānaṃ mūlakattā papañcasaṅkhānaṃ‘‘ pathaviṃ pathavito sañjānātī’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
1049536,192,415,114,126,1,93,8,Andhaputhujjanassa ahaṃkāra-mamaṃkārānaṃ katthacipi appahīnattā‘‘ pathaviṃ maññatī’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
1049537,192,416,2,21,1,116,12,"Pubbe aggahitattā, sāmaññato ca gayhamānattā, puggalassa pathavīādiārammaṇasabhāgatāya labbhamānattā ca‘‘ yopī’’ ti vuttaṃ."
1049538,192,416,22,33,1,61,7,‘‘ Yo’’ ti aniyamena gahitassa niyametabbato paṭiniddisitabbato ca;
1049539,192,416,34,54,1,94,12,‘‘ so’’ ti vuttaṃ sātisayaṃ saṃsāre bhayassa ikkhanato kilesabhedanasambhavato ca‘‘ bhikkhū’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1049540,192,416,55,66,1,66,7,Sikkhāhi samannāgamato sekkhadhammapaṭilābhato ca‘‘ sekkho’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1049541,192,416,67,80,1,87,9,Manasā laddhabbassa arahattassa anadhigatattā adhigamanīyato ca‘‘ appattamānaso’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1049542,192,416,81,96,1,89,10,"Aparena anuttaraṇīyato, paraṃ anucchavikabhāvena uttaritvā ṭhitattā ca‘‘ anuttaran’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
1049543,192,416,97,111,1,81,10,Yogena bhāvanāya kāmayogādito ca khemaṃ sivaṃ anupaddavanti‘‘ yogakkheman’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1049544,192,416,112,122,1,57,6,Chandappavattiyā ussukkāpattiyā ca‘‘ patthayamāno’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1049545,192,416,123,137,1,114,10,Tadatthassa sabbaso sabbairiyāpathavihārassa samathavipassanāvihārassa dibbavihārassa ca vasena‘‘ viharatī’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1049546,192,416,138,152,1,107,10,Sekkhassa sabbaso abhiññeyyabhāvañceva pariññeyyabhāvañca ñāṇena abhibhavitvā jānanato‘‘ abhijānātī’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1049547,192,416,153,165,1,65,8,Sekkhassa sabbaso appahīnamaññanatāya abhāvato‘‘ mā maññī’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1049548,192,416,166,169,1,34,3,Sesaṃ vuttanayānusārena veditabbaṃ. 
1049549,192,416,170,177,1,53,7,Iminā nayena ito paraṃ sabbapadesu vinicchayo kātabbo. 
1049550,192,416,178,191,1,123,13,Sakkā hi aṭṭhakathaṃ tassā līnatthavaṇṇana ñca anugantvā ayamattho viññūhi vibhāvetunti ativitthārabhayena na vitthārayimha. 
1049551,192,416,192,196,1,31,4,Iti anupadavicayato vicayo hāro.
1049552,192,417,2,4,1,16,2,3 . Yuttihāravaṇṇanā 
1049553,192,418,2,8,1,79,6,Sakkāyassa sabbamaññanānaṃ mūlabhāvo yujjati parikappamattakattā lokavicittassa. 
1049554,192,418,9,13,1,94,4,Byāhusaccadvayarahitassa andhaputhujjanabhāvo yujjati puthukilesābhisaṅkhārajananādisabhāvattā. 
1049555,192,418,14,21,1,84,7,Yathāvuttaputhujjanassa vā vuttappakārabāhusaccābhāvo yujjati tasmiṃ sati sabbhāvato. 
1049556,192,418,22,59,1,277,30,"Tattha assutavato puthujjanassa ariyānaṃ sappurisānañca adassāvitādi yujjati ariyakaradhammānaṃ ariyabhāvassa ca tena adiṭṭhattā appaṭipannattā ca tathā tassa pathaviyā‘‘ ahaṃ pathavī, mama pathavī, paro pathavī’’ ti sañjānanaṃ yujjati ahaṃkāramamaṃkārānaṃ sabbena sabbaṃ appahīnattā. "
1049557,192,418,60,71,1,129,11,Tathā sañjānato cassa pathaviṃ kammādikaraṇādivasena gahetvā nānappakārato maññanāpavatti yujjati saññānidānattā papañcasaṅkhānaṃ. 
1049558,192,418,72,81,1,81,8,"Yo maññati, tassa apariññātavatthukatā yujjati pariññāya vinā maññanāpahānābhāvato."
1049559,192,418,82,92,1,42,6,‘‘ Āpaṃ āpato sañjānātī’’ tiādīsupi eseva nayo. 
1049560,192,418,93,97,1,63,4,Apariyositasikkhassa appattamānasatā yujjati katakiccatābhāvato. 
1049561,192,418,98,103,1,61,5,Sekkhassa sato yogakkhemapatthanā yujjati tadadhimuttabhāvato. 
1049562,192,418,104,112,1,76,8,Tathā tassa pathaviyā abhijānanā yujjati pariññāpahānesu mattaso kāribhāvato. 
1049563,192,418,113,130,1,102,12,Tato eva cassa‘‘ mā maññī’’ ti vattabbatā yujjati vatthupariññāya viya maññanāpahānassapi vippakatabhāvato. 
1049564,192,418,131,140,1,90,9,Sekkhassa pathaviyā pariññeyyatā yujjati pariññātuṃ sakkuṇeyyattā sabbaso apariññātattā ca.
1049565,192,418,141,150,1,32,5,‘‘ Āpaṃ āpato’’ tiādīsupi eseva nayo. 
1049566,192,418,151,172,1,198,19,"Arahattādiyuttassa pathaviyādīnaṃ abhijānanā maññanābhāvo ca yujjati saṅkhātadhammattā, sabbaso kilesānaṃ pahīnattā, tato eva cassa vītarāgādibhāvo tato sammadeva ca paṭiccasamuppādassa paṭividdhatāti. "
1049567,192,418,173,175,1,14,2,Ayaṃ yuttihāro.
1049568,192,419,2,4,1,21,2,4 . Padaṭṭhānahāravaṇṇanā 
1049569,192,420,2,29,1,249,22,"Kissopi maññanā sakkāyassa padaṭṭhānaṃ, maññanānaṃ ayonisomanasikāro padaṭṭhānaṃ, sutadvayaviraho andhaputhujjanabhāvassa padaṭṭhānaṃ, so ariyānaṃ adassāvitāya padaṭṭhānaṃ, sā ariyadhammassa akovidatāya padaṭṭhānaṃ, sā ariyadhamme avinītatāya padaṭṭhānaṃ."
1049570,192,420,30,40,1,43,6,‘‘ Sappurisānaṃ adassāvī’’ ti etthāpi eseva nayo. 
1049571,192,420,41,44,1,37,3,Saññāvipallāso maññanānaṃ padaṭṭhānaṃ. 
1049572,192,420,45,48,1,30,3,Saññānidānā hi papañcasaṅkhāti. 
1049573,192,420,49,103,1,193,18,"Maññanāsu ca taṇhāmaññanā itaramaññanānaṃ padaṭṭhānaṃ‘‘ taṇhāgatānaṃ paritassitavipphanditan’’ ti,( dī. ni.1.105-109)‘‘ taṇhāpaccayā upādānan’’ ti( ma. ni.3.126; mahāva.1) ca vacanato, taṇhāgatasseva ca‘‘ seyyohamasmin’’ tiādinā mānajappanāsabbhāvatā. "
1049574,192,420,104,111,1,50,6,Sabbāpi vā maññanā sabbāsaṃ maññanānaṃ padaṭṭhānaṃ .
1049575,192,420,112,124,1,64,8,‘‘ Upādānapaccayā taṇhā’’ ti hi vacanato diṭṭhipi taṇhāya padaṭṭhānaṃ.
1049576,192,420,125,150,1,69,8,‘‘ Ahamasmi brahmā mahābrahmā’’ ti( dī. ni.1.42;3.39) ādivacanato mānopi diṭṭhiyā padaṭṭhānaṃ. 
1049577,192,420,151,171,1,124,14,"Tathā‘‘ asmīti sati itthaṃsmīti hoti, evaṃsmīti hoti, aññathāsmīti hotī’’ tiādivacanato mānassapi taṇhāya padaṭṭhānatā labbhateva. "
1049578,192,420,172,177,1,54,5,Sekkhā dhammā sappadesato maññanāpahānassa padaṭṭhānaṃ. 
1049579,192,420,178,182,1,48,4,Asekkhā nippadesato maññanāpahānassa padaṭṭhānaṃ. 
1049580,192,420,183,187,1,32,4,Kammabhavo ca jātiyā padaṭṭhānaṃ. 
1049581,192,420,188,191,1,30,3,Jāti jarāmaraṇassa padaṭṭhānaṃ. 
1049582,192,420,192,196,1,62,4,Paccayākārassa yathābhūtāvabodho sammāsambodhiyā padaṭṭhānanti. 
1049583,192,420,197,200,1,20,3,Ayaṃ padaṭṭhāno hāro.
1049584,192,421,2,4,1,19,2,5 . Lakkhaṇahāravaṇṇanā
1049585,192,422,2,24,1,203,18,"‘ ‘ Sabbadhammamūlapariyāyan’’ ti ettha mūlaggahaṇena mūlapariyāyaggahaṇena vā yathā taṇhāmānadiṭṭhiyo gayhanti, evaṃ dosamohādīnampi sakkāyamūladhammānaṃ saṅgaho daṭṭhabbo sakkāyassa mūlabhāvena ekalakkhaṇattā."
1049586,192,422,25,45,1,162,15,"‘‘ Assutavā’’ ti iminā yathā tassa puggalassa pariyattipaṭivedhasaddhammānaṃ abhāvo gayhati, evaṃ paṭipattisaddhammassapi abhāvo gayhati saddhammabhāvena ekalakkhaṇattā. "
1049587,192,422,46,48,1,33,2,Ariyānaṃ adassanakāmatādilakkhaṇā.
1049588,192,422,49,61,1,76,7,‘‘ Ariyadhammassa akovido’’ ti iminā ariyadhammādhigamassa vibandhabhūtaṃ aññāṇaṃ.
1049589,192,422,62,71,1,45,5,‘‘ Ariyadhamme avinīto’’ ti iminā ariyavinayābhāvo. 
1049590,192,422,72,86,1,119,14,So panatthato ariyavinaye appaṭipatti eva vāti tīhipi padehi yathāvuttavisayā micchādiṭṭhi vicikicchā ca gahitāva honti. 
1049591,192,422,87,96,1,90,9,Taggahaṇena ca sabbepi akusalā dhammā saṅgahitāva honti saṃkilesalakkhaṇena ekalakkhaṇattā.
1049592,192,422,97,107,1,43,6,‘‘ Sappurisānaṃ adassāvī’’ ti etthāpi eseva nayo.
1049593,192,423,2,14,1,83,9,‘ ‘ Pathaviṃ pathavito sañjānātī’’ ti idaṃ diṭṭhimaññanādīnaṃ saññāya kāraṇabhāvadassanaṃ. 
1049594,192,423,15,31,1,160,15,"Tattha yathā saññā, evaṃ vitakkaphassāvijjāayonisomanasikārādayopi tāsaṃ kāraṇanti atthato tesampettha saṅgaho vutto hoti maññanānaṃ kāraṇabhāvena ekalakkhaṇattā."
1049595,192,423,32,45,1,79,8,‘‘ Maññatī’’ ti iminā maññanākiccena taṇhāmānadiṭṭhiyo gahitā tāsaṃ kilesasabhāvattā. 
1049596,192,423,46,52,1,81,6,Taggahaṇeneva vicikicchādinampi saṅgaho daṭṭhabbo kilesalakkhaṇena ekalakkhaṇattā. 
1049597,192,423,53,62,1,113,9,Tathā taṇhāya hetusabhāvattā taggahaṇeneva avasiṭṭhākusalahetūnaṃ saṅgaho daṭṭhabbo hetulakkhaṇena ekalakkhaṇattā. 
1049598,192,423,63,72,1,145,9,Tathā taṇhādiṭṭhīnaṃ āsavādisabhāvattā taggahaṇeneva avasiṭṭhāsavoghayogaganthanīvaraṇādīnampi saṅgaho daṭṭhabbo āsavādisabhāvattā ekalakkhaṇattā. 
1049599,192,423,73,94,1,204,17,Tathā‘‘ pathaviṃ maññatī’’ tiādinā pathavīādīnaṃ rūpasabhāvattā tabbisayānañca maññanānaṃ rūpavisayattā taggahaṇeneva sakalarūpakkhandhavisayāpi maññanā dassitā honti rūpavisayalakkhaṇena āsaṃ ekalakkhaṇattā. 
1049600,192,423,95,99,1,49,4,Evaṃ cakkhāyatanādivisayāpi maññanā niddhāretabbā.
1049601,192,423,100,113,1,136,9,‘‘ Apariññātan’’ ti pariññāpaṭikkhepena tappaṭibaddhakilesānaṃ pahānapaṭikkhepoti daṭṭhabbo maggakiccabhāvena pariññāpahānānaṃ ekalakkhaṇattā. 
1049602,192,423,114,120,1,60,6,Iminā nayena sesesupi yathārahaṃ ekalakkhaṇā niddhāretabbāti. 
1049603,192,423,121,124,1,18,3,Ayaṃ lakkhaṇo hāro.
1049604,192,424,2,4,1,20,2,6 . Catubyūhahāravaṇṇanā 
1049605,192,425,2,23,1,288,21,Pathavīādīsu vatthūsu byañjanacchāyāya atthaṃ gahetvā dhammagambhīrataṃ asallakkhetvā asaddhammassavanādinā vañcitā hutvā saddhammassavanadhāraṇaparicayamanasikāravimukhā pathavīādīsu vatthūsu puthujjanasekkhāsekkhatathāgatānaṃ paṭipattivisesaṃ ajānantā ca veneyyā imissā desanāya nidānaṃ. 
1049606,192,425,24,43,1,148,15,Te‘‘ kathaṃ nu kho yathāvuttadosavinimuttā yathāvuttañca visesaṃ jānantā sammāpaṭipattiyā ubhayahitaparāyaṇā saveyyun’’ ti ayamettha bhagavato adhippāyo. 
1049607,192,425,44,72,1,203,16,"Padanibbacanaṃ niruttaṃ, taṃ‘‘ evan’’ tiādinidānapadānaṃ,‘‘ sabbadhammamūlapariyāyan’’ tiādipāḷipadānañca aṭṭhakathāyaṃ, tassā līnatthavaṇṇanāya ñceva vuttanayena suviññeyyattā ativitthārabhayena na vitthārayimha. "
1049608,192,426,2,5,1,61,3,Padapadatthadesanānikkhepasuttasandhivasena pañcavidhā sandhi. 
1049609,192,426,6,26,1,142,14,"Tattha padassa padantarena sambandho padasandhi, tathā padatthassa padatthantarena sambandho padatthasandhi, yo‘‘ kiriyākārakasambandho’’ ti vuccati. "
1049610,192,426,27,36,1,108,8,"Nānānusandhikassa suttassa taṃtaṃanusandhīhi sambandho, ekānusandhikassa pana pubbāparasambandho desanāsandhi. "
1049611,192,426,37,50,1,81,8,Yā aṭṭhakathāyaṃ‘‘ pucchānusandhi ajjhāsayānusandhi yathānusandhī’’ ti tidhā vibhattā. 
1049612,192,426,51,57,1,61,6,Ajjhāsayo cettha attajjhāsayo parajjhāsayoti dvidhā veditabbo. 
1049613,192,426,58,66,1,60,7,"Yaṃ panettha vattabbaṃ, taṃ heṭṭhā nidānavaṇṇanāyaṃ vuttameva. "
1049614,192,426,67,72,1,57,5,Nikkhepasandhi catunnaṃ suttanikkhepānaṃ vasena veditabbo. 
1049615,192,426,73,77,1,50,4,Suttasandhi idha paṭhamanikkhepavaseneva veditabbo. 
1049616,192,426,78,83,1,58,5,Kasmā panettha mūlapariyāyasuttameva paṭhamaṃ nikkhittanti? 
1049617,192,426,84,116,1,300,29,"Nāyamanuyogo katthaci nappavattati, apica yasmā maññanāmūlakaṃ sakkāyaṃ, sabbamaññanā ca tattha eva anekabhedabhinnā pavattati, na tassā savisayāya lesamattampi sāraṃ atthīti pathavīādivibhāgabhinnesu maññanāsu ca sātisayaṃ nibbedhavirāgasañjananī upari sekkhāsekkhatathāgataguṇavibhāvanī ca ayaṃ desanā. "
1049618,192,426,117,135,1,186,17,"Suttantadesanā ca visesato diṭṭhiviniveṭhanakathā, tasmā sanissayassa diṭṭhiggāhassa ādito asārabhāvadīpanaṃ upari ca sabbesaṃ ariyānaṃ guṇavisesavibhāvanamidaṃ suttaṃ paṭhamaṃ nikkhittaṃ. "
1049619,192,426,136,149,1,155,13,Kiñca sakkāye maññanāmaññanāmukhena pavattinivattīsu ādīnavānisaṃsavibhāvanato sabbesaṃ puggalānaṃ paṭipattivibhāgato ca idameva suttaṃ paṭhamaṃ nikkhittaṃ. 
1049620,192,427,2,16,1,96,12,"Yaṃ pana ekissā desanāya desanantarena saddhiṃ saṃsandanaṃ, ayampi desanāsandhi, sā evaṃ veditabbā."
1049621,192,427,17,31,1,58,8,‘‘ Assutavā puthujjano… pe… nibbānaṃ abhinandatī’’ ti ayaṃ desanā.
1049622,192,427,32,83,1,326,39,"‘‘ Idha, bhikkhave, assutavā puthujjano… pe… sappurisadhamme avinīto manasikaraṇīye dhamme nappajānāti, amanasikaraṇīye ca dhamme nappajānāti, so manasikaraṇīye dhamme appajānanto amanasikaraṇīye ca dhamme appajānanto ye dhammā na manasikaraṇīyā, te dhamme manasi karoti… pe… anuppanno vā kāmāsavo uppajjati, uppanno vā kāmāsavo pavaḍḍhati. "
1049623,192,427,84,118,1,160,20,"Anuppanno vā bhavāsavo uppajjati, uppanno vā bhavāsavo pavaḍḍhati, anuppanno vā avijjāsavo uppajjati, uppanno vā avijjāsavo pavaḍḍhatī’’ ti( ma. ni.1.17) imāya desanāya saṃsandati. "
1049624,192,427,119,158,1,212,24,"Tathā‘‘ tassetaṃ pāṭikaṅkhaṃ subhanimittaṃ manasi karissati, tassa subhanimittassa manasikārā rāgo cittaṃ anuddhaṃsessati, so sarāgo sadoso samoho sāṅgaṇo saṃkiliṭṭhacitto kālaṃ karissatī’’ ti( ma. ni.1.59) imāya desanāya saṃsandati. "
1049625,192,427,159,177,1,103,12,"Tathā‘‘ cakkhuñcāvuso paṭicca rūpe ca uppajjati cakkhuviññāṇaṃ, tiṇṇaṃ saṅgati phasso, phassapaccayā vedanā. "
1049626,192,427,178,214,1,176,22,"Yaṃ vedeti taṃ sañjānāti, yaṃ sañjānāti taṃ vitakketi, yaṃ vitakketi taṃ papañceti, yaṃ papañceti tatonidānaṃ purisaṃ papañcasaññāsaṅkhā samudācarantī’’ ti( ma. ni.1.204) imāya desanāya saṃsandati. "
1049627,192,427,215,242,1,122,17,"Tathā‘‘ idha, bhikkhave, asutavā puthujjano… pe… sappurisadhamme avinīto rūpaṃ‘ etaṃ mama, esohamasmi, eso me attā’ ti samanupassati. "
1049628,192,427,243,271,1,91,15,"Vedanaṃ… pe…, saññaṃ… pe…, saṅkhāre… pe…, viññāṇaṃ‘ etaṃ mama, esohamasmi, eso me attā’ ti samanupassati. "
1049629,192,427,272,325,1,235,34,"Yampi taṃ diṭṭhaṃ… pe… yampi taṃ diṭṭhiṭṭhānaṃ, so loko so attā so pecca bhavissāmi nicco dhuvo sassato avipariṇāmadhammo sassatisamaṃ tatheva ṭhassāmīti, tampi‘ etaṃ mama, esohamasmi, eso me attā’ ti samanupassatī’’ ti( ma. ni.1.241) imāya desanāya saṃsandati."
1049630,192,428,2,20,1,63,11,"‘ ‘ Yopi so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu… pe… nibbānaṃ mābhinandī’’ ti ayaṃ desanā."
1049631,192,428,21,108,1,465,58,"‘‘ Idha, devānaminda, bhikkhuno sutaṃ hoti‘ sabbe dhammā nālaṃ abhinivesāyā’ ti, evañcetaṃ, devānaminda, bhikkhuno sutaṃ hoti‘ sabbe dhammā nālaṃ abhinivesāyā’ ti, so sabbaṃ dhammaṃ abhijānāti, sabbaṃ dhammaṃ abhiññāya sabbaṃ dhammaṃ parijānāti, sabbaṃ dhammaṃ pariññāya yaṃ kiñci vedanaṃ vedeti sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā, so tāsu vedanāsu aniccānupassī viharati, virāgānupassī viharati, nirodhānupassī viharati, paṭinissaggānupassī viharatī’’ ti( ma. ni.1.390) imāya desanāya saṃsandati."
1049632,192,428,109,184,1,291,43,"‘‘ Yopi so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu arahaṃ… pe… abhisambuddhoti vadāmī’’ ti ayaṃ desanā‘‘ sutavā ca kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako… pe… sappurisadhamme suvinīto rūpaṃ‘ netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ ti samanupassati, vedanaṃ… pe…, saññaṃ… pe…, saṅkhāre… pe…, viññāṇaṃ‘ netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ ti samanupassati. "
1049633,192,428,185,208,1,130,18,"Yampi taṃ diṭṭhaṃ sutaṃ viññātaṃ pattaṃ pariyesitaṃ anuvicaritaṃ manasā, tampi‘ netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ ti samanupassati. "
1049634,192,428,209,245,1,190,28,"Yampi taṃ diṭṭhiṭṭhānaṃ, so loko so attā so pecca bhavissāmi‘ nicco dhuvo sassato api pariṇāmadhammo sassatisamaṃ tatheva ṭhassāmī’ ti, tampi‘ netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ ti samanupassati. "
1049635,192,428,246,269,1,89,11,"So evaṃ samanupassanto na paritassatī’’ ti( ma. ni.1.241) evamādidesanāhi saṃsandatīti, ayaṃ catubyūho hāro."
