1049643,192,430,88,130,1,87,9,Tattha taṇhāggāhena‘‘ taṇhaṃ paṭiccapariyesanā’’ tiādikā( dī. ni.2.103; dī. ni.3.359; a. ni.3.23; vibha.963) nava taṇhāmūlakā dhammā āvattanti. 
1049644,192,430,131,141,1,58,6,Mānaggāhena‘‘ seyyohamasmī’’ tiādikā nava mānavidhā āvattanti. 
1049645,192,430,142,163,1,87,8,Diṭṭhiggāhena‘‘ rūpaṃ attato samanupassatī’’ tiādikā( saṃ. ni.4.345) vīsativatthukā sakkāyadiṭṭhi āvattati. 
1049646,192,430,164,175,1,85,10,"Tīsu ca gāhesu yāya saññāya taṇhāggāhassa vikkhambhanā, sā dukkhasaññā dukkhānupassanā. "
