1049660,192,433,2,4,1,19,2,8 . Vibhattihāravaṇṇanā
1049661,192,434,2,15,1,91,10,‘ ‘ Sabbadhammamūlapariyāyan’’ ti ettha sabbadhammā nāma tebhūmakā dhammā sakkāyassa adhippetattā. 
1049662,192,434,16,21,1,64,5,Tesaṃ maññanā padaṭṭhānaṃ papañcasaṅkhānimittattā lokavicittassa. 
