1049664,192,434,28,39,1,130,9,"Tesu kusalānaṃ yonisomanasikārādi padaṭṭhānaṃ, akusalānaṃ ayonisomanasikārādi, abyākatānaṃ kammabhavaāvajjanabhūtarūpādi padaṭṭhānaṃ. "
