1049732,192,446,2,4,1,21,2,14 . Adhiṭṭhānahāravaṇṇanā
1049733,192,447,2,12,1,75,7,‘ ‘ Sabbadhammamūlapariyāyan’’ ti ettha sabbadhammaggahaṇaṃ sāmaññato adhiṭṭhānaṃ.
1049734,192,447,13,24,1,55,7,‘‘ Pathaviṃ āpan’’ tiādi pana taṃ avikappetvā visesavacanaṃ. 
1049735,192,447,25,50,1,109,13,"Tathā‘‘ mūlapariyāyan’’ ti sāmaññato adhiṭṭhānaṃ, taṃ avikappetvā visesavacanaṃ‘‘ pathaviṃ maññati… pe… abhinandatī’’ ti."
1049736,192,447,51,87,1,209,24,"‘‘ Pathaviṃ maññatī’’ ti ca sāmaññato adhiṭṭhānaṃ taṇhādiggāhānaṃ sādhāraṇattā maññanāya, taṃ avikappetvā visesavacanaṃ‘‘ etaṃ mama, esohamasmi, eso me attā’’ ti, evaṃ suttantarapadānipi ānetvā visesavacanaṃ niddhāretabbaṃ. "
1049737,192,447,88,91,1,23,3,Sesavāresupi eseva nayo.
1049738,192,447,92,114,1,128,13,"‘‘ Sekkho’’ ti sāmaññato adhiṭṭhānaṃ, taṃ avikappetvā visesavacanaṃ‘‘ kāyasakkhī diṭṭhippatto saddhāvimutto saddhānusārī dhammānusārī’’ ti. "
1049739,192,447,115,158,1,177,21,"Tathā‘‘ sekkho’’ ti sāmaññato adhiṭṭhānaṃ, taṃ avikappetvā visesavacanaṃ‘‘ idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sekkhāya sammādiṭṭhiyā samannāgato hoti… pe… sekkhena sammāsamādhinā samannāgato hotī’’ ti( saṃ. ni.5.13)."
1049740,192,447,159,208,1,119,13,"‘‘ Arahan’’ ti sāmaññato adhiṭṭhānaṃ, taṃ avikappetvā visesavacanaṃ‘‘ ubhatobhāgavimutto paññāvimutto( pu. pa.13.2;15.1 mātikā), tevijjo chaḷabhiñño’’ ti( pu. pa.7.26,27 mātikā) ca."
1049741,192,447,209,238,1,132,14,"‘‘ Khīṇāsavo’’ ti sāmaññato adhiṭṭhānaṃ, taṃ avikappetvā visesavacanaṃ‘‘ kāmāsavāpi cittaṃ vimuccittha, bhavāsavāpi cittaṃ vimuccitthā’’ tiādi( pārā.14). "
1049742,192,447,239,242,1,23,3,Sesapadesupi eseva nayo.
1049743,192,447,243,261,1,76,9,"‘‘ Abhijānātī’’ ti sāmaññato adhiṭṭhānaṃ, taṃ avikappetvā visesavacanaṃ‘‘ maññatī’’ ti. "
1049744,192,447,262,278,1,174,14,"Maññanābhāvo hissa pahānapaṭivedhasiddho, pahānapaṭivedho ca pariññāsacchikiriyābhāvanāpaṭivedhehi na vināti sabbepi abhiññāvisesā maññanāpaṭikkhepena atthato gahitāva hontīti. "
1049745,192,447,279,300,1,106,12,"Tathā‘‘ arahan’’ ti sāmaññato adhiṭṭhānaṃ, taṃ avikappetvā visesavacanaṃ‘‘ vītarāgattā vītadosattā vītamohattā’’ ti. "
1049746,192,447,301,306,1,59,5,Iminā nayena sesapadesupi sāmaññavisesaniddhāraṇā veditabbā. 
