1049748,192,448,2,4,1,21,2,14 . Parikkhārahāravaṇṇanā
1049749,192,449,2,16,1,106,10,"‘ ‘ Sabbadhammamūlapariyāyan’’ ti ettha sabbadhammā nāma pariyāpannadhammā, te kusalākusalābyākatabhedena tividhā. "
1049750,192,449,17,39,1,184,19,"Tesu kusalānaṃ yonisomanasikāro alobhādayo ca hetū, akusalānaṃ ayonisomanasikāro lobhādayo ca hetū, abyākatesu vipākānaṃ yathāsakaṃ kammaṃ, itaresaṃ bhavaṅgamāvajjanasamannāhārādi ca hetū. "
1049751,192,449,40,54,1,106,12,"Ettha ca sappurisūpanissayādiko paccayo hetumhi eva samavaruḷho, so tattha ādi-saddena saṅgahitoti daṭṭhabbo."
1049752,192,449,55,67,1,56,8,‘‘ Mūlan’’ ti vuttānaṃ maññanānaṃ hetubhāvo pāḷiyaṃ vutto eva. 
1049753,192,449,68,73,1,50,5,Maññanāsu pana taṇhāmaññanāya assādānupassanā hetu.
1049754,192,449,74,95,1,68,8,‘‘ Saññojaniyesu dhammesu assādānupassino taṇhā pavaḍḍhatī’’ ti( saṃ. ni.2.52) hi vuttaṃ. 
1049755,192,449,96,108,1,87,8,Mānamaññanāya diṭṭhivippayuttalobho hetu kevalaṃ saṃsaggavasena‘‘ ahamasmī’’ ti pavattanato. 
1049756,192,449,109,159,1,343,38,"Diṭṭhimaññanāya ekattanayādīnaṃ ayāthāvaggāho hetu, assutabhāvo puthujjanabhāvassa hetu, so ariyānaṃ adassanasīlatāya, sā ariyadhammassa akovidatāya, sā ariyadhamme avinītatāya hetu, sabbā cāyaṃ hetuparamparā pathavīādīsu‘‘ etaṃ mama, esohamasmi, eso me attā’’ ti tissannaṃ maññanānaṃ hetu, sekkhārahādibhāvā pana mattaso sabbaso ca maññanābhāvassa hetūti. "
1049757,192,449,160,163,1,20,3,Ayaṃ parikkhāro hāro.
1049758,192,450,2,4,1,21,2,16 . Samāropanahāravaṇṇanā
1049759,192,451,2,22,1,208,16,"‘ ‘ Sabbadhammamūlapariyāyan’’ tiādīsu mūlapariyāyaggahaṇena assutavāgahaṇena sañjānanamaññanāpariññāgahaṇehi ca saṃkilesadhammā dassitā, te ca saṅkhepato tividhā taṇhāsaṃkileso diṭṭhisaṃkileso duccaritasaṃkilesoti. "
1049760,192,451,23,51,1,286,20,"Tattha taṇhāsaṃkileso taṇhāsaṃkilesassa, diṭṭhisaṃkilesassa, duccaritasaṃkilesassa ca padaṭṭhānaṃ, tathā diṭṭhisaṃkileso diṭṭhisaṃkilesassa, taṇhāsaṃkilesassa, duccaritasaṃkilesassa ca padaṭṭhānaṃ, duccaritasaṃkilesopi duccaritasaṃkilesassa, taṇhāsaṃkilesassa, diṭṭhisaṃkilesassa ca padaṭṭhānaṃ. "
1049761,192,451,52,80,1,134,15,"Tesu taṇhāsaṃkileso atthato lobhova, yo‘‘ lobho lubbhanā lubbhitattaṃ sārāgo sārajjanā sārajjitattan’’ tiādinā ( dha. sa.389) anekehi pariyāyehi vibhatto. "
1049762,192,451,81,130,1,214,21,"Tathā diṭṭhiyeva diṭṭhisaṃkileso, yo‘‘ diṭṭhigataṃ diṭṭhigahanaṃ diṭṭhikantāro diṭṭhivisūkaṃ diṭṭhivipphanditan’’ tiādinā( dha. sa.1105) anekehi pariyāyehi,‘‘ santi, bhikkhave, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā’’ tiādinā( dī. ni.1.30) dvāsaṭṭhiyā pabhedehi ca vibhatto. "
1049763,192,451,131,178,1,221,24,"Duccaritasaṃkileso pana atthato dussīlyacetanā ceva cetanāsampayuttadhammā ca, yā‘‘ kāyaduccaritaṃ vacīduccaritaṃ kāyavisamaṃ vacīvisaman’’ ti( vibha.913,924),‘‘ pāṇātipāto adinnādānan’’ ti( vibha.913) ca ādinā anekehi pariyāyehi, anekehi pabhedehi ca vibhattā. "
1049764,192,452,2,14,1,109,9,"Tesu taṇhāsaṃkilesassa samatho paṭipakkho, diṭṭhisaṃkilesassa vipassanā, duccaritasaṃkilesassa sīlaṃ paṭipakkho. "
1049765,192,452,15,31,1,105,12,Te pana sīlādayo dhammā idha pariññāgahaṇena sekkhaggahaṇena‘‘ arahan’’ tiādinā ariyatādiggahaṇena ca gahitā. 
1049766,192,452,32,48,1,183,13,"Tattha sīlena duccaritasaṃkilesappahānaṃ sijjhati, tathā tadaṅgappahānaṃ vītikkamappahānañca, samathena taṇhāsaṃkilesappahānaṃ sijjhati, tathā vikkhambhanappahānaṃ pariyuṭṭhānappahānañca. "
1049767,192,452,49,56,1,87,6,"Vipassanāya diṭṭhisaṃkilesappahānaṃ sijjhati, tathā samucchedappahānaṃ anusayappahānañca. "
1049768,192,452,57,71,1,115,12,"Tattha pubbabhāge sīle patiṭṭhitassa samatho, samathe patiṭṭhitassa vipassanā, maggakkhaṇe pana samakālameva bhavanti. "
1049769,192,452,72,94,1,276,21,"Pubbeyeva hi suparisuddhakāyavacīkammassa suparisuddhājīvassa ca samathavipassanā āraddhā gabbhaṃ gaṇhantiyo paripākaṃ gacchantiyo vuṭṭhānagāminivipassanaṃ paribrūhenti, vuṭṭhānagāminivipassanā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchantī maggena ghaṭenti maggakkhaṇe samathavipassanā paripūreti. "
1049770,192,452,95,103,1,127,8,Atha maggakkhaṇe samathavipassanābhāvanāpāripūriyā anavasesasaṃkilesadhammaṃ samucchindantiyo nirodhaṃ nibbānaṃ sacchikarontīti. 
1049771,192,452,104,107,1,20,3,Ayaṃ samāropano hāro. 
