1049774,192,455,2,4,1,23,2,1 . Nandiyāvaṭṭanayavaṇṇanā
1049775,192,456,2,14,1,102,8,‘ ‘ Sabbadhammamūlapariyāyan’’ tiādīsu sabbadhammamūlaggahaṇena maññanāgahaṇena ca taṇhāmānadiṭṭhiyo gahitā. 
1049776,192,456,15,20,1,49,5,Maññanānampi hi maññanā kāraṇanti dassitoyamattho.
1049777,192,456,21,36,1,101,9,"‘‘ Assutavā’’ tiādinā avijjāmānadiṭṭhiyo gahitā, sabbepi vā saṃkilesadhammā, tathā saññāapariññātaggahaṇena."
1049778,192,456,37,67,1,206,24,"‘‘ Khīṇāsavo parikkhīṇabhavasaññojano’’ ti ettha pana āsavā saññojanāni ca sarūpato gahitāni, tathā nandiggahaṇena taṇhāgahaṇena ca taṇhā, evampettha sarūpato pariyāyato ca taṇhā avijjā tappakkhiyadhammā ca gahitā. "
1049779,192,456,68,84,1,131,14,"Tattha taṇhāya visesato rūpadhammā adhiṭṭhānaṃ, avijjāya arūpadhammā, te pana sabbadhammaggahaṇena pathavīādiggahaṇena ca dassitā eva. "
